# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:17
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_cfc018e4:

    # "I wake to the annoying din of my alarm clock, its bright red numerals lighting up my face."
    "Em desperta el soroll molest del despertador, els números vermells m'il·luminen la cara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:21
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_209990fd:

    # "It's the same alarm clock I had at home, one of the few remaining artifacts from my days before coming to Yamaku. I'd hoped that using it would help ease my transition into this new life."
    "És despertador que tenia a casa, un dels pocs artefactes que em queden d'abans de venir al Yamaku. El vaig portar perquè esperava que em fes més fàcil el canvi cap a aquesta nova vida."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:23
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_22de8e82:

    # "No such luck, though."
    "No hi ha hagut tanta sort."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:25
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_2c369007:

    # "Groggily dragging myself out of bed, I wipe the sleep out of my eyes, then reach over to my desk. I open a couple of the bottles of medication strewn across it, and swallow a few pills dry."
    "M'arrossego fora del llit, encara espès, em trec les lleganyes i m'apropo a l'escriptori. Obro un parell d'ampolles de medicació que hi ha escampades per sobre i m'empasso un parell de pastilles sense aigua."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:27
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_129293d6:

    # "By now, the process is starting to become automatic - something I should be glad for, given their purpose."
    "A hores d'ara, aquest procés comença a ser automàtic, cosa que m'hauria d'alegrar, si tenim en compte la seva finalitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:34
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_3279adb9:

    # "Feeling much more awake than before, I wander into the bathroom."
    "Em sento molt més despert que abans, vaig cap al quarto de bany."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:41
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_9d2e4b78:

    # "While the shower warms up, my mind begins to wander as my new daily routine begins once again."
    "Mentre la dutxa s'escalfa, em poso a divagar mentre començo de nou la meva rutina diària."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:43
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f481e23b:

    # "The bright colors of the fireworks fill my mind, as do the two girls with whom I spent my time watching them. It feels strange to be moved so much by people I know so little about."
    "Els colors brillants dels focs artificials m'omplen la ment, igual que les dues noies amb qui vaig mirar-los. Se'm fa estrany que em commoguin tant unes persones que conec de fa tan poc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:45
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f5543ea2:

    # "Then again, I suppose these aren't normal circumstances. At least I have someone to talk to, now, aside from my schoolmate next door."
    "Però suposo que no són circumstàncies normals. Almenys ara tinc algú amb qui parlar, a part del company d'escola del costat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:52
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_18392d56:

    # "With the time left before school begins today waning, I begin to get ready for class."
    "Quan queda poc perquè comencin les classes d'avui, em començo a preparar per marxar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:59
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_ef224c4c:

    # "Walking through the door into the classroom, I notice that I'm still somewhat early. I see about five or six students milling around, most of them looking as if they'd rather be still in bed."
    "Quan travesso la porta i entro a l'aula, m'adono que encara és d'hora. Veig que hi ha cinc o sis estudiants congregats, la majoria sembla que preferirien continuar al llit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:61
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_067cc585:

    # "It's at times like this that I appreciate being a morning person. That said, two students in particular seem just as perky as always."
    "És en moments com aquest que aprecio ser matiner. Dit això, hi ha dues estudiantes que semblen tan benhumorades com sempre."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:63
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_c67625c7:

    # hi "Hi Shizune, hi Misha."
    hi "Hola Shizune, hola Misha."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:69
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_6073338f:

    # "I suddenly realize that my greeting would be lost on the former, so I quickly follow it up with a wave. She doesn't seem overly bothered."
    "De sobte, m'adono que la meva salutació es perdrà en la primera, així que m'afanyo a saludar-la amb la mà. No sembla estar de gaire humor."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:71
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_dbaeb253:

    # "Or interested, for that matter."
    "O interessada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:76
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:81
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_fe67b690:

    # mi "Hello, Hicchan~! Are you feeling well?"
    mi "Hola, Hicchan~! Et trobes bé?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:83
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_4b8901cb:

    # "I can only assume her greeting comes from Shizune. It's hard to tell if she's speaking as herself or Shizune, sometimes."
    "Només puc suposar que la salutació ve de Shizune. De vegades és difícil dir si parla com ella mateixa o com Shizune."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:85
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7af88fd1:

    # hi "Better than most everyone else, I guess. You two seem bright and chipper."
    hi "Sembla que millor que la resta. Vosaltres dues sembleu animades i alegres."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:94
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_3a3d20d6:

    # "Misha signs this back to Shizune as I say it, eliciting a somewhat terse answer, if her sharp and rapid arm movements are any indication."
    "La Misha es gira cap a la Shizune per dir-li mentre parlo, fet que provoca una resposta seca, si ens guiem pels seus moviments de braços rígids i ràpids."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:96
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f9de7fcc:

    # "Considering that these two made such a big deal out of the festival preparations, I probably should've chosen my words more carefully."
    "Si tenim en compte que aquests dues han donat tanta importància als preparatius del festival, segurament hauria d'haver triat les meves paraules amb més cura."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:101
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "...!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:106
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f2ee3be2:

    # mi "Since you're a new student, we've been cutting you some slack. Please don't expect this kind of task-dodging to be allowed in the future."
    mi "Com que ets un estudiant nou, hem estat força indulgents amb tu. Si us plau, no t'esperis que en el futur et continuem permetent evadir les teves tasques."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:108
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_8b1b6c15:

    # "Misha looks as if she's about to add her own comment, but quickly goes back to interpreting as Shizune continues, unabated."
    "La Misha sembla que està a punt d'afegir el seu propi comentari, però de seguida torna a fer d'intèrpret mentre la Shizune continua, immutable."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:114
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_23c53818:

    # mi "While your contribution to class 3-2's stall is appreciated—"
    mi "Tot i que apreciem la teva contribució a la parada de la classe 3-2..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:116
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_9dd790f1:

    # "Huh. Word sure got around quickly. That, or these two have their fingers on the pulse of the school."
    "Bah. Les coses s'escampen de pressa. Això, o aquestes dues estan al corrent de tot allò que passa a l'escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:121
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_52919325:

    # mi "—we would prefer your efforts to be focused on the task at hand. Namely, your own class."
    mi "—preferiríem que centressis els teus esforços en l'assumpte que ens ocupa. O sigui, la teva pròpia classe."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:123
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_ee93d9e1:

    # "As much as I hate to admit it, they do have a point. Before I can respond, though, Shizune adds something more, which draws a smile from Misha."
    "Per molt que no m'agrada admetre-ho, sí que tenen raó. Però abans de poder respondre, la Shizune afegeix alguna cosa més, que li dibuixa un somriure a la Misha."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:128
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_ef2b123c_1:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:133
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_8e8e1c9e:

    # mi "Did you enjoy the festival, then~?"
    mi "Al final, ho vas passar bé al festival~?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:135
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f33b2189:

    # "Lecture over, I guess."
    "S'ha acabat el sermó, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:137
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_efef2299:

    # hi "Yeah, it was good. Did you two enjoy it?"
    hi "Sí, prou bé. I vosaltres dues el vàreu gaudir?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:143
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f225f44f:

    # "Shizune gives a short nod as Misha grins and bounces her head up and down. The contrast, side-by-side, is amusing."
    "La Shizune fa que sí breument mentre la Misha riu i assenteix amb força. El contrast, l'una al costat de l'altra, és divertit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:145
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_2f080066:

    # "Out of the corner of my eye, I notice more students starting to trickle into the classroom. A quick glance at my watch confirms that they're a few minutes late."
    "De reüll, veig que cada cop més estudiants comencen a entrar de mica en mica a l'aula. Confirmo, amb un cop d'ull ràpid al rellotge, que arriben uns minuts tard."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:158
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a0855f2a:

    # "I look over to Hanako's seat and realize that she's already there, and contentedly reading a book. It makes me wonder just how long she's been there without me noticing."
    "Miro el seient de la Hanako i m'adono que ja ha arribat, i està contenta llegint un llibre. Em pregunto quant de temps fa que ha arribat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:172
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_48b87a87:

    # "With heavy footsteps coming up the hallway signaling Mutou's arrival, our idle talking comes to an end and I take my seat next to Misha."
    "Se sent que arriba en Mutou per les passes fortes que se senten al passadís, s'acaba aquesta conversa que no sembla que vagi a arribar a enlloc i jo m'assec al costat de la Misha."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:174
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_d5812d21:

    # "As the door slides open, he strides through with a ponderous gait. His posture is even worse than usual, and his eyes are barely staying open. I guess my quip to Lilly and Hanako about the staff was misplaced."
    "Quan la porta s'obre, avança a passos mesurats. La seva postura és pitjor del que és habitual, i en prou feines pot mantenir els ulls a oberts. Suposo que la meva broma a la Lilly i la Hanako sobre el personal estava fora de lloc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:178
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_0ffd98b9:

    # "Everyone opens their books as he reaches his desk, and the first class of the new week begins."
    "Tothom obre els seus llibres a mesura que arriba al seu escriptori, i comença la primera classe de la nova setmana."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:190
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_fbb93d12:

    # "I rub my eyes as the lunch bell rings out, glad for the temporary reprieve from work."
    "Em frego els ulls mentre sona la campana de dinar, content pel respir temporal de la feina."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:200
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_8d2cf21e:

    # "I'm entirely unsurprised when I look over to the door and see Lilly standing there, cane in hand, patiently waiting for Hanako."
    "No em sorprèn gens quan miro cap a la porta i veig a la Lilly dempeus, amb el bastó a la mà, esperant pacientment a la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:202
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f72317b2:

    # "Considering her acceptance of my request to join them yesterday, I decide to spend my lunchtime with them rather than eat alone."
    "Tenint en compte que ahir van acceptar que m'unís, decideixo passar l'hora de dinar amb elles en lloc de menjar sol."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:213
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_9fe1e60e:

    # "Hanako moves surprisingly fast to meet her companion, and the two enter the hallway before I can catch up."
    "La Hanako es mou sorprenentment ràpid per trobar-se amb la seva companya, i totes dues surten al passadís abans no pugui atrapar-les."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:226
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_46add2a6:

    # "Lilly's head turns slightly, registering the sound of footsteps behind her. As Hanako notices and follows her lead, she almost jumps in surprise."
    "La Lilly gira lleugerament el cap, per sentir el so dels passos darrere seu. Quan la Hanako se n'adona i la imita, gairebé fa un bot de l'ensurt."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:231
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_fd0aa95d:

    # ha "Hi… Hisao?"
    ha "Ei... Hisao?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:239
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_181f7493:

    # ha "I mean… um… hello, Hisao…"
    ha "Vull dir... em... hola, Hisao..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:241
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_0e1c2e96:

    # hi "Hi. Sorry if I startled you."
    hi "Ei. Perdona si t'he espantat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:247
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_d1d2fa32:

    # "Lilly turns to greet me, helped in her orientation by Hanako."
    "La Lilly es gira per saludar-me, amb l'ajuda de la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:252
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_5be9f64a:

    # li "Good afternoon, Hisao. Are you joining us?"
    li "Bona tarda, Hisao. Vens amb nosaltres?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:254
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_20abc6a8:

    # hi "If it's no trouble. There's not much else to do, really."
    hi "Si no és cap problema. No hi ha molt més a fer, de veritat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:259
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_30b8a954:

    # "Lilly gives a small nod, as if to silently brush away any idea that it would be troubling in the least."
    "La Lilly fa un subtil gest amb el cap, com si s'espolsés discretament qualsevol idea que la pogués preocupar mínimament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:269
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_b4e51361:

    # "We descend one set of stairs and walk down the hallway to the usual room, our pace somewhat quicker than usual thanks to Lilly using Hanako for direction, rather than her cane and the railings."
    "Baixem un tram d'escales i caminem pel passadís fins a la sala de sempre, el nostre ritme és una mica més ràpid que normalment, gràcies al fet que la Lilly fa servir a la Hanako per guiar-se, en lloc del seu bastó i les baranes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:274
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_6813c57b:

    # "As expected, it's deserted. The sounds of the other clubs can only barely be heard as sunlight streams into the room from outside."
    "Com era d'esperar, està buida. En prou feines es poden sentir els altres clubs, mentre els rajos de sol s'escolen dins de l'habitació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:276
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_22aef5a0:

    # "Looking around the room, I notice a couple of empty easels propped up against a wall that I don't think were there before. The art club must use this room as extra storage."
    "Miro al voltant de la sala i veig un parell de cavallets buits recolzats contra una paret que no crec que hi fossin abans. El club d'art deu utilitzar aquesta sala com a emmagatzematge de més."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:281
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_1e3d9a46:

    # ha "Should I get the chess set out?"
    ha "Voleu que tregui els escacs?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:283
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_883ce386:

    # "Hanako's voice seems less tense when she's directly addressing Lilly."
    "La veu de Hanako sembla menys tensa quan s'està dirigint directament a la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:292
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_220d1b6b:

    # li "Yes. I'll make tea while you sort the pieces."
    li "I tant. Prepararé el te mentre ordenes les peces."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:294
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_bf5ff7bd:

    # hi "Ah, I can do that for you, if you'd like."
    hi "Ah, ja ho puc fer jo, si vols."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:304
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_43276568:

    # "She ponders the offer for a moment before smiling, confirming that I've made the right choice. Her face is remarkably easy to read."
    "Reflexiona un moment sobre l'oferta abans de somriure, i em confirma que he pres la decisió correcta. És molt fàcil llegir-li la cara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:309
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_fd3e1f8e:

    # li "Very well. Thank you."
    li "Molt bé. Gràcies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:322
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_387bc699:

    # "She slides her retracted cane into the handle of her bag and sets it against one of the table legs, before taking a seat opposite Hanako."
    "Fa lliscar el bastó retràctil per dins la nansa de la seva bossa i la recolza en una de les cames de la taula, abans de seure davant de la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:324
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_6e6173c1:

    # "As I prepare tea for the three of us, I can hear the small wooden pieces being set on the board. I wonder how good Lilly is at chess, given her circumstances."
    "Mentre preparo te per als tres, puc sentir com col·loca les petites peces de fusta al tauler. Em pregunto si la Lilly és bona jugant a escacs, donades les seves circumstàncies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:326
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_5b512e1f:

    # "By the time I place the steaming teacups onto the table, Lilly and Hanako have already moved their first pieces as they nibble on sandwiches and rice balls from their respective bags."
    "En el moment en què col·loco les tasses de te fumejant sobre la taula, la Lilly i la Hanako ja han mogut les seves primeres peces mentre piquen entrepans i boles d'arròs de les seves respectives bosses."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:339
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_39f816ad:

    # "I note that the chessboard they're using has holes in the middle of each square and pegs on the bottom of the pieces, and has each dark square slightly raised."
    "Observo que el tauler d'escacs que estan utilitzant té forats al mig de cada quadrat i marques a la part inferior de les peces, i cada quadrat fosc està lleugerament aixecat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:341
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_e3556111:

    # "Watching Lilly's fingers skating over the board, tracing out the positions of the pieces, makes me marvel a little at the simple ingenuity of the design. It must be specifically made for blind players."
    "Observo els dits de la Lilly lliscar sobre el tauler, seguint les posicions de les peces, i em meravello una mica davant la senzilla inventiva del disseny. Deu estar fet específicament per a jugadors cecs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:352
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_22c987dc:

    # hi "Here you go."
    hi "Aquí teniu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:361
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_9bb6ec05:

    # "Hanako gives a small nod as I put down the cup next to her side of the board. Lilly's hand ventures sideways slightly, so I gently place the cup touching the tips of her fingers; a gesture she seems to appreciate."
    "La Hanako fa un subtil gest amb el cap quan li poso la tassa al costat del tauler. La mà de la Lilly es desvia lleugerament cap a un costat, així que li acosto suaument la tassa a la punta dels dits; un gest que sembla apreciar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:366
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_5348a403:

    # "I finally take a seat and silently sip my tea as the two play. The contrast in their appearances while playing is interesting to watch."
    "Finalment, m'assec i prenc el te en silenci mentre totes dues juguen. El contrast del seu aspecte mentre juguen és interessant de veure."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:371
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_c48283bf:

    # "Hanako looks closely at the board, her face one of focused concentration. Lilly, on the other hand, keeps her head level and maintains her calm neutrality."
    "La Hanako inspecciona el tauler de prop, fa cara de concentrada. La Lilly, en canvi, manté cap dret i la seva serenitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:373
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a5388aac:

    # "Lilly's gentle voice addresses both of us as she continues to play."
    "La veu suau de la Lilly s'adreça a tots dos mentre continua jugant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:378
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_44ae68d3:

    # li "How was class, now that the festival's over?"
    li "Com van les classes, ara que el festival s'ha acabat ?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:384
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a8f4627f:

    # "I look to Hanako to see whether she'll answer first, but see that she's doing the same."
    "Miro a la Hanako per veure si respondrà primer, però m'adono que ella fa el mateix."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:389
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a6531f6a:

    # hi "Not… great. Half the class seemed to be dozing off, even including the teacher. Not to mention a test on top of all that."
    hi "No... gaire bé. La meitat de la classe semblava adormida, fins i tot el professor. I a sobre avui hi havia un examen."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:394
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_3ba01a37:

    # "Hanako quietly adds her own agreement with this."
    "La Hanako afegeix amb veu baixa que hi està d'acord."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:399
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_c4eb83b8:

    # li "I could imagine that being a bit difficult for you, being a transfer student."
    li "M'imagino que et deu haver estat difícil, sent estudiant nou."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:404
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_c7be8f45:

    # hi "Well, I think I did fine. Other than the shock of a test coming so early, science is probably my best subject."
    hi "Bé, crec que ho he fet bé. A part del xoc de fer una prova tan aviat, la ciència és l'assignatura que millor porto."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:409
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_0dbdc18c:

    # hi "How'd you do, Hanako?"
    hi "I tu que tal, Hanako?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:414
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_95edaad7:

    # ha "Me? Ah… okay… I guess…"
    ha "Jo? Ah... bé... suposo..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:416
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_fd54115d:

    # "Hanako's too sincere to be able to pull off lying very well. That much is obvious."
    "La Hanako és massa sincera per poder dir una bona mentida. Es veu de lluny."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:421
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_3ab6b265:

    # "Lilly's smile slips very slightly. From her reaction, Hanako mustn't be skilled enough at academics to do very well without preparation."
    "Els llavis de la Lilly insinuen un lleuger somriure. Per com reacciona, la Hanako no deu ser gaire hàbil en els estudis per sortir-se'n sense preparació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:426
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_e71d46df:

    # hi "How did your class handle it, Lilly?"
    hi "Com us ha anat la classe a vosaltres, Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:431
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_31f90efe:

    # li "It went surprisingly well, actually. Only one student was absent, which was better than what the teacher expected."
    li "Ha anat sorprenentment bé, de fet. Només ha faltat un alumne, millor del que el professor s'esperava."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:437
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_e7d05f59:

    # "With the topic all but run dry, the two concentrate on their chess game once again."
    "Amb el tema a punt d'esgotar-se, totes dues es tornen a concentrar en el seu joc d'escacs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:442
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_0d73c6be:

    # "I can't say I've ever liked the idea of chess as a spectator sport, but given its unique nature, for once I'm rapt in watching the game unfold."
    "Mai he gaudit de veure els escacs com a espectador esportiu, però donada la seva naturalesa única, per primera vegada estic embadalit veient com es desenvolupa el joc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:448
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7863142a:

    # "As time wears on, both of them demonstrate decent skill at playing the game. Having captured two more pawns than Hanako, Lilly has the upper hand, but only slightly."
    "A mesura que el temps s'esgota, totes dues demostren prou habilitat per jugar-hi. La Lilly, després de menjar-se dos peons més que la Hanako, va guanyant, però per poc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:454
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_d8e18ae1:

    # "…until Hanako makes a strange move with her queen. Seizing upon this lapse in judgment, Lilly takes the piece with her knight."
    "... fins que la Hanako fa un estrany moviment amb la seva reina. Aprofitant aquesta badada de judici, la Lilly li pren la peça amb el cavall."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:459
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_448e1fc2:

    # "Without hesitation, Hanako moves a pawn to take Lilly's rook on the opposite side of the board, and promotes it to queen."
    "Sense dubtar-ho, la Hanako mou un peó per prendre la torre de la Lilly al costat oposat del tauler, i el converteix en dama."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:465
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a4cb861f:

    # "Lilly's face falters as her fingers move over the pieces and she realizes that she just fell to Hanako's trap. It's a little distracting to have the board traced out after each move, even if it's out of necessity."
    "La cara de la Lilly es desfà quan els seus dits es mouen sobre les peces i s'adona que acaba de caure a la trampa de la Hanako. Distreu una mica veure com segueix les posicions amb la mà després de cada moviment, encara que sigui per necessitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:467
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_5e3826da:

    # "Judging by Hanako's lack of reaction, she must be used to this. She and Lilly must have played at least a few games of chess against each other, after all."
    "Si he de jutjar per la falta de reacció de Hanako, ja hi deu estar acostumada. Al capdavall, ella i la Lilly deuen haver jugat unes quantes partides d'escacs plegades."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:469
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7764d55b:

    # ha "Check."
    ha "Escac."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:474
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_8f7327a0:

    # hi "That's not bad at all. Nice, Hanako."
    hi "No ha estat gens malament. Ben fet, Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:479
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_e72e67fe:

    # "The compliment causes her to flower into a surprised blush."
    "S'enrojola tota sorpresa amb aquest elogi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:481
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_f8d5e9ff:

    # ha "Th-thank you. I didn't… think it would work."
    ha "Gra-gràcies. No... sabia si funcionaria."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:486
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_c82e3000:

    # "I look over to Lilly, her fingers having just finished tracing out the position of her remaining pieces in an attempt to extricate her king from this bind."
    "Miro cap a la Lilly, els seus dits just han acabat de traçar la posició de les seves peces restants per intentar treure el seu rei d'aquesta destret."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:488
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_508dc190:

    # li "I think this is checkmate…"
    li "Crec que això és escac..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:493
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "Hmm?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:498
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_fa8a56d4:

    # "I take another look at the board to confirm."
    "Torno a mirar el tauler per confirmar-ho."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:500
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_df77fbab:

    # "Sure enough, her king has nowhere to escape without being threatened by another piece. My earlier question as to which of them is better at this has just been answered."
    "Té raó, el seu rei no pot escapar sense que l'amenaci una altra peça. S'acaba de respondre a la meva pregunta anterior sobre quina en sabia més."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:505
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_bbc95e02:

    # hi "So it is."
    hi "Ho és."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:510
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_88394bf5:

    # "Lilly gives a small sigh as Hanako smiles. From their reactions, this seems like a fairly usual result."
    "La Lilly fa un petit sospir mentre la Hanako somriu. Per les seves reaccions, això sembla un resultat força habitual."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:515
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a787d79f:

    # hi "How long have you two been playing?"
    hi "Quant de temps fa que jugueu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:521
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_aaea8c8c:

    # ha "Since… I was young."
    ha "Des de... que soc petita."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:527
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_29cd0152:

    # "Lilly nods at Hanako's brief answer."
    "La Lilly assenteix amb la resposta breu de la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:532
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a5813e3d:

    # li "Hanako taught me how to play soon after I met her. I can beat her every now and then… but that's a rarity. I don't seem to have the right mindset for it."
    li "La Hanako em va ensenyar a jugar poc després de conèixer-la. Puc guanyar-la de tant en tant... però és poc freqüent. Sembla que no tinc la forma de pensar adequada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:534
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_b87fcf4e:

    # "If Lilly came to Yamaku at the start of high school, and met Hanako when she moved to the dorms, that'd mean she's only been playing for about one year."
    "Si la Lilly va venir al Yamaku a l'inici de l'institut, i va conèixer a la Hanako quan es va traslladar als dormitoris, això voldria dir que només ha estat jugant durant un any."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:536
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_ce86aded:

    # "After seeing Hanako's level of play, I'm not too surprised Lilly has trouble beating her."
    "Després de veure el nivell de joc de la Hanako, no em sorprèn gaire que la Lilly no pugui vèncer-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:542
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7e10977e:

    # ha "But… she's better at languages than I am, so…"
    ha "Però... és millor en idiomes que jo, així que..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:548
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_d58113c4:

    # "Lilly gives an appreciative, if slightly amused, smile at Hanako's quick reversal of her compliment."
    "Lilly somriu amb afecte, si bé una mica alegre, pel fet que la Hanako li hagi tornat l'elogi tan ràpid."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:553
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_beedabe2:

    # li "Well, that's how it is."
    li "Bé, és així."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:558
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_66fee553:

    # "Much to everyone's surprise, the bell suddenly rings, heralding an end to the lunch break."
    "Tots ens sorprenem quan la campana sona de sobte, que assenyala el final de la pausa per dinar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:564
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7fb6e2ab:

    # li "Hmm, that game lasted longer than I thought it did."
    li "Hmm, la partida ha durat més del que pensava."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:566
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_9765189b:

    # hi "Same. I guess we'd better get back to class."
    hi "Cert. Millor que tornem aviat a classe,"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:573
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a470eb89:

    # "Hanako's already in the middle of packing up, so I take Lilly's bag and offer it to her. To my surprise, she takes it and nods, but then places it back down on the table."
    "La Hanako ja està mig recollint-ho tot, així que agafo la bossa de la Lilly i li ofereixo. Em sorprenc quan l'agafa i assenteix, però després la torna a posar sobre la taula."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:582
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_fec6788a:

    # li "Hisao, may I make a request?"
    li "Hisao, et puc fer una pregunta?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:584
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_683db8a9:

    # hi "Sure, go ahead."
    hi "I tant, dispara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:589
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7642e029:

    # li "Would you mind if I were to quickly feel your face?"
    li "Em deixaries palpar-te ràpid la cara?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:591
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_9bd5c3d0:

    # hi "Oh, uh… no, go ahead. I don't mind."
    hi "Oh, eh... d'acord, fes. No em fa res."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:593
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_961b7d07:

    # "The question takes me severely off guard, but once I regain my composure it seems sensible enough. So far Lilly's had no idea what I actually look like, and this would be her only way to find out."
    "La pregunta m'agafa amb la guarda baixa, però un cop recupero la compostura, em sembla prou lògica. Fins ara, la Lilly no ha sabut com soc físicament, i aquesta és l'única manera que té d'esbrinar-ho."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:600
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_66cd43f4:

    # "Lilly raises her right hand, which I take in mine and guide to my face before letting go."
    "La Lilly aixeca la mà dreta, que agafo amb la meva i la guio fins a la meva cara abans de deixar-la anar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:602
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_8cf57413:

    # "The room is entirely silent as Lilly's hand moves over and around my features, from my chin, to my cheeks, to everywhere else."
    "L'habitació està totalment en silenci mentre la mà de la Lilly es mou per sobre i al voltant dels meus trets, des de la barbeta, fins a les galtes, per tot arreu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:604
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_94c228ae:

    # "I expected this to feel a lot more disquieting than it does. I suppose that's because the action is entirely a matter of practicality, being functionally no different to simply looking at someone's face."
    "Pensava que això seria molt més inquietant del que realment és. Suposo que això és perquè es tracta d'una qüestió pràctica, sent funcionalment similar al fet de mirar la cara d'algú."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:606
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_c0f48b48:

    # "Her hand is soft, but what takes me by surprise is the length of her fingers, not to mention how sure even the slightest of her movements are. I have no doubt that her level of tactile feeling would be far beyond mine."
    "La seva mà és suau, però em sorprèn com té de llargs els dits, per no parlar de la seguretat fins i tot del més mínim dels seus moviments. No tinc cap dubte que la seva sensibilitat tàctil deu superar de lluny la meva."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:608
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_af383d5e:

    # "Her hand briefly runs once through my hair before retreating. I'm sure that every inch of my face has been committed to her memory. It's only now, too, that I realize Hanako has been silently watching the entire time."
    "Em passa la mà breument pels cabells abans de retirar-la. N'estic segur que ha memoritzat cada centímetre de la meva cara. Ara m'adono que la Hanako ens ha estat mirant tot aquest temps en silenci."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:617
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_a16de6b0:

    # li "Thank you for letting me do that, Hisao."
    li "Gràcies per deixar-me fer-ho, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:622
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_ccbde474:

    # li "And if I might add, I think you are quite handsome."
    li "Si em permets dir-ho, crec que ets força atractiu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:624
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_71e665b0:

    # "I blush a little at her remark, before raising a questioning eyebrow."
    "Em poso una mica vermell per la seva frase, abans d'aixecar una cella interrogant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:626
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_abf6dfa9:

    # hi "But if you can't see, how…"
    hi "Però si no em pots veure, com..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:631
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_b30cc688:

    # li "Just because I can't see, that doesn't mean I don't have my own preferences."
    li "Que no pugui veure-hi no vol dir que no tingui els meus gustos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:636
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_d6d7cf4c:

    # ha "Um, we'd better go now…"
    ha "Daixò, hauríem de marxar ja..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:638
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7ad89f6c:

    # hi "Yeah, that's a good point. I guess we'll see you later then, Lilly."
    hi "Si, tens raó. Suposo que fins després, Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:645
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_140bb7ff:

    # "Walking through the hallways back to our classrooms, I notice that Hanako seems quieter than before, but also more comfortable."
    "Tot caminant pels passadissos de tornada a les nostres aules, noto que la Hanako sembla més callada que abans, però també més còmode."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:647
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_ebde3ce4:

    # "Lilly, her hand on Hanako's shoulder, seems to pick up on her assured pace as well, smiling as they walk."
    "La Lilly, amb la mà a l'espatlla de la Hanako, sembla agafar també un pas ferm, tot somrient mentre camina."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:649
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_7ce1a44f:

    # "If I could spend the rest of my time at Yamaku like this, I don't think it'd be so bad. All that's needed for joy are small exchanges of happiness, after all."
    "Si pogués passar la resta del meu temps al Yamaku d'aquesta manera, no estaria tan malament. Al cap i a la fi, per ser feliç necessites petits intercanvis d'alegria."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:656
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_0f7b578e:

    # "As I reach my desk and set my bag beside it, I realize something. Or rather, my stomach does."
    "Quan arribo al meu escriptori i deixo la bossa al costat, m'adono d'una cosa. O més ben dit, el meu estómac se n'adona."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:658
translate ca a2_lilly_earl_grey_5abfd5b8:

    # "I was so busy with those two, I forgot to buy lunch…"
    "Estava tan ocupat amb aquestes dues, m'he oblidat de comprar el dinar..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:674
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_8d9b1f87:

    # "Saturday. My second most favorite day of the week."
    "El dissabte. És el meu segon dia preferit de la setmana."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:676
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_854757a7:

    # "This is almost entirely due to the fact that it is the day with the second least amount of school, with class ending at the beginning of lunch."
    "Això es deu quasi totalment al fet que és el segon dia amb menys classes, ja que s'acaben quan comença l'hora de dinar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:681
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_0ee4f470:

    # "I open my door confidently, myself being more than confident of being able to get enjoyment out of the fine weather and shorter class length."
    "Obro la porta amb confiança, em sento més que segur de poder gaudir del bon temps i del curt període de classes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:689
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_80108354:

    # "I confidently stride down the hallway and down the stairs to the lobby of the male dorms."
    "Avanço amb seguretat pel passadís i baixo per les escales fins al vestíbul dels dormitoris masculins."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:693
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ed4b8b1e:

    # "I confidently look behind me to see whose footsteps are approaching."
    "Miro amb confiança darrere meu per a veure de qui són els passos s'acosten."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:697
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7e541872:

    # "I… lose my confidence in this day being enjoyable."
    "I... perdo la confiança de què aquest dia sigui agradable."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:710
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_23c20dee:

    # ke "Hey man. Sup?"
    ke "Ei tio. Com prova tot?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:712
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fd7c5948:

    # hi "Not much I guess, just looking forward to the afternoon. You?"
    hi "Bé suposo, amb ganes que arribi la tarda. I tu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:717
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f2aab39b:

    # "He wraps an arm around my slumped shoulders far too comfortably. Something's up."
    "Em passa un braç per sobre les espatlles amb massa confiança. Alguna cosa passa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:722
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6742c84e:

    # ke "Let's step outside, shall we?"
    ke "Sortim fora, d'acord?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:724
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1e4020df:

    # hi "I was just about to, before you stopped me."
    hi "Estava a punt de fer-ho quan m'has parat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:732
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_5b2c0dd3:

    # "He doesn't take my reaction to his theatrics well. Ignoring him, I walk outside and start down the steps."
    "No es pren bé la reacció al seu teatre. L'ignoro, camino cap a fora i començo a baixar pels esglaons."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:734
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4c8bdcb9:

    # "It doesn't take too long for him to catch up with me again. I wonder if he wants money, or to rant about another conspiracy. Maybe both."
    "No tarda gaire en tornar-me a atrapar. Em pregunto si vol diners, o si vol parlar d'una altra conspiració. Potser totes dues coses."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:744
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ab218535:

    # ke "I've got a bone to pick with you."
    ke "Tinc un assumpte pendent amb tu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:746
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_417298e1:

    # hi "Uh huh."
    hi "Sí, ja."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:748
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e5298636:

    # ke "It's about that blonde. You know who I'm talking about."
    ke "Parlem d'aquella rossa. Ja saps qui vull dir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:750
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9f1757b2:

    # "Conspiracy it is. For a moment I contemplate feigning ignorance, but realize this will go quicker if I just let him get it all out."
    "Toca conspiració. Per un moment em plantejo fingir ignorància, però m'adono que tot anirà més ràpid si el deixo desfogar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:752
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4654e266:

    # hi "Lilly? The one from your class?"
    hi "La Lilly? La que va a la teva classe?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:757
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9a1e05c4:

    # ke "You're on first name terms with her?!"
    ke "Ja us dieu pel nom i tot?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:759
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b82211ca:

    # "He looks positively shocked at this development. Did he not expect me to be able to answer?"
    "Sembla molt sorprès per això. Esperava que no el pogués respondre?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:764
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c7d47272:

    # "He gathers himself and coughs into his fist. Dramatically, like everything he does."
    "Recobra la serenitat i s'estossega al puny. Dramàticament, com tot el que fa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:766
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e89f5c16:

    # ke "Well, never mind that. I'm here to warn you. You know. Man to man."
    ke "Bé, això no importa. Soc aquí per avisar-te. Ja m'entens. D'home a home."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:768
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1655a9fb:

    # hi "Warn me about what? Lilly?"
    hi "Avisar-me sobre què? Sobre la Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:770
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_cee24fb6:

    # ke "Yeah. You don't know her, man."
    ke "Sí. No la coneixes, tio."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:772
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_935a1c53:

    # "It's mostly true. I've only known her and Hanako for less than two weeks, and even then we've just been exchanging banal chatter about school as we while away lunch."
    "Té raó. No fa ni dues setmanes que les conec tant a ella com a la Hanako, i fins ara només hem intercanviat xerrameca banal sobre l'escola mentre dinem."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:774
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_906ca4e8:

    # hi "I'm pretty sure you don't either."
    hi "N'estic segur que tu tampoc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:776
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fe6b1d2b:

    # ke "That's not the point. You're the one spending inordinate amounts of time with her."
    ke "Aquesta no és la qüestió. Ets tu qui passa massa temps amb ella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:778
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7ebd27e4:

    # "It distresses me that someone like Kenji, who's probably as far out of the loop as one could possibly get, knows about such a trivial fact as who I choose to befriend."
    "M'angoixa que algú com Kenji, que probablement està tan desinformat com es pugui estar, sàpiga un fet tan trivial com qui trio per fer-me amic."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:780
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_497bdd00:

    # "Then again… I am a transfer student, and she's not only the representative of their class, but also a tall blonde."
    "A més... jo soc estudiant nou, i ella no només és la delegada de la seva classe, sinó també una rossa alta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:782
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_39e95b87:

    # "Maybe I should appreciate this ranting as a warning that the rumor mill exists in this school, and that I'm firmly within it."
    "Potser hauria d'apreciar aquesta conversa com una advertència que la fàbrica de rumors també existeix a l'escola, i que hi he entrat de ple."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:784
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ce160a7d:

    # hi "It's just lunch. Nothing special."
    hi "Només dinem. Res especial."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:789
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_2c2e8fa2:

    # ke "Look, man, under the bridge. See this bridge? You're under it. A man's gotta do what a man's gotta do to get intel."
    ke "Mira, tio, sota el pont. Veus aquest pont? Tu estàs sota. Un home ha de fer el que sigui per tal d'aconseguir informació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:794
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9ff38001:

    # ke "I just want to make sure you don't end up too far under the bridge."
    ke "Només vull assegurar-me que no acabis massa lluny sota el pont."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:796
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e3c652d9:

    # hi "You're losing me, Kenji."
    hi "M'he perdut, Kenji."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:801
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4d1c67c2:

    # ke "That's okay, lots of people get lost. That's why I'm here to help."
    ke "No passa res, la gent es perd. Per això estic aquí, per ajudar-te."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:807
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_30e89f2d:

    # ke "Just be careful around her, okay? She looks all harmless on the outside, but I've heard shit. Bad shit."
    ke "Ves-hi amb compte, d'acord? Sembla inofensiva per fora, però he sentit moltes coses. Molta merda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:812
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1f47e8c4:

    # ke "You know the Student Council, right?"
    ke "Coneixes el Consell d'estudiants, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:814
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_64c2486e:

    # "He seems to involuntarily shudder as he says the words. Putting him and Shizune together in a room is an amusing mental exercise. I wonder if they've met."
    "Sembla que s'esgarrifa involuntàriament mentre diu les paraules. Posar-los a ell i a la Shizune en una habitació és un exercici mental divertit. Em pregunto si s'han conegut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:816
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b91aa998:

    # hi "Yeah, Shizune and Misha are in my class. I seem to have dodged the draft, though."
    hi "Sí, la Shizune i la Misha van a la meva classe. Tot i que sembla que he esquivat una bala."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:821
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_531b417f:

    # ke "Good man. Good man."
    ke "Ben fet, tio. Ben fet."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:826
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9f52f646:

    # ke "But this blonde? She was there. In the Student Council. Right. Damn. There."
    ke "Però aquesta rossa? N'era part. Del Consell d'Estudiants. N'era. Puta. Part."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:828
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_3cff92ac:

    # hi "I see. And?"
    hi "Ja. I què?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:830
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_32a5d186:

    # ke "And she's not there now."
    ke "Ara ja no n'és."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:834
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_35c4f685:

    # hi "…"
    hi "..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:836
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a614d113:

    # ke "Seriously, think about it. Something must have gone down."
    ke "De debò, pensa-hi. Alguna cosa deu haver passat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:838
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_62efd8e9:

    # "I stop walking for a moment, giving the idea more thought than I probably should."
    "Deixo de caminar un moment, hi dono més voltes de les que segurament hauria de fer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:840
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4e03f33d:

    # "It would explain that fight the two had, at least in part. Wait, no, not really. Even leaving the Student Council would need a catalyst."
    "Això explicaria la baralla que van tenir, almenys en part. Espera, no, de fet no. Fins i tot per sortir del Consell d'Estudiants faria falta un catalitzador."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:842
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_2e3ce77d:

    # "In the end, it doesn't explain much at all. Other than the fact that their feud goes back some ways."
    "Al final, no explica gaire. A part del fet que la seva enemistat es remunta a alguna altra cosa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:844
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c76d7ede:

    # hi "I guess you have a point. I'm not seeing how that really affects me, though."
    hi "Suposo que tens raó. Però no acabo d'entendre com això m'afecta a mi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:849
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a4c49570:

    # ke "Okay, now field this one. Lilly's foreign, obviously."
    ke "D'acord, anem a pams. La Lilly és estrangera, òbviament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:851
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fa08f1c5:

    # hi "Obviously."
    hi "Òbviament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:853
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9d75420e:

    # ke "Now, what nationality is she?"
    ke "Val, quina nacionalitat té?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:855
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_66015df6:

    # "I open my mouth to give the answer, but realize that I have none. In fact, I've given the matter very little thought."
    "Obro la boca per donar la resposta, però m'adono que no la sé. De fet, no hi he pensat gaire en això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:857
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ae5582fe:

    # "Given that she has no accent and acts perfectly Japanese, I suppose it never really seemed important. Now that he mentions it though, I am rather curious."
    "Com que no té accent i es comporta com una japonesa, mai m'ha semblat realment important. Ara que ho diu, em pica la curiositat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:859
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d0453458:

    # hi "To be honest, I don't know. Maybe English? They like tea."
    hi "Si et soc sincer, no ho sé. Anglesa potser? Li agrada molt el te."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:861
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9cf2fb58:

    # "I probably shouldn't resort to stereotypes, but that's the only lead I have."
    "Probablement no hauria de recórrer als estereotips, però aquesta és l'única pista que tinc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:868
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_08c6b6db:

    # ke "You're not thinking. Luckily, you have me here to think for you."
    ke "No fas servir el cap. Tens sort de tenir-me aquí per pensar amb tu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:870
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b32e4395:

    # hi "Gee, thanks."
    hi "Ui, gràcies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:872
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_580efa52:

    # "He brushes off the quip effortlessly."
    "Es desfà de la broma sense cap esforç."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:877
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a739fff4:

    # ke "Now answer me this: who has lots of social power, is filthy stinking rich - you know blondes are all rich, right? - has a long history of disputes and used to belong to a much larger organization?"
    ke "Ara contesta'm: qui té molt poder social, és fastigós i pudent ric - ja saps que les rosses són totes riques, oi? - Té una llarga història de disputes i solia pertànyer a una organització molt més gran?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:879
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_19d3f135:

    # hi "The Roman Catholic Church?"
    hi "L'Església catòlica?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:884
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_34b49839:

    # ke "…Well okay, there's that."
    ke "... Bé, en part sí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:889
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f2e9121d:

    # ke "But there's also the Mafia. Come on. Rich, foreign, there's no way she doesn't have connections to them."
    ke "Però també la màfia. Espavila. Rica, estrangera, segur que d'alguna manera hi està connectada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:891
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_cffe58bf:

    # "I have reason to doubt the logic of his deductions, but he shows no sign of stopping."
    "Tinc raons per a dubtar de la lògica de les seves deduccions, però no sembla que vulgui parar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:897
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_018329ca:

    # ke "So do you know where I think she's from?"
    ke "Vols saber d'on crec que realment és?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:899
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_1d960b34:

    # hi "Italy?"
    hi "Itàlia?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:904
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_90f119d6:

    # ke "Mainland Italy's small-time, dude. She has to be from Sicily. All those mafioso types come from there."
    ke "La Itàlia continental és poca cosa, noi. Ha de ser de Sicília. Tots aquests tipus de mafiosos venen d'allà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:909
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_376f257a:

    # ke "Wait, no, Russia. Damn, this could be bad. The Mafia there is serious business, man; Ex-KGB everywhere, paramilitaries, hardcore smuggling, and—"
    ke "Espera, no, Rússia. Collons, això es podria complicar. La màfia que hi ha té negocis seriosos, tio; ex-KGB per tot arreu, paramilitars, contraban del xungo i-"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:911
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b4761584:

    # hi "Wait, wait, stop, just slow down a sec. What point are you trying to get at here?"
    hi "Espera, espera, para, relaxa't un moment. On se suposa que vols arribar?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:916
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_8933072f:

    # ke "You don't know what she'll do, man. I won't get in your way - agents don't operate like that - but I just want you to be careful."
    ke "No saps què farà, tio. No m'interposaré en el teu camí, els agents no ho fem això, però vull que vagis amb compte."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:921
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7e2d3032:

    # ke "When the time comes, we'll need all the help we can get. I don't want to lose you, comrade."
    ke "Quan arribi el moment, necessitarem tota l'ajuda possible. No et vull perdre, camarada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:923
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_03335320:

    # "Well, at least he's concerned for me. Kinda."
    "Bé, com a mínim es preocupa per mi. Una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:930
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ae2db81a:

    # "I wave goodbye to him as we separate out to our respective classes, but I'm not sure that he sees the gesture."
    "M'acomiado d'ell mentre ens dirigim cap a les nostres respectives classes, però no n'estic segur que m'hagi vist."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:937
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_5b1c983d:

    # "Piling my books into my bag, I catch a glimpse of the library books I'd borrowed last week. I might as well return them, considering they took all of two days to finish."
    "Apilo els llibres dins la meva bossa, i veig els de la biblioteca vaig demanar la setmana passada. També podria tornar-los, ja que van trigar dos dies a acabar-los."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:939
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_32f14797:

    # "I briefly consider inviting Hanako along to the library, but she's already gone. It'll probably be better for my studying if I'm alone anyway."
    "Per un instant, em plantejo convidar a la Hanako a la biblioteca, però ja ha marxat. De totes maneres, serà millor si estic sol per estudiar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:941
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_86aa5e35:

    # "With a quick stretch and a wave to a couple of classmates who give the same to me, I make my way out of the classroom."
    "Faig un estirament ràpid i m'acomiado amb un gest d'un parell de companys que em responen de la mateixa manera, i m'obro pas per sortir de l'aula."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:948
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_fc51f162:

    # "As I open my bag and shove the books through the returns slot in the front counter, I notice a strange person behind the desk. Old and graying, she must be Yuuko's replacement when she's working at the café."
    "Quan obro la bossa i entaforo els llibres per la ranura de la bústia de retorn al taulell de davant, noto una persona estranya darrere de l'escriptori. Vella i grisa, deu ser qui substitueix a la Yuuko quan li toca treballar a la cafeteria."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:950
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ebd7dbd7:

    # "I begin looking for a free table, a task made somewhat difficult considering that, despite there not being many students in here, they're all sitting at their own tables."
    "Començo a buscar una taula lliure, una tasca força difícil tenint en compte que, tot i que aquí no hi ha molts estudiants, tots estan asseguts a les seves pròpies taules."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:952
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ae912e20:

    # "Noticing a familiar head of hair, I walk over to one near the Braille section."
    "Veig uns cabells que em sonen, vaig cap a un prop de la secció Braille."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:957
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7f42075f:

    # "It's hard to tell whether Lilly's concentrating hard or not, her placid expression holding perfectly still as her finger slides across the dot-filled pages of her book."
    "És difícil saber si la Lilly està molt concentrada o no, te una expressió relaxada i s'està totalment quieta mentre llisca el dit per les pàgines plenes de punts del seu llibre."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:959
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_65430f73:

    # hi "Hi. Mind if I sit here?"
    hi "Ei. Et fa res si sec aquí?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:964
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_12a516df:

    # li "Hmm? Oh, no problem at all…"
    li "Mmm? Oh, cap problema..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:966
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_16ad4f08:

    # "She trails off, evidently still focused on her business at hand."
    "No acaba la frase, es nota que està centrada en les seves coses."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:973
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a27535b0:

    # li "Ah, Hisao."
    li "Oh, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:978
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_255aaa14:

    # "She gives a nod of greeting as I sit opposite her at the table, pluck a chemistry textbook out of my bag and quickly thumb to the chapter we're covering in class."
    "Em fa un gest amb el cap per saludar-me mentre m'assec a la taula davant seu, trec el llibre de química de la bossa i de seguida vaig al capítol que estem fent a classe."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:980
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f323f6d4:

    # "For a while, we sit there and read, each in our own way."
    "Durant un temps, seiem i llegim, cadascun a la seva manera."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:982
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_40903c14:

    # "Seeing her reminds me of what Kenji said this morning, though. That and the fact that I've never seen someone read in Braille before makes me keep throwing glances at her."
    "Però veure-la em recorda allò que m'ha dit en Kenji aquest matí. Això i el fet que mai hagi vist algú llegir abans en Braille, em fa seguir mirant-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:984
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4fe62599:

    # "I kind of feel guilty about it, given that she has no way to realize I'm doing so, so I decide to just ask her about it. Her lineage isn't exactly a state secret, after all, and there is another thing I've only just noticed from her movements."
    "Això em fa sentir culpable, ja que no té manera d'adonar-se de què estic fent, així que decideixo preguntar-li sobre el tema. El seu llinatge no és exactament un secret d'estat, al cap i a la fi, i hi ha una altra cosa que acabo de notar pels seus moviments."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:986
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_30976bb3:

    # hi "Hey Lilly, mind if I ask a question?"
    hi "Escolta Lilly, et puc fer una pregunta?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:991
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_2f8227c6:

    # li "Not at all. Is anything wrong?"
    li "I tant. Passa alguna cosa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:993
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_473e3592:

    # hi "I was just wondering… you're at least part foreign, right?"
    hi "Em preguntava... si més no, ets mig estrangera, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:998
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c42b6b2d:

    # "She gives a small giggle before setting down her book."
    "Se li escapa una rialleta abans de deixar el seu llibre."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1003
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d55f46a4:

    # li "I've always been amused at how squeamish people are about that. Akira's mentioned how much she and I look different from most others before."
    li "Sempre m'ha divertit com n'és de maniàtica, la gent, sobre el tema. L'Akira m'havia mencionat abans com de diferents com ella i jo de la resta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1008
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_065ffe05:

    # li "The details are a bit complicated, but I'm half Japanese, half Scottish."
    li "Els detalls són una mica complicats, però soc mig japonesa, mig escocesa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1010
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4d31e17e:

    # "…Scottish? That was not exactly my first guess. It takes some effort to not blurt it out loud."
    "... Escocesa? Aquesta no era pas la meva primera suposició. Em cal fer un esforç per no saltar i dir-ho en veu alta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1012
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_7c132b43:

    # "I try to conjure images of the place in my mind. I think as far as the UK goes, Scotland isn't bad to live in… but I'm not really sure."
    "Intento imaginar-me el lloc en la meva ment. Crec que, pel que fa al Regne Unit, Escòcia no deu ser un mal lloc per viure... però no n'estic gaire segur."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1014
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_26bd030e:

    # "My first guess of England was surprisingly close, at least geographically. That does leave another question though."
    "La meva primera suposició d'Anglaterra era sorprenentment propera, almenys geogràficament. Però això deixa una altra qüestió."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1016
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c1289fe0:

    # hi "But you have no accent…?"
    hi "Però no tens accent...?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1021
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_3b17bf36:

    # li "That's where the details begin. I was born and raised in Japan, despite my mother being foreign."
    li "Aquí és on comencen els detalls. Vaig néixer i he crescut al Japó, tot i que la meva mare era estrangera."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1023
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f27a2235:

    # hi "Ah, I get it."
    hi "Ah, ja ho entenc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1025
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a4bba82a:

    # "Hold on, if she moved to the dorms simply due to Akira working longer hours…"
    "Un moment, si es va traslladar als dormitoris només perquè l'Akira treballava més hores..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1027
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_bec2b1ea:

    # hi "So they don't live near the school?"
    hi "Llavors, no viuen a prop de l'escola?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1032
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a49e7c20:

    # "She gives a small sigh, as if she didn't expect me to go any deeper. Was her previous frankness just a front?"
    "Fa un sospir lleu, com si no esperés que anés més enllà. La seva franquesa anterior només era aparença?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1034
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6a55a5c8:

    # li "Not… exactly. It's been a long time since we've actually met."
    li "No... exactament. Fa molt de temps que no els veig."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1036
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_06c3f775:

    # "I feel like I'm not getting the whole story, but I don't really want to go unduly prying into her situation. Her about-face shows she feels kind of awkward about it."
    "Tinc la sensació que no estic entenent tota la història, però no vull entrar més del compte en la seva situació. Fa cara d'estar una mica incòmoda sobre el tema."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1038
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_61be3ec3:

    # hi "So… do you speak much English? To be honest I don't know that much about Scotland, but at least I know that's the main language there."
    hi "Així que... parles bé l'anglès? Sincerament, no sé gaire d'Escòcia, tot i que com a mínim sé que aquesta és la seva llengua principal."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1040
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_44cff7db:

    # "It takes her a moment to collect herself, appreciating the change in topic."
    "Es pren un moment per refer-se, se la veu alleujada amb el canvi de tema."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1045
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d08a062a:

    # li "That's right. My family mostly used Japanese around the house when I was young, but they made sure Akira and I knew our Scottish side just as well."
    li "Així és. La meva família utilitzava sobretot el japonès a casa quan era petita, però també es van assegurar que l'Akira i jo coneguéssim la nostra part escocesa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1050
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_03730284:

    # li "I'm fluent in the language, but I'm also studying it in school. To keep my skills up and to have the qualifications on paper, mainly."
    li "La parlo amb fluïdesa, però també l'estic estudiant a l'escola. Principalment, per mantenir la meva habilitat i tenir les qualificacions en paper."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1052
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d251289a:

    # hi "So you're bilingual? That's pretty impressive."
    hi "Així ets bilingüe? Quina passada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1057
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_d1a24460:

    # li "I wouldn't go that far. Having parents who can speak the language is a large advantage, and English books in Braille aren't too hard to buy or import. With Yuuko's help, at least."
    li "No diria tant. Tenir pares que puguin parlar la llengua és un gran avantatge, i els llibres en anglès en braille són fàcils de comprar o importar. Amb l'ajuda de la Yuuko, almenys."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1062
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_500d4233:

    # li "There's a relatively high demand for local English teachers here anyway, which also helps give me some motivation to learn it well."
    li "De totes maneres, hi ha força alta demanda de professors locals d'anglès per aquí, cosa que m'ajuda a motivar-se per aprendre'l bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1064
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_3c588ed9:

    # "Demand for English teachers? For a moment, I wonder why she brought this up."
    "Demanda de professors d'anglès? Per un moment, em pregunto per què ho ha deixat anar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1066
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_75e2055d:

    # hi "You're planning to be an English teacher?"
    hi "Et planteges ser professora d'anglès?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1071
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_63803f95:

    # "She gives an enthusiastic nod."
    "Assenteix amb entusiasme."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1073
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_ca6b3e38:

    # "It must be nice, having such a definite future in mind. I've never really given much thought to mine, so I'm kind of envious."
    "Deu estar bé això de tenir un futur tan definit en ment. Mai he pensat gaire en el meu, així que em fa una mica d'enveja."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1075
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a4df7806:

    # hi "Hmm…"
    hi "Hmm..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1080
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_132986ee:

    # li "What's wrong?"
    li "Què passa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1082
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4294f020:

    # hi "It's just… I could see you as a teacher pretty easily. It suits you."
    hi "Només que... et puc imaginar com a professora. Fa per tu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1087
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_0611dff9:

    # "For a moment, she's speechless. She lowers her face a little and lets out a nervous giggle, something I've never seen her do before."
    "Momentàniament, es queda sense paraules. Abaixa una mica la cara i deixa anar una rialla nerviosa, cosa que mai li havia vist fer abans."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1089
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_e9ed0225:

    # "With Lilly's role as a class representative and her dependable nature, teaching does seem to be a line of work fitting her personality."
    "Quan penso en el paper de la Lilly com a delegada de classe i la seva naturalesa fiable, tinc la sensació que l'ensenyament és un ram que s'adapta a la seva personalitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1091
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_97422389:

    # hi "Sorry, that was probably a little much. It is true, though."
    hi "Perdona, potser m'he passat. Però ho penso de veritat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1096
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_40d53304:

    # "Waving her hand in front of her face dismissively, she quickly recovers."
    "Movent la mà davant de la cara amb indiferència, es recupera ràpidament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1098
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_cfd565df:

    # li "It's not that, it's just that… only one person's ever said that to me before."
    li "No és això, és només que... ets la segona persona que em diu això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1102
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_b0443108:

    # "A short, somewhat awkward silence follows the discussion. Without knowing it, I ended up steering into a troublesome topic again."
    "Després de parlar, es fa un silenci curt i una mica incòmode. Sense saber-ho, he tornat a tocar un tema problemàtic."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1104
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_69b2c9c1:

    # "I should try to cheer her up a little. It was me who went and got her brooding, after all."
    "Hauria d'intentar animar-la una mica. Al cap i a la fi, he estat jo qui l'ha ensopit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1106
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_f336e180:

    # hi "Want to go grab lunch at the cafeteria after this?"
    hi "Vols anar a buscar el dinar a la cafeteria després?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1108
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6f9f70d2:

    # "It might perk her up a bit, or at least take her mind off her apparently complicated family situation."
    "Potser això l'anima una mica, o com a mínim li treu del cap la seva situació familiar, que sembla complicada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1113
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4e8be329:

    # "Going by her smile, it seems to have the intended effect."
    "A jutjar pel seu somriure, sembla que ha tingut l'efecte que volia."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1118
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_9b3c543d:

    # li "I appreciate the thought, but the food there…"
    li "Gràcies per l'oferiment, però el menjar que tenen..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1120
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_0da1cb4b:

    # "Quite a quick redirection of the conversation. She does have a point though - the food there isn't the greatest."
    "Quin canvi de direcció de la conversa. Però té raó, el menjar que hi ha no és el més bo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1122
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_16e5fc78:

    # hi "Maybe the Shanghai? We could ask Hanako if she wants to come as well."
    hi "Potser al Shanghai? Podríem preguntar-li a la Hanako si vol venir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1127
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_948ec9ba:

    # li "Ah…"
    li "Ah..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1129
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_46b9decc:

    # hi "What is it?"
    hi "Què passa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1134
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_495ff28d:

    # li "I almost forgot, until you reminded me. Hanako's birthday is coming up soon, and I was going to go shopping in the city for a present tomorrow."
    li "Quasi me n'oblido, fins que m'ho has recordat. D'aquí poc és l'aniversari d'en la Hanako, i demà volia anar a comprar-li un regal a la ciutat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1136
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_6773633a:

    # hi "If that's an invitation, I'd be happy to accompany you."
    hi "Si m'estàs convidant, estaré encantat d'acompanyar-te."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1138
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_03131f0d:

    # "The ability to get more used to the layout of the city would probably be a good thing. I have barely set foot in there, so I'd be hopelessly lost by myself."
    "Seria una bona oportunitat de poder acostumar-me més a la composició de la ciutat. Amb prou feines l'he trepitjat, així que jo sol m'acabaria perdent de mala manera."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1143
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_a816f2f5:

    # "She gives a nod, signaling that she happily approves of this plan for Sunday."
    "Assenteix, com a mostra que accepta de gust aquest pla per al diumenge."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1145
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_c4cafb8b:

    # "We eventually get back to our books, though before I begin reading again I steal one last glance at her."
    "Finalment, tornem als nostres llibres, però abans de començar a llegir de nou, la miro de reüll."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1147
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_4ea8d959:

    # "Maybe I've been thinking on my situation too much. After all, everybody here would have their own unique circumstances."
    "Potser he donat massa voltes a la meva situació. Al cap i a la fi, tothom aquí té les seves pròpies circumstàncies excepcionals."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1149
translate ca a2_lilly_a_pound_sterling_525f58b2:

    # "The chance to get outside and clear my head will probably do me good."
    "L'oportunitat de sortir i aclarir-me cap segur que m'anirà bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1167
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_c1efd181:

    # "Bored of standing in place and watching the television in a shop window, I pull myself away from the tacky display with little effort."
    "Cansat d'estar dret mirant la televisió en un aparador, m'allunyo de l'enganxosa pantalla amb una mica d'esforç."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1169
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4bb26bac:

    # "After living at Yamaku, the city seems like an entirely different world."
    "Després de viure al Yamaku, la ciutat sembla un món completament diferent."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1171
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8e4f2929:

    # "No running in the halls. Calm and orderly conduct is to be used at all times in the classrooms. Students are to exit rooms after checking both directions for oncomers. Elevators are reserved for movement-impaired students. Single file on stairs."
    "No es pot córrer pels passadissos. A les aules la gent sempre es comporta de manera calmada i ordenada. Quan surten d'una sala, els estudiants han de mirar les dues direccions per si algú s'acosta. Els ascensors estan reservats per a estudiants amb discapacitat física. Només es fa una fila per les escales."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1173
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_fedcaa36:

    # "Compared to such strict, almost regimental, standards, the city's shopping arcade might as well be a strange country."
    "En comparació amb aquestes normes estrictes, gairebé regimentals, el centre comercial de la ciutat bé podria ser un país estrany."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1175
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f53092f8:

    # "While the school may have its fair share of hustle and bustle during the festival, the outside world is much different."
    "Si bé l'escola pot tenir la seva part justa de tràfec i moviment durant el festival, el món exterior és molt diferent."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1177
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2b8845d1:

    # "It's strange. Having lived in a metropolitan city before my accident, this should feel more natural than Yamaku and the surrounding town ever could."
    "És estrany. Tot i que vaig viure en una ciutat metropolitana abans del meu accident, em sento més còmode al Yamaku i el poble del voltant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1179
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4fa5ae83:

    # "Yet it feels foreign, somehow. The elevated walkways and tall buildings, each adorned with billboards taller than any three people, don't do anything to distract me from the passing crowd's reactions."
    "No obstant això, d'alguna manera se sent estrany. Els passos elevats i els edificis alts, cadascun adornat amb cartells més alts que tres persones juntes, no em distreuen de les reaccions de la multitud que passa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1192
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_979fa55c:

    # "Lilly keeps one hand on my shoulder, the other holding her cane which taps the ground with a metronome-like steadiness. Looking over to her, that neutral smile of hers still holds."
    "La Lilly té una mà a la meva espatlla i amb l'altra porta el bastó, que dona cops a terra amb el tremp d'un metrònom. Quan la miro, veig que encara té aquell somriure neutral."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1194
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b88c98b4:

    # "Having only seen her in school uniform, I'd not have recognized her as she sat on a bench waiting for me to come, if not for her cane propped up against it and her distinctive hair."
    "Després d'haver-la vist només amb uniforme escolar, no l'hauria reconegut asseguda en un banc esperant-me, si no hagués estat perquè portava bastó i que té uns cabells distintius."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1196
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_00b448d9:

    # "I can't tell whether they're glancing at her due to her height, her foreign looks, her obvious blindness, or all three. Not that any of those would make the situation any less uncomfortable than it is."
    "No sabria dir si la miren per la seva alçada, per la seva aparença estrangera, per la seva ceguesa innegable, o per les tres a la vegada. Cap d'aquestes tres coses faria que la situació fos menys incòmoda del que és."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1201
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_c4bed76b:

    # li "Do you have any ideas of where to look first, Hisao?"
    li "Saps d'algun lloc on puguem començar a mirar, Hisao?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1203
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a97c4d21:

    # "Her soft voice breaks me out of my line of thought."
    "La seva veu suau em trenca de la línia de pensaments."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1205
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2ea19df6:

    # "I can't imagine that she's failing to notice the attention she garners, but she seems unfazed by it. I get the feeling she's the type to enjoy walking outside, so she might be used to it by now."
    "No puc imaginar-me que no noti l'atenció que desperta, però sembla impassible. Tinc la sensació que és el tipus de noia a qui li agrada caminar a fora, així que potser ja hi està acostumada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1207
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d3a97790:

    # hi "Not really. This is my first time in this city, so I've got no idea of where to go."
    hi "No et pensis. Aquest és el primer cop que vinc a la ciutat, així que no en tinc ni idea."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1212
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_21706370:

    # "She furrows her brow in thought, planning a route for us to take. And, come to think of it, a way to communicate it."
    "Arruga el front mentre pensa, planejant quina ruta podem fer. I, ben mirat, també una manera de comunicar-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1214
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_365b889d:

    # "Something I'd noticed in the time I've been with her is how, when deep in thought, she lacks close to any form of body language to show it."
    "Una cosa que he notat d'ençà que hi passo temps és com, quan està absorta en els seus pensaments, li falta gairebé tota forma de llenguatge corporal per comunicar-ho."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1216
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d28aa5b0:

    # "Her expression may change, but not a hint of movement shows. She seems to have little in the way of sweeping physical gestures in general though, so I've assumed it's part of her reserved nature."
    "Potser canvia d'expressió, però no mostra el més mínim moviment. En general, no sembla fer molts gestos físics, així que suposo que és part de la seva naturalesa reservada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1221
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2c6c3bfa:

    # li "Is there a large electronics store near here?"
    li "Hi ha alguna botiga d'electrònica per aquí?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1223
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_aa267599:

    # "I take a quick look around, mostly finding clothing stores. After a few seconds I notice a store with a bright blue sign some distance away that fits her description."
    "Faig un cop d'ull ràpid al voltant, sobretot hi ha botigues de roba. Poc després, una mica lluny, veig una botiga amb un senyal blau i brillant que s'adapta a la seva descripció."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1225
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_71676974:

    # hi "Yep, it's just a bit ahead of us. Should we go in that direction?"
    hi "Sí, més endavant. Anem cap a aquella direcció?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1230
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d9feda33:

    # "Thankfully, it's just the information she needed. With a nod we start off and head towards Lilly's unknown destination, landmarks being our guide."
    "Afortunadament, és just la informació que necessitava. Assenteix, comencem a caminar i ens dirigim cap al destí desconegut de la Lilly, guiats per punts de referència."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1239
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d1aa582d:

    # "Storeowner" "Here you go. One vanilla, one chocolate."
    "Botiguer" "Aquí teniu. Un de vainilla i un de xocolata."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1244
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1329f005:

    # "I hand the money over the counter and take the cones to the railing that Lilly's sitting on."
    "Deixo els diners al taulell i porto els cons a la barana on està asseguda la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1246
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0962595b:

    # "I can't believe I let her trick me like this. She not only led me to an ice cream stall, but also got me to buy her some. At least she gave me the money for hers."
    "No em puc creure que m'hagi deixat enganyar així. No només m'ha portat a una parada de gelats, sinó que també ha fet que li'n comprés. Almenys m'ha donat els diners pel seu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1252
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b79c4c20:

    # "Sure enough, she's patiently waiting where I'd left her. I guess she was planning on making the day an event, rather than a simple shopping trip."
    "Ben segur que està esperant pacientment on l'he deixat. Suposo que volia que el dia fos una ocasió, en lloc d'una simple sortida per comprar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1259
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b2d132e5:

    # "I call out to her and slowly place the vanilla cone in her outstretched hands, being careful to make sure she has a good hold of it before letting go."
    "La crido i a poc a poc li col·loco el cucurutxo de vainilla a les mans que té esteses, i amb cura m'asseguro que el té ben agafat abans de deixar-li anar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1261
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_87ed4b3d:

    # "At least her tastes are fairly normal. I was worried she'd ask for some weird flavor when she first asked."
    "Encara sort que té gustos força normals. Em preocupava que em demanés un gust estrany quan m'ho ha demanat per primera vegada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1263
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_810283a7:

    # hi "Here's the change."
    hi "Aquí tens el canvi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1268
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_c61d7352:

    # li "It's okay, keep it."
    li "Està bé, queda-te'l."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1270
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_caf683e7:

    # "I move to protest, but realize the futility of doing so over such a small amount. I slip the coin into my pocket, supplementing my meager allowance ever so slightly."
    "Faig el gest de protestar, però m'adono que és inútil fer-ho per una quantitat tan petita. Em fico la moneda a la butxaca, arrodonint una mica la meva magre setmanada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1275
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_526919b4:

    # "Lilly shows no signs of wanting to get up, so I take a seat beside her and start eating my own ice cream."
    "La Lilly no mostra cap senyal de voler aixecar-se, així que m'assec al seu costat i començo a menjar-me el gelat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1277
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_033c98a9:

    # hi "The summer weather's nice. Hopefully it will hold out for a while."
    hi "Quin bon temps d'estiu. Espero que aguanti un temps."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1282
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_69ed5824:

    # li "You too? I'm beginning to think I'm the only person who prefers winter."
    li "Tu també? Començo a pensar que soc l'única persona a qui lli agrada l'hivern."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1284
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_dd0d7d0d:

    # "I contemplate her statement for a long moment."
    "Reflexiono una bona estona sobre les seves paraules."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1286
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_38642f8f:

    # hi "Yeah, I think you might be."
    hi "Sí, segur que ho ets."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1291
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_df61433e:

    # "It draws the intended reaction. She's cute when she's pouting."
    "Aconsegueixo la reacció que buscava. És maca quan fa morros."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1293
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a3f778a6:

    # hi "Still, I can't really imagine what's so good about winter. You can't go out without bundling up, and you still freeze anyway."
    hi "Tot i això, no entenc què t'agrada tant de l'hivern. No pots sortir sense abrigar-te, i de totes maneres t'acabes congelant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1298
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_63a8ccae:

    # li "I used to live further north, where there'd be plenty of snow to play in, so it's a little nostalgic. I don't like the heat very much, either."
    li "Abans vivia més al nord, on hi havia molta neu per poder jugar, així que em desperta nostàlgia. A més, tampoc m'agrada massa la calor."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1300
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3403858c:

    # hi "At least you can wear a skirt, so don't complain about that."
    hi "Com a mínim pots portar faldilla, així que no et pots queixar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1305
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ba45acbb:

    # "She gives an amused giggle as we both get back to finishing off our already melting cones."
    "Fa una rialleta divertida mentre tots dos ens posem a acabar-nos els cucurutxos mig fosos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1313
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ff9fdc73:

    # "I idly sit and watch the crowds going by as we eat, catching bits and pieces of conversation."
    "M'assec i veig com passa la multitud mentre mengem, atrapant trossos de conversa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1319
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_30d4abd2:

    # "Looking to Lilly, I see her dutifully licking her ice cream from the top downwards, blissfully unaware of the fact that it's beginning to melt."
    "Miro a la Lilly, veig com llepa diligentment el gelat de dalt a baix, feliçment sense saber que està començant a fondre's."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1321
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d6a9b8ce:

    # hi "It's melting."
    hi "S'està desfent."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1326
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f34e9e20:

    # li "Where?"
    li "On?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1328
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2c9d1540:

    # hi "Um… down a bit?"
    hi "Mm.. cap a baix?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1333
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bf8f3356:

    # "She lowers her mouth from the top of the cone, but has no idea of exactly where the ice cream's dripping. What follows is a game of guiding her left and right until she finally finds it."
    "Baixa la boca de la part superior del cucurutxo, però no té ni idea exactament d'on degoteja el gelat. El que segueix és un joc de guiar-la esquerra o dreta fins que finalment ho troba."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1335
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_363e7b0a:

    # "To any onlooker, it must seem absolutely bizarre - a girl with her eyes closed turning her cone over and over as the guy next to her gives instructions. A strange variant of childhood blindfold games, maybe."
    "Per a qualsevol espectador, ha de semblar totalment estrany: una noia amb els ulls tancats girant el cucurutxo una vegada i una altra mentre el noi del seu costat li dona instruccions. Una variant estranya de la gallineta cega, potser."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1340
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ec466669:

    # "In good time we finally finish our treats, and while away the time conversing casually."
    "Per fi ens acabem els gelats, i deixem passar el temps mentre conversem casualment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1347
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_00604461:

    # "Caught mid-sentence, Lilly perks her head in her trademark manner. It's an unmistakable sign that something's caught her attention."
    "Atrapada a mitja frase, la Lilly aixeca el cap d'una manera característica. És un senyal inconfusible que alguna cosa li ha cridat l'atenció."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1352
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_948ec9ba:

    # li "Ah…"
    li "Ah..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1354
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_46b9decc:

    # hi "What is it?"
    hi "Què passa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1359
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_70f4b98f:

    # li "Is Akira somewhere over there? I think I heard her."
    li "Hi ha l'Akira per allà? M'ha semblat sentir-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1367
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9f03fd14:

    # "I raise an eyebrow as I look in the direction she's facing, somewhat doubtful of her ability to pick out Akira's lone voice in the din."
    "Aixeco una cella mentre miro en la direcció cap a on apunta, una mica dubtós de la seva capacitat per distingir la veu aïllada de l'Akira d'entre tot l'escàndol."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1374
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_71dd79a9:

    # "Sure enough though, a blonde girl in a suit can be seen through the tiny gaps between people walking every which way."
    "No obstant això, puc veure una noia rossa amb vestit a través dels petits buits entre les persones que caminen cap a cada direcció."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1376
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9c0e287b:

    # "I raise a hand and wave, trying to catch her attention."
    "Aixeco una mà i li faig senyals, intentant cridar la seva atenció."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1378
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2a330b55:

    # hi "Satou! Hey, Satou!"
    hi "Satou! Eh, Satou!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1383
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8868f7ef:

    # "She stops in her tracks and looks towards me, evidently noticing my calls. As she does, I notice someone walking beside her."
    "S'atura en sec i mira cap a mi, evidentment nota que la crido. A la vegada, veig a algú que camina al seu costat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1385
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_868733cc:

    # "I can't get a good look at whoever it is though, before the two begin walking towards where we are."
    "No veure ben bé qui és abans que tots dos comencin a caminar cap a on som."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1408
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_97418ca5:

    # "As they reach us, Lilly and I stand and dust ourselves off."
    "Quan s'apropen, la Lilly i jo ens posem drets i ens espolsem."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1413
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ea4a144e:

    # li "Akira?"
    li "Akira?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1421
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f4af1f4c:

    # aki "Hey, you two."
    aki "Eh, vosaltres dos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1434
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_23d32919:

    # "She nods towards me, a gesture which I quickly return. My gaze shifts towards the young girl next to her, and our eyes meet. As they do, Akira plops a hand onto her head, a move which doesn't seem to faze her."
    "Em fa una inclinació amb el cap, i de seguida li torno el gest. La meva mirada es desplaça cap a la jove que té al costat, i els nostres ulls es creuen. Quan passa, l'Akira li posa una mà al cap, un moviment que no sembla molestar-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1439
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2dbd862a:

    # hh "I don't believe we've met. I'm Hideaki. Pleased to meet you, Hisao."
    hh "No crec que ens hàgim conegut abans. Soc en Hideaki. Encantat de conèixer-te, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1441
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bb81baab:

    # "A guy's name, huh? Guess I just dodged a bullet there. He bows, somewhat restrained by Akira's hand being on his head."
    "Nom de noi, eh? Suposo que acabo d'evitar fotre la pota. Inclina el cap, una mica frenat per la mà de l'Akira que té al cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1447
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_57c9bbcf:

    # li "Oh, Hideaki's here too? Are you well?"
    li "Oh, també hi ha en Hideaki? Com estàs?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1452
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b9e8a699:

    # hh "Akira's been taking very good care of me, thank you."
    hh "L'Akira em cuida molt bé, gràcies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1458
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5612a85c:

    # "Akira grins as if to affirm the point and rubs his head hard, dragging it around in a circular motion. His dreary face during this is somewhat amusing."
    "L'Akira fa mitja rialla com si afirmés allò que ha dit i li frega fort el cap, arrossegant-lo amb un moviment circular. La cara lúgubre que posa mentre li fa és força divertida."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1463
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_17944aa9:

    # aki "Uncle's out on business again, so I'm just taking him around town for today."
    aki "El tiet ha tornat a marxar per negocis, així que l'estic portant a fer un tomb avui."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1468
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9115b3a5:

    # aki "I'd have preferred to be spending the day on a date with my boyfriend, but…"
    aki "Hauria preferit passar el dia tenint una cita amb el meu xicot, però..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1473
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_7eb444c6:

    # "Hideaki gives a cough to try and redirect Akira's thoughts."
    "Hideaki té un atac de tos per intentar redirigir els pensaments de l'Akira."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1475
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f903fd68:

    # "As he does so, though, I find mine wandering. They're related? And further, as first cousins? I suppose that explains why she's taking care of him in any case."
    "No obstant això, mentre ho fa, trobo que els meus divaguen. Són parents? A més, deuen ser cosins germans? Suposo que això explica per què se'n fa càrrec en qualsevol cas."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1477
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f592f1e0:

    # hi "Come to think of it, Hideaki, how did you know my name?"
    hi "Ara que hi penso, Hideaki, com és que sabies el meu nom?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1482
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4b6ca4f9:

    # hh "Akira told me. Being a Yamaku student, I suppose you're disabled in some way?"
    hh "L'Akira me l'ha dit. Si ets un estudiant del Yamaku deus tenir alguna discapacitat, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1484
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e8149f66:

    # hi "Not everyone in Yamaku's disabled…"
    hi "No tothom del Yamaku té una discapacitat..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1486
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ae3d5159:

    # "Which I only learned a handful of days ago. I give silent thanks to Shizune and Misha for their stream of information about how the school works."
    "Cosa que vaig aprendre fa poc. Dono les gràcies a la Shizune i la Misha pel seu fil d'informació sobre com funciona l'escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1488
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ff90943f:

    # "Because of them, I found out that since the school will accept practically anybody suffering from non-mental disabilities, it doesn't discriminate against healthy people either."
    "Gràcies a elles vaig descobrir que, ja que l'escola accepta pràcticament a qualsevol persona que no pateixi una discapacitat mental, tampoc discrimina a les persones sense discapacitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1490
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_708b12c8:

    # "It seems unlikely that many in good health would enroll there though. While the standard of education is pretty high, it's extremely isolated and very much focused on helping disabled students."
    "No obstant això, és poc probable que algú amb bona salut s'hi matriculi. Tot i que el nivell d'educació és molt alt, està molt aïllat i està molt enfocat a ajudar als estudiants amb discapacitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1495
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_30739bd7:

    # hh "You're dodging the question."
    hh "Has esquivat la pregunta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1497
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0ba98048:

    # "Damn, he's sharp."
    "Merda, és llest."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1499
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1b306030:

    # "Before I can say another word though, he decides to take a stab at it himself."
    "Però abans que pugui dir res més, decideix intentar-ho ell mateix."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1504
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_335e01ef:

    # hh "If I were to call it myself… your heart?"
    hh "Si ho hagués d'endevinar, diria... el cor?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1513
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9dbffc8e:

    # "Akira looks mildly curiously at me, her interest piqued as well. That sure was a lucky guess."
    "L'Akira amb mira amb curiositat, també li ha despertat l'interès. Sens dubte ha estat un encert fortuït."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1515
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_cf455b71:

    # hi "How did you…?"
    hi "Com ho has...?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1523
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_84895856:

    # hh "You show no missing limbs or deformities, so external disabilities are out."
    hh "No et falta cap membre, ni tens deformitats així que he descartat les discapacitats externes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1528
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_50039022:

    # hh "Considering the lack of any strange mannerisms, it's also unlikely that you'd have any mental disability."
    hh "Si tenim en compte que no tens tics estranys, sembla poc probable que pugui ser una discapacitat mental."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1533
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_de0a44c8:

    # li "But Yamaku doesn't take mentally disabled students."
    li "Però si el Yamaku no accepta estudiants amb discapacitat mental."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1538
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a82cf1e5:

    # hh "I know."
    hh "Ho sé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1543
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0f231ad7:

    # hh "Leaving that aside, the only possibility left is that of internal disabilities."
    hh "Deixant-ho de banda, l'única possibilitat que queda és una discapacitat interna."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1548
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_423e5adb:

    # hh "I didn't know which one you might bear, so I guessed. Correctly, as it turns out. And your reaction confirmed my guess."
    hh "No sabia quina podies tenir així que ho he deduït. Correctament, pel que sembla. I la teva reacció m'ho ha confirmat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1553
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_83c4dcc7:

    # "More than a little bemused, I look to Akira. She grins and shrugs, obviously taking some enjoyment out of her partner's deductions."
    "Més que desconcertat, miro cap a l'Akira. Somriu i arronsa les espatlles, es nota que està gaudint de la deducció del seu company."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1555
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_89ead067:

    # "He's sharp, yes, but more than a little unsympathetic. Logical, but lacking in tact. His attitude reminds me of Shizune, in a way, as do his looks."
    "És llest, sí, però també força insensible. Racional, però sense tacte. La seva actitud em recorda a la Shizune, segons com, també la seva aparença."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1560
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_cd7431a3:

    # hh "May I ask why you're staring at me? Surely I'm not that unusual a specimen."
    hh "Em podries dir per què em mires tan fixament? No crec ser un espècimen tan interessant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1562
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0a13c00d:

    # "Does he not know how unusual he looks? I could overlook the spats and clothing as just being coincidental, but the ribbon in his hair really is too much."
    "És que no sap que té una aparença singular? Podria passar per alt les postes i la roba com si fossin només una coincidència, però la cinta que porta els cabells realment és massa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1564
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6ab30047:

    # "This is entirely beside the point, though."
    "Tanmateix, això està totalment fora de lloc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1566
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_72265436:

    # hi "Sorry. You just remind me of someone."
    hi "Perdona. M'has recordat a algú."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1574
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8f5f45aa:

    # "Akira gives him a sharp jab with her elbow."
    "L'Akira li dona un cop fort amb el colze."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1579
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a2dfc8f0:

    # aki "Told ya you're not that much different from her."
    aki "Ja t'he dit que tu i ella us assembleu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1584
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_371061d5:

    # "He coughs into his hand to try and maintain an upright and serious demeanor."
    "Tus, tapant-se la boca a la mà, per intentar mantenir un aire íntegre i seriós."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1586
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_47898324:

    # hh "I see you've met my sister, then. Perhaps my full name might help you."
    hh "Veig que has conegut a la meva germana. Potser el meu nom complet t'ajudarà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1591
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d4db36c5:

    # hh "I am Hideaki Hakamichi. You are probably thinking of my sister, Shizune Hakamichi."
    hh "Em dic Hideaki Hakamichi. Segurament pensaves en la meva germana, la Shizune Hakamichi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1593
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_33038178:

    # "Oh, so he's Shizune's brother."
    "Així que és el germà de la Shizune."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1595
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2bc840dd:

    # "Wait a minute, if Hideaki is the son of Akira's uncle, and Shizune is his sister, then that means Lilly and Shizune's fathers are brothers-in-law. Therefore…"
    "Espera un moment, si en Hideaki és el fill de l'oncle d'Akira, i la Shizune és la seva germana, llavors això significa que els pares de la Lilly i la Shizune són cunyats. Per tant..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1597
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_155b2ea6:

    # hi "Lilly and Shizune are first cousins?"
    hi "La Lilly i la Shizune son cosines primeres?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1603
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9072231d:

    # "Lilly groans in an uncharacteristically unrestrained manner. The reaction earns an amused smirk from her sister."
    "La Lilly es queixa d'una manera poc habitual i sense restriccions. La reacció es guanya un somriure divertit de la seva germana."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1605
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1ab62561:

    # "The enmity between the two just took on another meaning. I had thought it simply a matter of difficulty of communication between the two, but a family feud makes things much more complicated."
    "L'enemistat entre les dues acaba d'adquirir un altre significat. Havia pensat que només era una qüestió de dificultat de comunicació entre elles, però una disputa familiar complica molt més les coses."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1610
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9b2d3286:

    # aki "You can choose your friends, but you can't choose your family."
    aki "Pots triar els teus amics, però no pots triar la teva família."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1615
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b030a829:

    # "She gives a halfhearted shrug. She mustn't give as much weight to the two's conflict as I do."
    "Encongeix les espatlles poc convençuda. No deu donar tant de pes al conflicte entre elles dues com jo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1620
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e22ef6d2:

    # aki "Well, that's how it is. What're you two up to anyway on this fine day?"
    aki "Bé, així són les coses. Què esteu fent vosaltres dos un bon dia com avui?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1625
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_28a39847:

    # li "We're shopping for Hanako's birthday present. The day will be coming up soon, so this is the last chance we'll have before school starts again for the week."
    li "Estem comprant un regal per l'aniversari de la Hanako. Queda poc, així que aquesta era l'última oportunitat que teníem abans que tornin a començar les classes de la setmana."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1632
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ebf788df:

    # "Akira makes a strange face, as if Lilly had just said that the sky wasn't blue and the clouds not white."
    "L'Akira fa una cara estranya, com si la Lilly hagués dit que el cel no era blau i els núvols no eren blancs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1634
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4244b400:

    # aki "Isn't her birthday on the tenth next month?"
    aki "El seu aniversari no és el deu del mes que ve?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1639
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3d074483:

    # li "Yes… Why? Is something wrong?"
    li "Si... Per què? Passa alguna cosa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1644
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6f2f584e:

    # "Akira's face seems to collapse. It's an utterly unbefitting expression for someone so rowdy and headstrong."
    "Sembla que a l'Akira se li desfà la cara. És una expressió completament inapropiada per a algú tan batusser i amb tossut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1646
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6c2d90fc:

    # aki "The folks didn't call you yet?"
    aki "Encara no t'ha trucat la família?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1652
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5170bb10:

    # "As Lilly shakes her head cluelessly, I look at Hideaki to see if he knows anything about this. A simple shrug is his only answer."
    "Mentre la Lilly nega amb el cap sense tenir-ne ni idea, miro a Hideaki per veure si sap res d'això. Només em respon arronsant les espatlles."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1657
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_379905b2:

    # "For a moment, Akira ponders what to do before smiling once again. The fact that she can hide her emotions so quickly and effectively is unsettling."
    "Per un moment, l'Akira reflexiona sobre què fer abans de tornar a somriure. El fet que pugui amagar les seves emocions tan ràpidament i eficaçment és inquietant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1662
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_48bbd4d2:

    # aki "Hey Shortie, sorry, but could you hang with Hisao for a while?"
    aki "Ei, Napbuf, perdona, podries fer companyia a en Hisao un moment?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1687
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_db7dc41b:

    # "He nods and waves her off, Akira placing an arm on Lilly's shoulder as she guides her away and out of earshot."
    "Assenteix i li fa adeu, l'Akira col·loca un braç a l'espatlla de la Lilly mentre la guia prou lluny perquè no les puguem sentir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1689
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_11657e51:

    # "And so, I'm alone with 'Shortie.'"
    "I, per tant, estic sol amb el 'Napbuf'."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1691
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f481691a:

    # hi "So… nice weather, isn't it?"
    hi "Ja... quin bon dia, eh?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1696
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9daf9b5a:

    # hh "It seems so."
    hh "Això sembla."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1698
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1700
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_954125ef:

    # hi "I guess they dumped us."
    hi "Sembla que ens han deixat a l'estacada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1705
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ded14347:

    # hh "Indeed."
    hh "Efectivament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1707
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_62e2292f:

    # "What a farcical attempt at smalltalk. I've got no idea of how to talk to this guy, and his robotic responses aren't helping. Blood and a stone come to mind."
    "Quin intent més absurd de dir alguna cosa. No tinc ni idea de com parlar amb aquest paio, i les seves respostes robòtiques no m'ajuden. D'on no n'hi ha, no en raja."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1712
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8ac32134:

    # "Without another word, he begins to rock on his feet in an obvious gesture of boredom with this discussion. He really is like a little kid, despite his serious demeanor."
    "Sense dir res més, comença a balancejar-se sobre els seus peus en un gest obvi que l'avorreix aquesta discussió. Realment és com un nen petit, tot i el seu tarannà seriós."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1714
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bb4883ea:

    # "Suspecting the conversation over, I decide to accomplish what I came here to do in the first place."
    "Suposant que s'ha acabat la conversa, decideixo fer allò que he vingut a fer aquí en primer lloc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1716
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3b1057b5:

    # hi "I'm going to go search for a present. Coming?"
    hi "Aniré a buscar un regal. Vols venir?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1721
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d6792514:

    # hh "Not much else to do."
    hh "Tampoc tinc res més a fer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1731
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8f5e6aef:

    # "In a little while, we come to a small shop beside a convenience store."
    "En poc temps, arribem a una botigueta al costat d'una botiga de conveniència."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1733
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3f512ad9:

    # "For once the store windows aren't filled with electronics and computer games, but dolls, stuffed bears and all manners of wood-crafted oddities."
    "Per primera vegada, els aparadors de la botiga no estan plens d'aparells electrònics i jocs d'ordinador, sinó de nines, ossos de peluix i tota mena de curiositats fetes amb fusta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1735
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_fd9b9669:

    # hi "Othello's… Antiques?"
    hi "Antiquari... Otel·lo?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1737
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_84e7a8b2:

    # "An antique store? Well, if there's anything in this town that'd suit Hanako, I guess it'd be here."
    "Un antiquari? Bé, si hi ha alguna cosa en aquest poble que li pugui agradar a la Hanako, suposo que seria aquí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1739
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_db1fc8a4:

    # "I reach for the old-looking door handle, but pull back at the last minute as I realize my companion's gone adrift."
    "Arribo a la maneta de la porta d'aspecte antic, però retrocedeixo a l'últim minut mentre m'adono que el meu company s'ha separat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1741
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bc2e718f:

    # hi "Not coming in?"
    hi "No vens?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1746
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5ea57e38:

    # hh "I'll just be in the newsstand for a while. Don't mind me."
    hh "Aniré una estona al quiosc. Fes sense mi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1748
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_da9da446:

    # "His voice makes it painfully clear he has zero interest in what's in the store, and that he doesn't feel obligated to follow me."
    "La seva veu deixa tristament clar que no té gens d'interès en allò que hi ha a la botiga, i que no se sent obligat a seguir-me."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1753
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b34262a8:

    # "As he wanders off without another word, I push the thick wooden door and enter the store, a bell above me ringing out."
    "Mentre se'n va deambulant sense dir res més, empenyo la porta gruixuda de fusta i entro a la botiga, mentre la campana sona a damunt meu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1765
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_79b75b17:

    # "The musty smell of old books and wooden shelves is distinctly anachronistic."
    "L'olor de resclosit dels llibres vells i les prestatgeries de fusta és clarament anacrònica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1767
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6a347470:

    # "I look to the counter beside the door. The graying man behind it sits there silently, reading a tattered book. He certainly fits the look of the place."
    "Miro al taulell que hi ha al costat de la porta. L'home gris hi seu darrere en silenci, llegint un llibre atrotinat. Sens dubte, s'adapta a l'aspecte del lloc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1769
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_85c776b6:

    # "Slowly wandering through the aisles, the person I'm reminded of as I inspect each handcrafted or imported oddity in turn isn't Hanako."
    "Mentre passejo lentament pels passadissos, la persona que em ve al cap mentre inspecciono cada la curiositat artesanal o importada de torn no és la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1771
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8a2dc293:

    # "Crouching down, I examine the ancient oak desk inside the shop window."
    "Ajupit, examino l'antiga taula de roure que hi ha dins de l'aparador."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1773
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1e22bbf7:

    # "At least thirty dolls, all varying wildly in size and make. The only similarity between them is the long Victorian dresses they wear."
    "Com a mínim trenta nines, totes de diferents grandàries i fabricació. L'única similitud entre elles són els vestits llargs victorians que porten."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1775
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8f3d3b31:

    # "I turn the price tag of one that looks to be about waist-height."
    "Dono la volta a l'etiqueta d'una que sembla arribar-me a la cintura."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1777
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e225602e:

    # "…It's not in my price bracket. At all."
    "... Està fora del meu preu. Totalment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1779
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a308c340:

    # "I do the same to each of them, getting more and more depressed as they get smaller and smaller in size."
    "Faig el mateix amb cadascuna d'elles, cada vegada em deprimeixo més a mesura que es fan més i més petites."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1781
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2844e042:

    # "That is, until I reach the very smallest one. It's affordable, just, yet of quality make and with long, auburn hair and a little blue dress."
    "Fins que arribo a la més petita. Me la puc permetre, pels pèls, però és de qualitat i té els cabells llargs i d'un castany rogenc, amb un vestit blau clar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1783
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_27089efa:

    # "I decide that it's the kind of present Hanako would appreciate. Pretty-looking, and far from gaudy."
    "Decideixo que és el tipus de regal que la Hanako agrairia. Bufó i no gens llampant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1785
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4560730c:

    # "After I carefully pick it up, I decide to keep looking around the store. I'm not sure whether it's because I like the atmosphere or out of simple curiosity."
    "Després d'agafar-lo amb cura, decideixo seguir mirant per la botiga. No estic segur de si és perquè m'agrada l'atmosfera o per simple curiositat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1791
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d5d7fefc:

    # "Peeking around the corner before I go to the next aisle, I see that the shelves in this one are stocked with wooden toys; from toy cars to intricate automatons."
    "Miro de cua d'ull abans de passar al següent passadís, i veig que les prestatgeries estan plenes de joguines de fusta; des de cotxes de joguina fins a autòmats enrevessats."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1801
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ea1dc45e:

    # "Tucked behind a line of nutcrackers, I notice a little plain wooden box. It feels surprisingly light as I pick it up with my free hand."
    "Entaforada darrere d'una línia de trencanous, veig una capseta senzilla de fusta. Em sembla sorprenentment lleugera quan l'agafo amb la meva mà lliure."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1808
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_aadc0a52:

    # "The lid only needs the smallest movement to pop open, the little metal drum inside beginning to rotate immediately."
    "La tapa només necessita un petit moviment per obrir-se, i el petit tambor metàl·lic de l'interior comença a girar immediatament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1810
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_006c5945:

    # "For seconds on end, I simply stand there listening to the palm-sized melody."
    "Durant una estona, em quedo dret aquí escoltant la melodia que em cap al palmell de la mà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1812
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b9d60217:

    # "As it plays, I take the tiny price tag in my fingers and bring it up to my face, the minuscule cursive writing taking some effort to read."
    "Mentre sona, agafo la minúscula etiqueta de preu amb els dits i me l'apropo a la cara, m'esforço a llegir la minúscula escriptura cursiva."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1814
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_303959a8:

    # "It's affordable… sort of."
    "Me la puc permetre... més o menys."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1829
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6fde37da:

    # "Grimacing slightly, I close the lid and make my way to the counter with doll and music box in hand."
    "Faig una ganyota, tanco la tapa i faig camí cap al taulell amb la nina i la capseta de música a la mà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1834
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2ec76fa4:

    # "When I lay the two on the counter, the man behind it sits up and takes stock of them. He doesn't hide very well his surprise at someone of my age buying them."
    "Quan els poso al taulell, l'home que hi ha darrere es posa dret i en pren nota. No s'amaga gaire bé la sorpresa que algú de la meva edat els compri."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1839
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d345232c:

    # "It's painful, but I hand over the money for the two and leave the store with a small opaque bag in hand."
    "Em fa mal, però li dono els diners per les dues coses i deixo la botiga amb una petita bossa opaca a la mà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1847
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_51933500:

    # "Hideaki being there takes me by surprise."
    "Que en Hideaki sigui allà em sorprèn."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1849
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_23ae9c24:

    # hi "Oh… hi. I thought you'd be at the newsstand."
    hi "Ei... hola. Pensava que series al quiosc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1854
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_229b96ec:

    # hh "Akira gave me a call. She's waiting for us at the fountain with Lilly."
    hh "L'Akira em fa un truc. Ens espera a la font amb la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1856
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2eeb71d8:

    # "At least that solves the issue of trying to find them again."
    "Almenys això resol la qüestió d'intentar trobar-nos de nou."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1863
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8ae97e74:

    # "We head off back to the fountain. Hideaki's immaculate posture and presentation despite his appearance makes for a strange contrast even as we walk."
    "Tornem a la font. La postura i aspecte irreprotxables d'en Hideaki, malgrat la seva aparença, fan que el contrast sigui estrany fins i tot mentre caminem."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1869
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a6c744aa:

    # "Lilly and Akira stand there waiting for us, their faces hard to read."
    "La Lilly i l'Akira estan allà esperant-nos, les seves cares són difícils de llegir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1874
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e1001b81:

    # aki "Hey. You ready to go, Shortie?"
    aki "Ei. Preparat per marxar, Napbuf?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1885
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_7b4f51dd:

    # "Hideaki's mood seems to improve as he rejoins her."
    "L'estat d'ànim d'en Hideaki sembla millorar quan es reuneixen."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1890
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bbad04d9:

    # aki "Seeya Lilly, Hisao. Tell Hanako I said happy birthday."
    aki "Ens veiem Lilly, Hisao. Feliciteu la Hanako de part meva."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1892
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bedf77ab:

    # hi "We will. Bye."
    hi "Ho farem. Adeu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1897
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_6e80cf90:

    # li "Goodbye, Akira."
    li "Que vagi bé, Akira."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1908
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9c56ca77:

    # "And with that, the two disappear into the fracas of the afternoon city crowd."
    "I amb això, tots dos desapareixen amb el sarau vespertí de la gentada que hi ha a la ciutat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1910
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e637660c:

    # "Turning to Lilly, I notice she's carrying a small bag. It's now that I realize why her disposition felt different from before; while Lilly's typically the type to wear her emotions on her sleeve, her expression and tone are clouded and difficult to read."
    "Em giro cap a la Lilly, veig que porta una bosseta. Ara entenc per què el seu tarannà sembla diferent d'abans; si bé la Lilly sol ser de les que mostra les emocions a flor de pell, la seva expressió i el seu to són tèrbols i difícils de llegir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1912
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ed6384c5:

    # "It's more than a little off-putting, but given the effort she's making to hide her emotions, I doubt she wants to be cornered on why she's feeling this way."
    "És més que desconcertant, però tenint en compte l'esforç que està fent per amagar les seves emocions, dubto que vulgui que l'acorrali amb el perquè se sent així."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1914
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9165163c:

    # hi "Already bought Hanako a present?"
    hi "Ja has comprat un regal a la Hanako?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1919
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ca17ea7a:

    # li "Yes. Have you?"
    li "Sí. I tu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1921
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_142d50b9:

    # hi "Yeah."
    hi "També."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1926
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_562f741f:

    # li "Shall we head back to the bus stop then?"
    li "Tornem a la parada d'autobusos?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1928
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_fe16565f:

    # hi "Okay. There should be a bus back to Yamaku pretty soon."
    hi "D'acord. Hi deu haver un bus cap al Yamaku aviat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1930
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_590225ec:

    # "And with that, we begin to walk."
    "I així, comencem a caminar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1938
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_dea4a049:

    # "It feels strange compared to before. Lilly's hand on my forearm feels unusually tense, and the whole atmosphere is extraordinarily awkward."
    "Se'm fa estrany comparat amb abans. Sento la mà de la Lilly a l'avantbraç especialment tensa, i tota l'atmosfera és extraordinàriament incòmoda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1940
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e0dd01e8:

    # "The silence continues for a long while. I really don't like seeing her like this."
    "El silenci continua durant molt de temps. Realment no m'agrada veure-la així."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1945
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_03707b21:

    # li "Hanako's birthday party is going to have to be held earlier. Is the fourth going to be all right for you?"
    li "Haurem de celebrar la festa d'aniversari de Hanako abans. El quatre t'aniria bé a tu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1947
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8d946768:

    # "I have no other possible obligations anyway, so I reflexively nod. Only afterwards do I remember that doing so is pointless, and quickly answer so by speech."
    "De totes maneres, no tinc altres possibles obligacions, així que assenteixo reflexivament. Només després recordo que fer-ho és inútil i responc ràpidament amb la veu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1949
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ecbc1783:

    # "She tries to collect herself, a task that looks almost pitiable in how plain it is to see how distant her thoughts are."
    "Intenta refer-se, una tasca que sembla gairebé lamentable per com és d'evident veure que lluny estan els seus pensaments."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1954
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ce32458c:

    # li "Sorry, Hisao. You said the bus would be coming soon, right?"
    li "Perdona, Hisao. Has dit que l'autobús arribarà aviat, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1956
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0535be30:

    # hi "That's right."
    hi "Així és."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1958
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d7babee2:

    # "But now that she says that, I have an idea."
    "Però ara que ho diu, tinc una idea."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1960
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_66c80454:

    # hi "Actually, do you have anything to do later today?"
    hi "De fet, has de fer alguna cosa després?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1965
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_f67f3e1f:

    # li "I… don't believe so. Why do you ask?"
    li "No... ho crec. per què preguntes?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1967
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_bb8b3ad5:

    # hi "This is the point where I'd normally take your hand and rush you somewhere, but even without that, you'll have to trust me. Okay?"
    hi "Aquest és el moment en què en teoria t'agafo la mà i ens precipitaríem fins a algun lloc, però fins i tot sense fer-ho, hauràs de confiar en mi. D'acord?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1972
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_ee151d4e:

    # "I take her hand and gently lead her on, her distant face replaced by one of mild surprise and curiosity."
    "Li agafo la mà i la guio suaument, canvia la cara absent per una lleugerament sorpresa i curiosa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1982
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4a17895c:

    # "As the waitress sets the cup of tea and cup of coffee that I'd ordered onto the table, I thank her before she takes her leave."
    "Quan la cambrera acaba de posar la tassa de te i la de cafè que hem demanat sobre la taula, li dono les gràcies abans que se'n vagi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1984
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_77091fb6:

    # "Truth be told, I really lucked out in finding this café. I didn't really know where I was going, rather I was just looking for any café that looked relatively nice."
    "La veritat és que havia tingut sort de trobar aquest cafè. Realment no sabia on anava, només buscava una cafeteria que semblés poc o molt agradable."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1986
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_abb48791:

    # "Having managed to recover a little, Lilly tentatively sips at her cup as I take a long gulp of the coffee in front of me."
    "Després d'haver aconseguit recuperar-se una mica, la Lilly veu amb compte de la seva tassa mentre bec grans glops del cafè que tinc davant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1988
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_29acdac3:

    # "As I hoped, her face lights up as she realizes what flavor it is."
    "Com esperava, la seva cara s'il·lumina a mesura que s'adona de quin sabor és."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1994
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_22d5a471:

    # li "Ah… this is wonderful!"
    li "Ah... és meravellós!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:1999
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e265768f:

    # li "Hisao, how did you know that this was…?"
    li "Hisao, com sabies que aquest era...?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2001
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3b897709:

    # "I'd asked for French vanilla black tea, hedging my bets that it would be her favorite flavor, or at least one she liked. While I don't really know much about tea, it sounded like one she might appreciate."
    "He demanat te negre francès amb vainilla, fent les meves apostes perquè fos el seu sabor preferit, o almenys un que li agradés. Tot i que no sé gaire sobre tes, m'ha semblat que li podria agradar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2003
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a8829ee8:

    # "…on the basis of her liking vanilla ice cream. A tea connoisseur I am definitely not."
    "... basant-me en el seu gelat de vainilla. Sens dubte, no soc un gran entès dels tes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2005
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2d964f9a:

    # hi "It was a lucky guess. You really like tea, don't you?"
    hi "He tingut sort. Realment t'agrada el te, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2010
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b1345a5b:

    # "She puts her teacup down and gives a tiny nod, that familiar small smile thankfully perched on her face once again."
    "Deixa la tassa i fa un lleu cop de cap, amb aquesta rialleta familiar que afortunadament se li torna a posar a la cara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2015
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_12e9cf41:

    # li "Drinking tea is… calming, I think."
    li "Beure te... em calma, crec."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2017
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_51e7b0cc:

    # hi "With the amount you drink, are you sure you're not addicted to it? Caffeine addiction's pretty common nowadays."
    hi "Amb el munt de te que beus, n'estàs segura que no ets addicte? És força comú tenir addicció a la cafeïna avui dia."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2022
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b30e208a:

    # li "Did I ever say I wasn't?"
    li "Mai he dit que no ho fos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2024
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_936dff74:

    # "She lets out a giggle as my head drops. We all have our vices, I suppose, and there are worse things to be addicted to."
    "Deixa anar una rialleta mentre abaixo el cap. Tots tenim els nostres vicis, suposo, i hi ha coses pitjors a les quals ser addicte."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2026
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_2e070d24:

    # hi "French vanilla black tea, huh? I'll have to remember that."
    hi "Així que te negre francès amb vainilla, eh? Ho hauré de recordar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2031
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_71e1f370:

    # "For a while, we both silently drink. It's comforting to have someone like her nearby in such new surroundings, even if it's just the two of us sitting in silence."
    "Durant una estona, tots dos bevem en silenci. És reconfortant tenir-la a prop en un entorn nou com aquest, encara que només estiguem tots dos asseguts en silenci."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2033
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5536af7b:

    # "I begin to wonder if this feeling is the same for her, until she sets down her cup."
    "Començo a preguntar-me si ella sent el mateix, fins que deixa la tassa sobre la taula."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2038
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0ff494cf:

    # li "Hisao, do you mind if I ask you a slightly odd question?"
    li "Hisao, et fa res si et faig una pregunta una mica estranya?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2040
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a4af47e0:

    # hi "That depends on the question, I guess."
    hi "Depèn de la pregunta, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2045
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_3aeabe83:

    # li "I was wondering… what your favorite color is. Everyone has one, after all."
    li "Em preguntava... quin és el teu color preferit. Ben mirat, tothom en té un."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2047
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4856898d:

    # "I almost reply before realizing why the seemingly mundane question is actually quite strange."
    "Gairebé contesto abans d'adonar-me de per què una pregunta aparentment banal de fet és força estranya."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2049
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_62925a18:

    # hi "My favorite color? But…"
    hi "El meu color preferit? Però..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2054
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_5a56accf:

    # "She gives a pouting look, wanting me to answer anyway. While the answer seems unavoidably wasted on her, there isn't any harm in giving it."
    "Fa mala cara, vol que respongui de totes maneres. Encara que la resposta sembla inevitablement inútil per ella, no té res de dolent que li doni."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2056
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_08acb58c:

    # hi "I've always had a thing for green. I'd say that's my favorite."
    hi "Sempre m'ha agradat el verd. Diria que és el meu preferit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2061
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_53ffc04a:

    # li "Green, is it? What things do you think of when contemplating that color?"
    li "Així que el verd? En què penses quan t'imagines aquest color?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2063
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a7cc9ef5:

    # hi "I suppose… grass fields and trees in summer. The Army as well, with camouflage."
    hi "Suposo que... prats vers i arbres a l'estiu. També l'exèrcit, amb el camuflatge."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2068
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_897f2eef:

    # li "Men always seem to like the military."
    li "Als homes sempre sembla que us agrada tot això militar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2073
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_a407c4e6:

    # li "But… that sounds like a nice color. A very nice color."
    li "Però... sembla un color bonic. Molt bonic."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2075
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b9b05c8a:

    # "She nods her head a little, as if approving of the choice. Considering how foreign the concept of color is to her mind, labeling it by association seems reasonable enough."
    "Assenteix lleugerament, com si aprovés l'elecció. Considerant com d'exòtic ha de ser el concepte de color per ella, etiquetar-lo per associació sembla prou raonable."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2077
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_7ba99119:

    # hi "If everyone has a favorite color, then what's yours?"
    hi "Si tothom té un color preferit, quin és el teu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2082
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_42845ccf:

    # li "White. I'm told that's the color of snow, and of ice cream."
    li "Blanc. He sentit que és el color de la neu, i del gelat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2084
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4b68c477:

    # hi "You're no better than me then, if you only like that color because of a favorite food. I guess white is nice too, though."
    hi "Llavors, no ets millor que jo si només t'agrada aquest color pel teu menjar preferit. Tot i que crec que el blanc també és bonic."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2086
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d50fde3e:

    # hi "And speaking of colors, it'll be getting dark soon. Let me help you up."
    hi "Parlant de colors, aviat es farà fosc. Deixa'm que t'ajudi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2094
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_948e820f:

    # "Lilly offers her hand, which I take in mine to help lever her up from her seat at the table. Its softness compared to mine takes me off guard, as I'm really not used to such casual contact."
    "La Lilly m'ofereix la mà, que agafo amb la meva per ajudar-la a aixecar-se de la taula. La seva suavitat en comparació amb la meva m'agafa desprevingut, ja que no estic gaire acostumat al contacte tan casual."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2096
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_e794b1f3:

    # "It doesn't seem to bother her at all though. While it seems obvious why, it feels like just one more ladylike aspect to her."
    "Però no sembla molestar-la gens. Tot i que sembla obvi per què, sembla un aspecte femení més seu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2098
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_dab722c4:

    # "As her hand moves to her pocket, I quickly cut her off."
    "La freno de quan veig que mou la mà cap a la butxaca."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2100
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_9311fcda:

    # hi "Don't worry, I'll pay for this."
    hi "No et preocupis, jo pago."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2105
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_0bb57d0e:

    # li "Oh. Thank you, Hisao."
    li "Oh. Gràcies, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2107
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_75a98ac2:

    # "She gives an earnest smile at the gesture, a reward much greater than that of her words."
    "Dibuixa un somriure sincer pel meu gest, una recompensa molt més gran que les seves paraules."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2117
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_034dcd61:

    # "By the time we step off the bus, it's well and truly dark."
    "Quan baixem de l'autobús, és molt fosc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2124
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_4e3e8f00:

    # "We make our way up the hill in silence, both of us behaving a little awkwardly, probably because of the day's events."
    "Ens dirigim cap al turó en silenci, tots dos estem una mica incòmodes, probablement pel que ha passat el dia d'avui."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2126
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_387bbdd6:

    # "While I'm still concerned over Lilly's withdrawn nature after meeting with her sister, the fact I managed to cheer her up even slightly feels like a personal victory."
    "Encara continuo preocupat pel seu caràcter retret després de reunir-nos amb la seva germana, el fet que hagi aconseguit animar-la, encara que només fos una mica, el veig com una victòria personal."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2128
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_72ab849a:

    # "But… it feels like the air between us has changed. Maybe it's only a bit, but it's something I don't think either of us realized before."
    "Però... sembla que es respira un aire diferent entre nosaltres. Potser només és una mica, però és una cosa que no crec que cap dels dos s'hagi adonat abans."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2133
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_693720f8:

    # li "That was… a date, wasn't it?"
    li "Ha estat... una cita, no?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2135
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_8b8caef5:

    # "It was. That doesn't elude either of us, the question's answer being so self-evident as to be rhetorical."
    "Ho ha estat. Això no se'ns escapa a cap dels dos, la resposta a la pregunta és tan evident que sembla retòrica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2137
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_18a7bfe1:

    # "Awkward as it may be, I don't think this feeling is bad. In fact, quite the opposite. I don't know what it is, I certainly can't be sure, but it feels like something a little more than friendship."
    "Per estrany que sembli, no crec que aquesta sensació sigui dolenta. De fet, és tot el contrari. No sé ben bé què és, no n'estic segur, però sembla més que només amistat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2139
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_b07797a2:

    # "Understanding? Empathy? Searching for words to adequately describe it is difficult. Nonetheless…"
    "Complicitat? Empatia? És difícil trobar paraules per descriure-ho bé. No obstant això..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2141
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_d31b3ffc:

    # hi "Would you like do this again sometime, Lilly? Without shopping for presents?"
    hi "T'agradaria tornar-ho a fer, Lilly? Sense haver de comprar regals?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2146
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_1eceff28:

    # "The tentative question is met with the same look from Lilly as before. Her pale skin makes the rosy tint of her cheeks just slightly more noticeable and her face, though still pointed to the street ahead of her, lowers. Just a little."
    "La Lilly respon a la tímida pregunta amb la mateixa mirada que abans. La seva pell pàl·lida fa que el tint rosat de les seves galtes es noti més i la seva cara, tot i que segueix apuntant cap al carrer, s'abaixa. Només una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2151
translate ca a2_lilly_presents_and_presence_595c3d64:

    # li "…Okay."
    li "... D'acord"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2169
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_68e52ddb:

    # "I walk down the hall of the girls' dormitories, my schoolbag in hand."
    "Baixo pel passadís dels dormitoris de noies, amb la bossa de l'escola a la mà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2171
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fe917c86:

    # "A doll lies inside, carefully placed on top of a small box. I've been carrying the box in there for a while now, still not sure of what to do with it."
    "Dins hi ha una nina, col·locada amb cura sobre d'una capseta. Fa temps que hi porto la capsa allà dins, encara no sé què fer amb ella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2173
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2d4a5a3e:

    # "This whole situation, come to think of it, is bizarre."
    "Tota aquesta situació, si hi penso, és ben estranya."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2175
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c0a8fa50:

    # "While I've known of Hanako's upcoming birthday party for a while now, I had no idea of exactly what the celebrations would be until I found a single note left in the abandoned tea room earlier today."
    "Encara que feia temps que sabia que hi hauria una festa d'aniversari per la Hanako, no tenia ni idea de com serien exactament les celebracions fins que avui he trobat una nota a la sala de te buida."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2177
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_962f26b0:

    # "I hold it up and read it again, doublechecking the instructions. The plain black handwriting's fairly legible despite Lilly's blindness, clearly thanks to considerable effort and care."
    "L'aguanto i la torno a llegir, tornant a comprovar les instruccions. L'escriptura negra és força llegible malgrat la ceguesa de Lilly, clarament gràcies a un esforç i una cura considerables."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2181
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c1ddb7fb:

    # "Not reassured, I continue walking down the hallway until I reach Lilly's dormitory room. I hesitate for a second, but eventually give three sharp taps on the door."
    "Sense confiança, segueixo caminant pel passadís fins a arribar al dormitori de la Lilly. Dubto un segon, però finalment dono tres cops secs a la porta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2187
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_01d246e5:

    # "A brief and muffled exchange of words can be heard from the other side. Listening closer, I can just pick out Hanako and Lilly's voices."
    "S'escolta un breu i confús intercanvi de paraules a l'altre costat. Quan l'escolto de més a prop, puc distingir les veus de la Hanako i la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2189
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b59589d4:

    # "As they finish, Lilly calls out."
    "Quan acaben, la Lilly em crida."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2191
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5056f26f:

    # li "Might that be Hisao?"
    li "Que ets en Hisao?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2193
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_139514f9:

    # hi "Yep. I got the note you left for me."
    hi "Sí. He llegit la nota que m'has deixat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2195
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fc11b9b1:

    # li "You can come in, the door is unlocked."
    li "Pots entrar, la porta està oberta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2197
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a7b95d2b:

    # "Glad that I managed to get the right room, I press down on the handle and let myself in."
    "M'alegro d'haver trobat l'habitació adequada, baixo la maneta i entro."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2201
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a95d169d:

    # "As the door swings open, my greeting to them is stolen from my mouth."
    "Quan la porta s'obre, em treuen la salutació de la boca."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2211
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_55426388:

    # "Lilly sits at a low table in the center of the room in her pajamas, while on the other side sits Hanako in a nightgown. Being dressed in only my normal school clothes, I feel quite out of place."
    "La Lilly seu en pijama en una taula baixa al centre de l'habitació, mentre que a l'altre costat hi seu la Hanako en una camisa de dormir. Vaig vestit amb roba normal de l'escola, i em sento bastant fora de lloc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2213
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d9dd8877:

    # "I steal a quick glance at the lovely sight of the two, my eyes tearing themselves from Lilly's long, thin and pale legs only with a measure of reluctance."
    "Faig un cop d'ull ràpid a l'adorable imatge de les dues, aparto els ulls de les cames llargues, fines i pàl·lides de la Lilly amb certa reticència."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2215
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d8f9b4b8:

    # hi "H-hi. I… think I brought everything that was needed."
    hi "E-ei. Crec... que he portat tot el que necessitàvem."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2222
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d0796007:

    # "She smiles and nods. I wonder if she's even aware of the pleasant sight she makes. The thin dark blue silk of her pajamas really suits her, accentuating both her eyes and her curves."
    "Somriu i assenteix. Em pregunto si és conscient que agradable és de veure. Realment li queda bé aquest pijama de seda de color blau fosc, li accentua tant els ulls com les corbes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2224
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8e422385:

    # "The look of her last night, that tentative and almost shy demeanor, seems all but replaced by her coy nature. It's nice to see her confidence returned, though I can't help casting my mind back to how she looked back then."
    "El seu aspecte la nit anterior, aquell aire indecís quasi tímid, sembla totalment substituït per la seva naturalesa coqueta. M'agrada veure que torna a tenir confiança, tot i que no puc evitar tornar a pensar en el seu aspecte de llavors."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2231
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ad727bdb:

    # "I look to Hanako, who nervously sits opposite her in her gown. It isn't a surprise that she'd wear something so conservative, though it definitely looks cute."
    "Miro a la Hanako, que s'asseu nerviosament davant d'ella amb el vestit. No em sorprèn que porti una cosa tan conservadora, tot i que sense cap dubte li queda bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2233
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_03ef6630:

    # hi "Hi, Hanako. Happy birthday."
    hi "Ei, Hanako. Per molts anys!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2235
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3158b324:

    # ha "Ah… th-thank you."
    ha "Ah... gr-gràcies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2237
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_00df23f1:

    # "She's unusually skittish, despite the fact that she's warmed up to me considerably over the weeks we've come to know each other. This is a pretty unusual situation, I guess."
    "Està més espantadissa del normal, tot i que durant aquestes setmanes m'ha començat a agafar més simpatia. És una situació bastant inusual, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2242
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_66d11420:

    # li "Feel free to take a seat, Hisao. I'll just pour you two some tea."
    li "Pots seure on vulguis, Hisao. Ara us serviré una mica de te."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2244
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_0527a675:

    # hi "Sure thing."
    hi "És clar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2251
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_90daa391:

    # "Lilly takes the steaming red teapot from the side of the table and gently pours its contents into our teacups as I take a seat beside them, setting my bag against the nearby wall."
    "La Lilly agafa la tetera vermella que fumeja a un costat de la taula, i n'aboca, suaument, el contingut a les nostres tasses mentre m'assec al seu costat, i deixo la bossa contra la paret més propera."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2253
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_0c5bfc12:

    # "With my senses returned and hormones somewhat calmer, I realize that this is the first time I've ever been in Lilly's room."
    "He recuperat els sentits i les hormones se m'han calmat, m'adono que és la primera vegada que estic a l'habitació de la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2255
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_827e071d:

    # "The first thing I notice is the ambient smell, just slightly different from that in mine… probably faint perfume, or nail polish. It could be anything of a girl's, really."
    "El primer que noto és l'olor de l'ambient, lleugerament diferent de la meva... deuen ser les restes d'un perfum o d'esmalt d'ungles. Podria ser qualsevol cosa de noies, de fet."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2257
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3eb3cd63:

    # "Another is the plain nature of the room, visually. Beige walls, a smart yet unadorned cabinet, the lack of posters or wall hangings. It's distinctly utilitarian, something I should have anticipated given her blindness."
    "Una altra és la senzillesa visual de l'habitació. Parets de beix, un armari elegant però sense adorns, sense cartells ni res penjat a la paret. És clarament funcional, cosa que hauria d'haver previst tenint en compte la seva ceguesa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2259
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9a5dfeb6:

    # "The only thing that really seems out of the ordinary is several piles of books sitting on the floor, each reaching from roughly knee height to waist height. Some of them have printed titles, others are entirely blank except for dots of Braille."
    "L'única cosa que realment sembla fora del normal és els munts de llibres a terra, que arriben des de l'alçada dels genolls a l'alçada de la cintura. Alguns tenen el títol imprès, altres estan totalment en blanc excepte els punts escrits en braille."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2261
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c6a8a73a:

    # "The fact that the ones with printed titles are uniformly in English is interesting, though not completely unexpected. She did mention her parents impressing the language upon her and Akira, after all."
    "El fet que aquells que tenen títols impresos siguin en anglès és interessant, encara que no del tot inesperat. Ben mirat, va dir que els seus pares volien transmetre'ls la llengua a ella i l'Akira."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2263
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_62e8bb22:

    # hi "Your room looks nice, Lilly."
    hi "Quina habitació més bonica, Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2270
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d6f065cd:

    # "I hear a call of thanks from beside my shoulder. Looking back to Hanako, her gaze is fixed on her lap and her hands are nervously clutching her gown."
    "Sento que em dona les gràcies des del costat de la meva espatlla. Miro cap a la Hanako, la seva mirada clavada a la falda i amb les mans agafades nerviosament al vestit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2272
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2278cbd8:

    # "It's now that I notice why. With these clothes on, the extent of her scarring is far more visible; reaching down her neck and out to cover her right shoulder."
    "Ara entenc el perquè. Amb aquesta roba posada, l'abast de les cicatrius és molt més visible; s'estenen pel coll i arriben a cobrir-li l'espatlla dreta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2274
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_dc49cb38:

    # "Considering this is a party for her, she doesn't really look like she's enjoying the experience now that I'm here."
    "Si considerem que aquesta és la seva festa, no sembla gaudir gaire de l'experiència ara que soc aquí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2276
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_7ae4585f:

    # hi "So how old are you turning? Eighteen?"
    hi "Quants anys fas? Divuit?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2281
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_86e6325d:

    # "Her look of surprise, not at all helped by her total lack of skill at hiding her feelings, shows that she was trying to mentally tune me out. This is really quite awkward."
    "El seu posat de sorpresa, destacat per la seva poca habilitat per amagar els sentiments, demostra que estava intentant desconnectar. Això em fa sentir realment incòmode."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2283
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_13b7ab07:

    # ha "Y-yes."
    ha "S-sí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2285
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9ead570a:

    # hi "On the plus side, there's only two more years till you can drink. So who's older? You or Lilly?"
    hi "Si ho mirem pel costat positiu, només falten dos anys perquè puguis beure alcohol. I qui és més gran? Tu o la Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2290
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fdf2a662:

    # ha "Lilly. She had her birthday in… F-February. What about… yours?"
    ha "La Lilly. El seu aniversari va ser el... f-febrer. Què n'hi ha del... teu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2292
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2f1e18bc:

    # hi "Earlier this year, so it's already passed."
    hi "A principis d'aquest any, així que ja ha passat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2294
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_86a57921:

    # "Unstated is that it passed while I was stuck in the hospital. That was… a particularly low point of the experience."
    "No dic que va passar mentre encara estava a l'hospital. Aquell va ser... un moment especialment baix de l'experiència."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2312
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_cc32dd9f:

    # "Conversation with her dries up as quickly as expected. It isn't long before Lilly's finished preparing our drinks, setting down the three teacups in front of us."
    "La conversa se'ns acaba tan ràpid com era d'esperar. La Lilly no triga gaire a acabar de preparar les nostres begudes, i ens posa les tres tasses al davant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2314
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_18470a38:

    # "I pick mine up, immediately noticing a much stronger aroma and taste than the tea we've been having."
    "Agafo la meva, i de seguida noto una aroma i un sabor molt més intensos que el te que hem pres abans."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2316
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b2d2205b:

    # hi "Huh, it tastes different than the tea we have in school."
    hi "Oh, té un gust diferent del te que bevem a l'escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2321
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c4ab4262:

    # li "It's a different variety, rather than the kind we've been having there. You've never tasted Orange Jaipur before?"
    li "És una varietat diferent del tipus que hem estat prenent allà. Has provat mai el te de taronja de Jaipur?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2323
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a94411a6:

    # hi "Not… that I can remember. I usually drink coffee after all, like when we were in town. This is nice, though."
    hi "No... que jo recordi. De totes maneres, normalment prenc cafè, com quan vam anar a la ciutat. De totes maneres, està bo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2328
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_58ed2f38:

    # "As we settle down and sip, Hanako seems to become more relaxed, or at least a bit less tense about my presence."
    "Mentre ens posem còmodes i tot fent glops, la Hanako comença a relaxar-se, o ni que sigui a estar menys tensa amb meva presència."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2330
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_61e4a532:

    # "We all finish our cups at about the same time, with Hanako failing rather badly at hiding her anticipation for the cake that's sitting to the side, begging to be eaten."
    "Ens acabem el te a la vegada, i la Hanako no aconsegueix amagar la il·lusió pel pastís que hi ha a un costat, que demana ser menjat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2334
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_11b6b2dd:

    # "Come to think of it, I'm feeling very eager myself. First things first, though."
    "Ara que hi penso, jo també estic il·lusionat. Però anem a pams."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2336
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2eecae53:

    # hi "Lilly?"
    hi "Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2341
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a8c505d1:

    # li "Yes, now is good."
    li "Sí, ara va bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2343
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e99597ad:

    # "Each of us knowing exactly what the other means, I lean sideways and dig around in my bag for the doll I bought Hanako as Lilly gets up and retrieves her gift."
    "Cadascun sap exactament què vol dir l'altre, m'inclino i busco a la nina que vaig comprar per la Hanako dins la bossa mentre la Lilly s'aixeca i treu el seu regal."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2345
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_35b20d6a:

    # "Hiding our gifts in our hands, we present them both on the table at the same time."
    "Ens amaguem els regals a les mans, i els posem sobre la taula a la vegada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2353
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fcd65adb:

    # "Hanako silently sits looking at them for seconds on end, out of sheer surprise."
    "La Hanako seu en silenci i els mira una bona estona, meravellada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2355
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f323351a:

    # "My little wooden doll, replete with Victorian-era dress and little hat, lies next to a light brown and fluffy stuffed bear from Lilly."
    "La nineta de fusta, amb un vestit i un barretet victorians, reposa al costat de l'osset de peluix, marró clar i peludet de la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2360
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_dab77af1:

    # "She clutches at her gown as she moves to speak, not taking her eyes off the modest presents."
    "S'agafa el vestit mentre es posa a parlar, sense treure els ulls de sobre d'aquests regals tan senzills."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2365
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c92542d7:

    # ha "Th… thank you… Lilly and… Hisao…"
    ha "Gr... Gràcies... Lilly i... Hisao"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2379
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c9677256:

    # "Her voice begins to crack as Lilly reaches forward, wrapping her in a soft embrace."
    "Se li comença a esquerdar la veu mentre la Lilly se li acosta, i li fa una abraçada suau."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2381
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8d7b7b7f:

    # "The sight of Hanako holding Lilly so tightly is heartwarming, so much so that I couldn't wipe the smile off my face even if I wanted to."
    "Em commou veure a la Hanako abraçar a la Lilly amb tanta força, tant que no podria esborrar-me el somriure de la cara encara que volgués."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2383
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_302497ca:

    # "As Lilly gently rests her face on Hanako's head, she speaks so quietly and softly that I can barely hear."
    "Mentre la Lilly reposa la cara en el cap de la Hanako, li parla amb tana tranquil·litat i suavitat que amb prou feines la puc sentir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2385
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5d2b877b:

    # li "Happy birthday, Hanako."
    li "Per molts anys, Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2387
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_de4373e6:

    # hi "Happy birthday."
    hi "Per molts anys."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2389
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_90d234c2:

    # "Hanako gives a small nod, holding on to Lilly for a time before breaking off and wiping an eye."
    "La Hanako assenteix suaument, agafant-se a la Lilly durant una estona abans deixar-la anar i eixugar-se un ull."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2391
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8b8b4504:

    # "I guess that for Hanako simply having someone, anyone, to be there and love her would be special. The fact that Lilly and I can now share that role for her is something I think I will always be grateful for."
    "Suposo que per a la Hanako el simple fet de tenir algú, qui sigui, que estigui per ella i l'estimi, és especial. El fet que tant la Lilly com jo puguem compartir aquest paper és una cosa per la qual sempre li estaré agraït."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2396
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_451223be:

    # "Hanako gently takes the doll and teddy bear, holding them both to her chest as she warmly smiles."
    "La Hanako agafa suaument la nina i l'osset de peluix, apropant-se'ls al pit mentre somriu amb tendresa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2398
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_426beb68:

    # "For a long time, all three of us simply sit in happy silence. The quiet is not broken until Lilly's soft voice beckons."
    "Durant una bona estona, estem simplement asseguts i feliçment en silenci. El silenci no es trenca fins que la Lilly ens convida amb una veu suau."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2400
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f8822123:

    # li "Shall we have at the cake, then?"
    li "Passem al pastís?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2411
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b7634a6e:

    # "Her proposal is met with two looks of unhidden anticipation."
    "La seva proposta és rebuda amb dues mirades plenes d'anticipació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2413
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1573559b:

    # hi "No argument from me."
    hi "Em sembla bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2415
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ea2d722a:

    # ha "Okay."
    ha "D'acord."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2428
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9a2e09ba:

    # hi "Phew, that was good."
    hi "Uf, que bo que estava."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2432
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1b69e2e5:

    # "I contentedly sit back, both Lilly and Hanako looking just as satisfied with the food as I. It took some effort, but we managed to finish off the cake in one go."
    "Em quedo satisfet, tant la Lilly com la Hanako sembla que estan tan satisfetes com jo. Ens ha costat una mica, però hem aconseguit acabar-nos el pastís d'una tirada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2437
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b3328ab5:

    # ha "I don't think I could fit any more in."
    ha "No crec que pugui menjar més."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2442
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4b3258a4:

    # li "I think next time I'll buy a smaller cake."
    li "Per la següent compraré un pastís més petit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2447
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_820423fc:

    # "Hanako and I give a chuckle, but I can't help noticing that, come this time next year, we'll have graduated from Yamaku."
    "A la Hanako i a mi se'ns escapa el riure, però no puc evitar pensar que, d'aquí a un any, ja ens haurem graduat del Yamaku."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2449
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f4c7d10d:

    # "That fact is somewhat depressing, since I finally feel as if my life is starting to get back into some kind of order."
    "Això em deprimeix una mica, ja que per fi sento que la meva vida comença a recuperar cert tipus d'ordre."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2451
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_cbbb3103:

    # "Idly looking around Lilly's neat and orderly room, her books catch my eye once again."
    "Passejo distretament la mirada per l'habitació ordenada i neta de la Lilly, i em tornen a cridar l'atenció els seus llibres."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2453
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_221cc495:

    # "This may be a little impetuous, but my curiosity gets the better of me. Besides, I don't think she'll mind in any case."
    "Potser és una mica impulsiu, però la curiositat em supera. A més, no crec que la molesti en cap cas."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2455
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4af6d51b:

    # hi "Hey Lilly, do you mind if I take a look at one of your books?"
    hi "Escolta Lilly, que podria donar un cop d'ull als teus llibres?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2460
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_66346526:

    # li "You're quite welcome to, Hisao."
    li "I tant que pots, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2465
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_91eec1f1:

    # li "That said, if you can overcome two language barriers I will be quite impressed."
    li "Dit això, si ets capaç de superar dues barreres lingüístiques em deixaràs admirada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2467
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1e206f19:

    # hi "Two? Braille and… oh right, English."
    hi "Dos? Braille i... ah és clar, anglès."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2472
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_efae91a6:

    # "She gives a nod."
    "Fa que sí amb el cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2474
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e4976665:

    # hi "I knew you were studying English, but I'm still amazed that you're this proficient at it."
    hi "Sabia que estudiaves anglès, però encara em sorprèn que en sàpigues tant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2479
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_7d138bf8:

    # li "One could say it's a perfect way to avoid people borrowing my collection."
    li "Podria dir-se que és una bona manera de fer que la gent no em demani la meva col·lecció."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2481
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8c21ba61:

    # "She says it in jest, but I am a little disappointed. Having all these books around me with no way of reading them feels like one big tease."
    "Ho diu amb broma, però em decebo una mica. Tinc tots aquests llibres al voltant però no poder-los llegir em sembla una conya."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2483
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_521a2aab:

    # "Hanako giggles quietly as I reach over the closest pile, plucking the topmost book with only a cursory glance. 'Death on the Nile,' in large letters on the cover, is the only printed text to be seen."
    "La Hanako riu fluixet quan m'apropo a la pila més propera, agafo el llibre de dalt de tot després d'un primer cop d'ull. \"Mort al Nil\", hi ha escrit en lletres grans a la portada, que és l'únic text imprès que hi ha."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2492
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_277a697d:

    # "I sit down for a while with the book open on my lap as Lilly and Hanako talk."
    "M'assec una estona amb el llibre obert a la falda mentre la Lilly i la Hanako parlen."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2494
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_68052d49:

    # "Try as I might to feel out the dots of Braille printed on each page, they seem to blend into one another and become indistinct."
    "Intento sentir els punts de Braille impresos a cada pàgina, semblen barrejar-se entre si i es tornen confusos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2496
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a48268d0:

    # "I'd thought this to be a lot easier than it actually is. With some practice though, I could see someone with a better sense of touch than mine managing to read at a pretty fast speed."
    "Pensava que això era molt més fàcil del que realment és. M'imagino que algú amb una mica de pràctica i amb millor sentit del tacte que el meu, aconseguiria llegir força de pressa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2509
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_90bc09d6:

    # "Noticing a silence that had probably begun earlier, I look up from the dotted pages to see Lilly smiling as Hanako sips another cup of tea."
    "Noto un silenci que deu fer estona que ha començat, així que aixeco els ulls de les pàgines de punts i veig a la Lilly somrient mentre la Hanako beu una altra tassa de te."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2511
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9dbd43ff:

    # hi "Is something wrong?"
    hi "Que passa alguna cosa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2516
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_16ad9b4b:

    # li "Quite the opposite, your curiosity's quite endearing."
    li "Tot el contrari, la teva curiositat em sembla entranyable."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2518
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a57ae9d4:

    # "I am inordinately pleased by the praise, though I can feel my cheeks heating up a little."
    "M'alegra molt aquest elogi, i noto com les galtes se m'encenen una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2520
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_dc80870f:

    # hi "Thanks, but I don't know how else I could act."
    hi "Gràcies, però no sé com més podria actuar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2525
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ff0ebb4d:

    # li "To be honest, I wasn't altogether sure of how you saw us, since you were a new transfer student from another school."
    li "Si et soc sincera, no tenia gaire clar com ens veies, ja que ets nou i vens d'una altra escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2532
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b31eb343:

    # li "If you'd pitied us, I would have been quite offended."
    li "Si t'haguéssim fet pena, m'hauria ofès bastant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2537
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_63122353:

    # "There's a certain edge to Lilly's voice, one that I'd quite possibly place as pride. Glancing over to Hanako, she seems even more subdued than usual, looking towards Lilly rather than me."
    "Noto certa tensió en la veu de Lilly, que segurament qualificaria d'orgull. Faig una ullada a la Hanako, que sembla encara més ensopida del que és habitual, mentre mira cap a Lilly en lloc de cap a mi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2539
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4b6d0e3a:

    # hi "I wouldn't worry about that. Considering the position I've found myself in, I'm perhaps the last person that should be dispensing pity on others."
    hi "No et preocupis per això. Si tenim en compte la posició en què em trobo, potser soc l'última persona que hauria de sentir llàstima dels altres."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2541
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e4e14992:

    # hi "My parents' first interactions with me after my heart attack… I wouldn't want anyone to see that kind of face."
    hi "Les primeres interaccions que vaig tenir amb els meus pares després de l'atac de cor... No voldria que ningú veiés aquell tipus de cares."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2547
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_bc4df9d5:

    # "I catch myself from going any further, but not soon enough. Both of the girls seem to be put off, Lilly especially."
    "Paro abans d'anar més lluny, però és massa tard. Les dues noies semblen desanimades, sobretot la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2553
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_c963a449:

    # li "I'm… sorry. I shouldn't have gone that far…"
    li "Em... perdona. No hauria d'haver anat tan lluny..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2561
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2198c715:

    # "An awkward silence reigns for a few beats, thankfully ended as Lilly's head perks up in a gesture I've come to easily recognize."
    "Es fa un silenci incòmode durant uns instants, i afortunadament acaba quan la Lilly aixeca el cap amb un gest que he après a reconèixer amb facilitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2563
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_108f0dd0:

    # hi "Hear something?"
    hi "Has sentit alguna cosa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2568
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_251af332:

    # li "The door…"
    li "La porta..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2581
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d523cca1:

    # "Everyone looks towards it, trusting in Lilly's senses. True enough, the door handle shudders and turns, a flash of yellow and black slipping through."
    "Tots mirem cap allà, confiant en els sentits de la Lilly. Tenia raó, la maneta de la porta tremola i gira, un llampec groc i negre s'esmuny cap a dins."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2595
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3d640b09:

    # aki "Akira Satou is in the house! Happy birthday, Hanako!"
    aki "L'Akira Satou ja és aquí! Per molts anys, Hanako!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2600
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_83a15294:

    # ha "Ah… thank you…"
    ha "Ah... gràcies..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2606
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_361021ff:

    # "Akira takes a seat at the table as she plops her tall bag beside her. She has her trademark boisterous air about her, making no small deal of her entrance."
    "L'Akira s'asseu a la taula i deixa una gran bossa llarga al seu costat. Té aquell aire escandalós que la caracteritza, i fa de la seva entrada tot un espectacle."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2611
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2a8db01d:

    # "Hanako clutches her gown to steady herself, but doesn't appear too shaken after she settles down. I guess she must have met Akira before, not a huge surprise given how close Akira and Lilly are."
    "La Hanako s'agafa el vestit per asserenar-se, però no sembla massa afectada quan ja s'ha acomodat. Suposo que ja deu conèixer a l'Akira, cosa que no em sorprèn veient que unides estan l'Akira i la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2613
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1149cfe5:

    # "Akira doesn't seem to be the least bit put off by Hanako's scarring, despite its prominence, but she also doesn't pull any punches in how she acts despite Hanako's shy nature."
    "L'Akira no sembla que s'immuti ni una mica per les cicatrius de la Hanako, malgrat que destaquen, però tampoc es mossega la llengua a l'hora d'actuar tot i la naturalesa tímida de la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2618
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8c7b4aa8:

    # li "I thought you said you'd have to work, Akira. Did you manage to get off for a while?"
    li "Pensava que havies dit que tenies feina, Akira. T'ho has fet venir bé per escapar-te una estona?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2624
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_53f47f02:

    # aki "Eh, kinda. I feel bad about ditching the guys doing overtime, so I gotta get back soon."
    aki "Eh, d'aquella manera. Em sap greu haver deixat als nois fent hores extres, així que tornaré aviat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2629
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_16b74a2b:

    # aki "But I felt bad about not coming to your cute little Hanako's birthday too, so for now I'm here."
    aki "Però em sentia malament si no venia a l'aniversari de la teva estimada Hanako, així que per ara estic aquí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2634
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4bf06053:

    # "She grins widely at Hanako, who flowers into a full blush as she pins her eyes downwards toward her lap. Her mouth seems to widen and retract over and over, as if she was trying to suppress a smile out of embarrassment."
    "Li fa un gran somriure a la Hanako, que es posa ben vermella mentre baixa els ulls cap a la seva falda. Sembla que eixampla i contrau la boca una vegada i una altra, com si estigués intentant suprimir un somriure per vergonya."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2636
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_7dbff2e2:

    # "It's a little strange how her reaction seems to be more immediate and forceful than when she's embarrassed by the way she looks. All she manages to give in return is a tiny nod, failing to hide her appreciation to any great extent."
    "És estrany com reacciona d'una manera més immediata i contundent que quan està avergonyida pel seu aspecte. L'únic que aconsegueix donar-li a canvi és una petita inclinació amb el cap, sense poder amagar massa el seu agraïment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2638
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5ea654a9:

    # "Not that many people give her positive attention, I suppose. It makes me respect how well Akira can handle her, making her so happy, compared to what little I could do."
    "Suposo que poca gent li dedica una atenció positiva. Em fa respectar com de bé la pot manejar l'Akira, fent-la tan feliç, en comparació amb el poc que podria fer jo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2643
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_35d5bfae:

    # aki "Now then, before I go…"
    aki "Ara, abans que marxi..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2647
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b780b25f:

    # "She reaches into the bag beside her and grandly displays its contents."
    "Posa la mà dins la bossa que té al costat i en mostra el contingut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2655
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_91e0c4a1:

    # "Out come two large glass bottles, both with long French names on the labels."
    "En treu dues grans ampolles de vidre, totes dues amb noms francesos i llargs a les etiquetes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2660
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9ed318b5:

    # "Hanako's expression is an odd mix of surprise and curiosity, and I suspect mine's no different. Lilly, not seeing the proceedings, is oblivious to what's going on."
    "L'expressió de Hanako és una barreja estranya de sorpresa i curiositat, i sospito que la meva no deu ser diferent. La Lilly, que no veu els fets, no s'adona del que està passant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2665
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_98279e99:

    # ha "Akira… this isn't…"
    ha "Akira... això no és..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2670
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d78581af:

    # li "What is it?"
    li "Què passa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2672
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b9681f1d:

    # hi "Wine. One red, one white."
    hi "Vi. Un de negre i un de blanc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2677
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_10b721d3:

    # li "A-Akira! That's…!"
    li "A-Akira! Això és...!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2688
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5e6a7f9f:

    # aki "Relax, relax, it's not like Shizune's here to scold you."
    aki "Relaxa't, relaxa't, la Shizune no està aquí per renyar-te."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2690
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5943ab32:

    # hi "Lilly has a point, that's not exactly allowed on campus."
    hi "La Lilly té raó, això no està exactament permès al campus."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2692
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8b8f2eef:

    # hi "…or anywhere, really. We're still short of the legal drinking age, remember?"
    hi "...o en qualsevol lloc, de fet. Encara no tenim l'edat legal per beure, recordes?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2697
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3bdb21ba:

    # aki "Rich words for someone practically drooling as he examines a bottle."
    aki "Unes paraules molt fortes per a algú a qui pràcticament li cau la bava mentre examina l'ampolla."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2699
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_87b41be4:

    # "She got me there. I am genuinely interested in trying some, even just a little. While Hanako may not be handling one herself, her look does tell me that she's far from opposed to the notion as well."
    "M'ha pillat. Realment m'interessa provar-ho, encara que només sigui una mica. Tot i que la Hanako no les toqui, la seva mirada em diu que està lluny d'oposar-se a la idea."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2704
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8d7a892a:

    # "Lilly rubs her forehead, giving up the fight that she knows Akira would win due to simply not caring enough about those funny 'rules' and 'regulations.'"
    "La Lilly es frega el front, renuncia a lluita perquè sap que l'Akira guanyaria, simplement perquè no li importen prou aquestes ridícules \"normes\" i \"regles\"."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2709
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d8af269e:

    # li "Just don't breathe a word of this to anyone in the school, please. I beg of you."
    li "No diguis res d'això a ningú de l'escola, si us plau. T'ho prego."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2714
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d6bc784e:

    # aki "I'm not stupid, don't worry."
    aki "No soc estúpida, no et preocupis."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2719
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f08e18d6:

    # aki "That said, I gotta get back to work pretty soon."
    aki "Dit això, he de tornar ben aviat a la feina."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2724
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_aead2be2:

    # li "So soon? But you only just arrived…"
    li "Tan aviat? Però acabes d'arribar..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2729
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_571688e4:

    # aki "Sorry, Lilly. Good to see you two again though, and you Hisao."
    aki "Ho sento, Lilly. M'alegro de tornar-vos a veure, a tu també Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2731
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_b0895212:

    # hi "See you later, then."
    hi "Ens veiem després, doncs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2733
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3411f5c5:

    # ha "Um… g-goodbye… Akira…"
    ha "Um... a-adeu... Akira..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2742
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_976f2e57:

    # "She levers herself up with a grunt and waltzes out of the room, leaving us alone with the two items on the table."
    "S'aixeca amb un grunyit i surt tot cofoia de l'habitació, ens deixa sols amb els dos objectes a sobre la taula."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2753
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d480160c:

    # hi "…Interesting."
    hi "... Interessant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2759
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4b24f138:

    # "Lilly gives a nervous giggle at her sister's antics as Hanako takes a wine bottle."
    "La Lilly fa una rialleta nerviosa per les pallassades de la seva germana mentre la Hanako agafa una ampolla de vi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2764
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_33e1c2d5:

    # ha "So…"
    ha "Així que..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2766
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_548e3224:

    # hi "What do you think, Lilly?"
    hi "Què en penses, Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2771
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_57e69965:

    # "She rests her elbow on the table and pinches the bridge of her nose, thinking things through. She really doesn't seem to be able to keep up with her sister."
    "Posa el colze sobre la taula i es pessiga el pont del seu nas, pensant-hi detingudament. Sembla que no sigui capaç de seguir el corrent a la seva germana."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2778
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_475dc263:

    # li "Well… it's already here. We may as well have some."
    li "Bé... ja que ho tenim. Podríem provar-ne una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2780
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_1ed1d01c:

    # "No sooner does she say it that I take a quick glance around the room for glasses."
    "Tan aviat com ho diu, faig un cop d'ull ràpid a l'habitació, tot buscant copes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2787
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_bd952d96:

    # "A small groan above me reminds me that Lilly retired to rest on her bed for a bit a few minutes ago."
    "Un petit gemec sobre meu em recorda que la Lilly fa poc se n'ha anat al llit a descansar una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2789
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_48d8e434:

    # "Almost completely drained of energy, I manage to stand up and drag myself to the side of the bed, sitting down and leaning my back against it."
    "Quasi sense forces, aconsegueixo aixecar-me i arrossegar-me al costat del llit, m'assec i hi recolzo l'esquena."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2801
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_87f991d4:

    # hi "Good God."
    hi "Déu meu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2808
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_5414d71e:

    # li "Eugh…"
    li "Buf..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2810
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f0d2de39:

    # "Lilly's groan sounds lifeless."
    "El gemec de la Lilly's sona sense esma."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2812
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_097e65fa:

    # hi "Too much to drink?"
    hi "Has begut massa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2817
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_0c425f2a:

    # li "My head hurts."
    li "Em fa mal el cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2819
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2423825f:

    # hi "Yeah, too much to drink."
    hi "Sí, has begut massa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2821
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3ef68f50:

    # "I rest my head back and idly stare at the ceiling. What an unmitigated disaster."
    "Recolzo el cap enrere i miro distretament el sostre. Quin desastre més absolut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2823
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ec61ff3f:

    # "Like proper idiots, we all drank the night away with one glass after another. Hanako simply fell to the side asleep, and it's a miracle I don't feel as ill as Lilly."
    "Com autèntics idiotes, ens hem passat la nit bevent una copa darrere l'altre. La Hanako simplement s'ha quedat dormida de costat, i és un miracle que no em trobi tan malament com la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2828
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_a4ebaa90:

    # li "Hey, Hisao? I'm sorry about today. I… didn't think this would happen."
    li "Ei, Hisao? Em sap greu això d'avui. Jo... no pensava que passaria això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2830
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3100de6a:

    # hi "It's fine, Lilly. To tell the truth, I had a lot of fun today."
    hi "No passa res, Lilly. Si et dic la veritat, m'he divertit molt avui."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2835
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_de0bfc95:

    # li "Really?"
    li "De debò?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2837
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4c933fe5:

    # hi "Mmm. I think Hanako did too. No, she certainly did."
    hi "Mmm. Crec que la Hanako també. No, definitivament s'ha divertit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2842
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_259aa7c3:

    # "There's a short silence, before another groan resounds from the supine Lilly."
    "Es fa un breu silenci, abans que un altre gemec ressoni de la Lilly, que està d'esquenes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2844
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_57b93a1c:

    # hi "You okay?"
    hi "Estàs bé?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2849
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_f0c19eef:

    # li "As you said, I just drank too much. What's the time?"
    li "Com tu has dit, he begut massa. Quina hora és?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2851
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_faea1407:

    # hi "The time? Uh, it's…"
    hi "L'hora? Eh, són..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2853
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_06d211d2:

    # "I quickly look at my wristwatch, its numerals barely legible in the gloom."
    "Ràpidament, em miro el rellotge de polsera, i amb prou feines puc llegir els números a la penombra."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2855
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d13148a4:

    # hi "About midnight."
    hi "Cap a mitjanit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2860
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_217b371a:

    # li "Curfew's in effect, then."
    li "Llavors, ja hi ha toc de queda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2862
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8cb85026:

    # hi "Yeah, guessed as much. We'll all have to sleep here for tonight."
    hi "Sí, ho he suposat. Haurem de dormir aquí aquesta nit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2864
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_09c64c6f:

    # "As soon as I say it, I hear the sheets moving as Lilly starts to sit up."
    "Tan aviat com ho dic, sento els llençols que es mouen mentre Lilly comença a seure."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2869
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9beb4157:

    # li "Hanako…"
    li "Hanako…"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2871
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_561e2508:

    # hi "Ah, no, go back to sleep, don't try to get up."
    hi "Ah, no, torna a dormir, no intentis aixecar-te."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2876
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_3687e298:

    # li "Hisao, I have to…"
    li "Hisao, he de..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2878
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_31500935:

    # hi "You're in worse shape than me by any stretch. Get some rest."
    hi "Estàs pitjor que no pas jo. Descansa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2883
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d12512e5:

    # li "But what about…"
    li "Però i..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2885
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_292495a9:

    # hi "I'll grab some spare blankets and put them over her, don't worry."
    hi "Agafaré unes mantes de recanvi i les hi posaré per sobre, no et preocupis."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2890
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4df4ef4f:

    # "As I give a deep yawn and stand to retrieve them, I hear her lie back down with a soft thud."
    "Mentre badallo profundament i m'aixeco per agafar-les, sento que es tomba de nou amb un cop suau."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2892
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_10354753:

    # li "Thank you, Hisao."
    li "Gràcies, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2894
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_9deea8c4:

    # hi "No problem, it's the least I can do. You look outright wasted."
    hi "Cap problema, és el mínim que puc fer. Francament, sembla que vas força pet."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2896
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_da5ce0bd:

    # li "I'm not… wasted… just a little bit… tired."
    li "No vaig... pet... només estic... cansada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2898
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d44a3463:

    # "She starts pouting, a slight slur beginning to distort her words as the alcohol takes hold of her again. I grab a couple of blankets rolled up at the end of her bed."
    "Comença a fer morros i a arrossegar les paraules a mesura que l'alcohol torna a prendre força de nou. Agafo un parell de mantes plegades al final del seu llit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2900
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_fc431f4b:

    # "Quietly walking over to Hanako, I carefully lay the blankets over her peacefully sleeping figure, making sure not to wake her up."
    "Passo amb silenci per sobre de la Hanako, li poso les mantes per sobre mentre dorm pacíficament, i m'asseguro de no despertar-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2902
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_388eacca:

    # "The thick smell of alcohol coming off her breath makes me doubt she'd wake up no matter what I did, though."
    "L'olor espessa de l'alcohol que li fa l'alè em fa dubtar si es despertaria, fes el que fes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2904
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_2cf7db94:

    # "I stand and take one last measure of the room."
    "M'aixeco i miro l'habitació una última vegada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2908
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ff5052ce:

    # "Two girls, both very drunk, and one guy sleeping overnight with them in the female students' dorm. What a scandal that'd be if it broke out."
    "Dues noies, totes dues molt begudes, i un noi que dorm amb elles durant tota la nit al mateix dormitori que les estudiants. Quin escàndol seria si es sabés."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2910
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ff1e96e6:

    # "As I move to sit back down at the side of the bed, I steal one last glance at Lilly."
    "Quan torno a seure al costat del llit, faig un últim cop d'ull a la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2912
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ce41eb06:

    # "Her sprawling, disheveled figure lies resting peacefully, slightly turned to the side."
    "Descansa pacíficament, desmanegada i rebregada, girada una mica cap a un costat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2914
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_4c170dc0:

    # "I crouch down to get a better look."
    "M'ajupo per veure-la millor."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2924
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ccc7789a:

    # "Her white skin blends in with the white pillow of the bed, a look of slumber-born peacefulness on her face."
    "La seva pell blanca harmonitza amb el coixí blanc del llit, té una expressió tranquil·la fruit de la son."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2926
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_d6b51eb8:

    # "Usually she seems so confident and forward, always there and caring for Hanako. Now, though, she seems painfully delicate."
    "Normalment, sembla tan segura i atrevida, sempre allà i cuidant la Hanako. Ara, però, sembla anguniosament delicada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2928
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_efb604ed:

    # "I think back to Hanako's presents."
    "Recordo els regals de la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2930
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_898b4ff3:

    # "I thought it'd be a nice occasion for her, but I'd hardly expected it to be so moving."
    "Pensava que seria una ocasió especial per a ella, però no m'esperava que fos tan commovedora."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2932
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ae88318f:

    # "One birthday after another, year after year."
    "Un aniversari després d'un altre, any rere any."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2934
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_8b82fed0:

    # "Just she and Lilly, all alone."
    "Només ella i la Lilly, totes soles."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2936
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_747e0b22:

    # "…I guess it wasn't just the presents she liked."
    "... suposo que no només li han agradat els regals."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2941
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_222a138b:

    # "Resigning myself to an uncomfortable sleep, I sit down at the side of the bed once again and rest my tired arms beside me."
    "Resignat a tenir un son incòmode, em torno a asseure al costat del llit i reposo els braços cansats al costat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2943
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_368d5020:

    # li "Hey, Hisao."
    li "Ei, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2945
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_e3f0d902:

    # "Lilly's voice is so quiet I can barely hear it. She must be on the verge of sleep."
    "La veu de la Lilly és tan fluixa que amb prou feines puc sentir-la. Deu estar a punt d'adormir-se."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2950
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_eb28cbfe:

    # hi "Yeah?"
    hi "Sí?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2955
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_58cff27e:

    # li "Thank you."
    li "Gràcies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2957
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_72e48d84:

    # hi "Thank you? For what?"
    hi "Gràcies? Per què?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2959
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_41588125:

    # li "For being here."
    li "Per haver vingut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2961
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_bad6fc01:

    # hi "…That's okay."
    hi "... Cap problema."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2966
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_ef204385:

    # "As I hear a deep breath, it's obvious Lilly's gone to sleep."
    "Sento una respiració profunda, és evident que la Lilly s'ha adormit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2968
translate ca a2_lilly_unidentified_drinking_object_11bc6d56:

    # "After closing my eyes, it doesn't take long for slumber to take me as well."
    "Després de tancar els ulls, no tardo gaire a caure rendit jo també."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2983
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_43b7d705:

    # mystery "Hisao?"
    mystery "Hisao?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2985
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_660c9db3:

    # mystery "Hisao, are you…?"
    mystery "Hisao, estàs...?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2987
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_dbb266a5:

    # "The soft, barely audible voice lingering in my ears slowly wakes me. I wish I could be awoken like this more often."
    "La veu suau, quasi inaudible que em ressona a les orelles, em desperta lentament. Tant de bo pogués despertar-me així més sovint."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:2989
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_620b629a:

    # "With a mumble, I slowly open my…"
    "Amb un murmuri, obro lentament els..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3011
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_2177d4cb:

    # "Taken by surprise at the face hovering curiously mere millimeters from mine, I make our heads collide with a harsh thud. The impact of our foreheads causes both of us to fall backwards and yelp in pain, Lilly sounding more like a squeak toy than a person."
    "La cara que vacil·la estranyament tan sols mil·límetres de la meva m'agafa per sorpresa, i faig que els nostres caps xoquin amb una patacada sorda. L'impacte dels nostres fronts fa que tots dos caiguem cap enrere i gemeguem de dolor, la Lilly sona més com una joguina que com una persona."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3013
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_328d62cb:

    # hi "Ow, ow, ow."
    hi "Ai, ai, ai."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3017
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_2dd1abac:

    # "I slowly rub my forehead with one hand, supporting myself with the other. Lilly lies a few feet ahead doing just the same, her face obviously pained."
    "Em frego el front lentament amb la mà, i em recolzo en l'altra. La Lilly jeu uns metres més endavant i fa el mateix, se li veia a la cara que li havia fet mal"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3019
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_d2928569:

    # hi "Ah… sorry. Your face was kinda close and I acted on reflex. You okay?"
    hi "Ah... ho sento. Tenies la cara molt a prop i he actuat per reflexos. Estàs bé?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3026
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_40b98f79:

    # li "My head…"
    li "Em fa mal el cap..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3028
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_7a003701:

    # "It seems she's not actually okay. Come to think of it, I doubt that the impact alone is what's causing her head so much pain."
    "Sembla que realment no està bé. Ben mirat, dubto que només amb l'impacte li hagi pogut fer tant de mal al cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3030
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_3657c4e9:

    # hi "Hangover? You drank a fair bit, last night."
    hi "Ressaca? Vas beure una mica, ahir a la nit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3036
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_3cac2239:

    # "She silently nods in confirmation as I lever myself up."
    "Assenteix en silenci per confirmar-m'ho mentre jo m'aixeco."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3043
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_36477042:

    # "I offer a hand to her, and help her back onto her feet. Glancing behind her, I find that Hanako's still fast asleep."
    "Li ofereixo una mà i l'ajudo a posar-se de peus. Miro darrere seu i veig que la Hanako encara està adormida."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3048
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_d160f86c:

    # li "It's not fair… I only drank as much as you did…"
    li "No és just... Vaig beure el mateix que tu..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3050
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_bfa2befd:

    # hi "That's very different from what I remember. And anyway, girls have a lower tolerance than men."
    hi "Jo ho recordo diferent. I de totes maneres, les noies tenen menys tolerància que els homes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3055
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_42da9e3f:

    # li "That doesn't help."
    li "Això no ajuda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3057
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_fe1c4783:

    # hi "Fine, I'll get you a glass of water. Just be careful not to trip over Hanako."
    hi "Bé, et portaré un got d'aigua. Ves amb compte de no ensopegar amb la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3062
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_abf0d6f4:

    # "I rub the sleep out of my eyes, or at least some of it, as I walk to the counter. Tending to someone with a hangover isn't the way I like to spend a morning."
    "Em trec les lleganyes dels ulls, o almenys una part, mentre camino cap a la pica. Cuidar algú amb ressaca no és com m'agrada passar els matins."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3064
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_685e2229:

    # "It only takes a few seconds for the glass to fill, the clear water reflecting the sliver of light that makes it through the thin curtains."
    "El got triga uns segons a omplir-se, l'aigua clara reflecteix la mica de llum que es filtra a través de les fines cortines."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3066
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_f604624b:

    # "It looks like Lilly's taken a seat on the side of the bed. I walk over to her while taking care to step over the peacefully sleeping Hanako, and place the glass into her outstretched hands."
    "Sembla que la Lilly s'ha assegut al costat del llit. Me'n vaig cap a ella amb compte de no trepitjar la Hanako, que dorm tranquil·lament, i li poso el got entre les mans."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3073
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_58cff27e:

    # li "Thank you."
    li "Gràcies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3075
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_11a6e6fb:

    # hi "No problem."
    hi "Cap problema."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3079
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_1c6e1983:

    # "I take a seat next to her, the soft bed having a surprising amount of give."
    "M'assec al seu costat, i em sorprèn com cedeix el llit de tou que és."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3081
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_3905d9e0:

    # "She drinks slowly and methodically. A long silence passes with only Hanako's soft breathing to be heard."
    "Beu a poc a poc i metòdicament. Es fa un llarg silenci en què només se sent la respiració suau de la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3086
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_9a3334a1:

    # "With some measure of guilt, I look at Lilly's face and attempt to read her expression. Her brow is furrowed, and she looks to be lost in thought."
    "Miro, amb certa culpa, la cara de Lilly i intento llegir la seva expressió. Té el front arrugat, i sembla abstreta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3091
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_fc22f25c:

    # "For a moment I hesitate, but eventually place a hand on her shoulder in an attempt to reassure her. I didn't expect her to flinch rather noticeably at that, though."
    "Dubto un moment, però finalment li poso una mà a l'espatlla per intentar tranquil·litzar-la. Tanmateix, no esperava que m'esquivés d'una manera tan evident."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3093
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_729735e8:

    # hi "Ah, sorry. I didn't mean to—"
    hi "Ah, perdona. No volia..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3098
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_70090ade:

    # "Lilly quickly shakes her head, in a manner somewhat more violent than usual for her."
    "La Lilly sacseja el cap ràpid, d'una manera més violenta del que és pròpia d'ella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3100
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_05547475:

    # "She takes a long breath to steady herself before letting her head sink."
    "Inspira profundament per calmar-se abans de deixar caure el cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3105
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_5b37784c:

    # li "I must look terrible right now…"
    li "Dec fer una pinta horrorosa ara mateix..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3107
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_567ffde9:

    # "I move to protest, but quickly realize that it would be futile to do so. That said, I want her to open up more."
    "Faig el gest de protestar, però de seguida m'adono que seria inútil. Dit això, m'agradaria que s'obrís més."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3109
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_d381466d:

    # hi "If you want to talk about anything, I'm here."
    hi "Si vols parlar d'alguna cosa, estic aquí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3114
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_64ed19d6:

    # "Lilly gives a self-deprecating snort, as if to mock her own emotions."
    "La Lilly deixa anar un esbufec de rebuig per ella mateixa, com si es burlés de les seves pròpies emocions."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3119
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_aa1db038:

    # li "There's just… a lot happening right now."
    li "És només que... estan passant moltes coses ara mateix."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3124
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_1f982b95:

    # li "I'm sorry for being so strange recently, especially back when we were in town. Even now I'm a bit confused about everything."
    li "Em sap greu haver estat tan rara últimament, sobretot quan estàvem a la ciutat. Encara ara, estic una mica confusa amb tot."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3126
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_d9e34bf1:

    # hi "Believe me, I know how that feels."
    hi "Creu-me, entenc com et sents."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3131
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_fb5e6a11:

    # "She smiles wistfully, resting a cheek on the backs of her fingers."
    "Somriu amb recança, recolzant una galta al dors dels dits."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3133
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_4a86b490:

    # li "We're a couple of broken young fools, aren't we?"
    li "Som un parell de joves ximplets i acabats, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3135
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_83a22dc4:

    # hi "Come on, don't say that. Come graduation, we'll be back out into the real world."
    hi "Au va, no diguis això. Quan arribi la graduació, tornarem al món real."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3137
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_bee4722f:

    # "The real world? Sometimes I surprise myself with the way I think about things. I guess the strange, divorced feeling of Yamaku and the surrounding town compared to the outside world still hasn't become natural."
    "El món real? A vegades em sorprenc a mi mateix per la manera en què penso les coses. Suposo que la sensació estranya d'aïllar el Yamaku i la ciutat circumdant del món exterior encara no em surt de manera natural."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3139
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_9fb93df1:

    # "Maybe it never will. It's strange, in hindsight; being isolated from society like this doesn't feel as bad as it probably should. A wry grin on her face, Lilly seems to share the same sense of amusement at the idea."
    "Potser mai em sortirà. És estrany, en retrospectiva; estar aïllat així de la societat no està tan malament com hauria de ser. Pel somriure murri que fa la Lilly, sembla que comparteixi el mateix sentiment d'hilaritat per la idea."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3141
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_72f2973e:

    # "Eventually, though, her smile drops."
    "Malgrat això, al final se li esborra el somriure."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3146
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_fbb073a4:

    # li "I'll be going back to Scotland for a week or two, soon."
    li "Aviat, tornaré a Escòcia una setmana o dues."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3148
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_0012205f:

    # hi "Is that why we had to reschedule Hanako's birthday party?"
    hi "És per això que vam haver de canviar la data de la festa d'aniversari de la Hanako?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3150
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_18c86061:

    # "She gives an affirmative nod."
    "Fa un cop de cap afirmatiu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3152
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_eee919bc:

    # hi "You'll be able to see your family again, at least. You're not looking forward to it?"
    hi "Podràs tornar a veure la teva família, almenys. No en tens ganes?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3157
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_a4134599:

    # li "I haven't met my family in six years. I don't even know how to act around them any more."
    li "Fa sis anys que no veig a la meva família. Ja no sé ni com actuar davant seu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3159
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_c0d019bb:

    # "Wait… what? My mouth hangs open as I try to process what she said."
    "Espera... què? Em quedo amb un pam de boca mentre intento pair això que ha dit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3163
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_9b293399:

    # "If she's eighteen, that means she'd have been only twelve when they left. I may have seen very little of my parents, what with them both working long hours, but that's…"
    "Si té divuit anys, vol dir que només en tenia dotze quan van marxar. Potser jo he vist molt poc els meus pares, ja que tots dos treballaven moltes hores, però això és..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3165
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_a560e373:

    # "I feel utterly useless as I struggle to find some way to respond."
    "Em sento com un negat mentre intento trobar alguna resposta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3167
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_b5a26fb7:

    # hi "That's… but, why?"
    hi "Això és... però, per què?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3172
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_5f3014a7:

    # li "Why did they leave, or why are they inviting Akira and me back?"
    li "Per què van marxar o perquè volen que l'Akira i jo tornem?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3174
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_0270e7b5:

    # hi "Both, I suppose."
    hi "Les dues coses, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3179
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_e3fcc65f:

    # li "My father's business has its headquarters in Scotland, and an executive position became available for him there. In the end, he had to move permanently."
    li "El negoci del meu pare té la seu a Escòcia, i va quedar-hi lliure un càrrec executiu. Al final, van haver de moure's permanentment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3181
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_c2f73d53:

    # li "My mother followed him, but Akira and I stayed in Japan for the sake of both Akira's job within the Japanese branch of my father's company, and my education."
    li "La mare el va seguir, però l'Akira i jo vam quedar-nos al Japó tant pel bé de la feina de l'Akira dins de la branca japonesa de la companyia del pare, com per la meva educació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3186
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_5c368bc0:

    # li "As for the latter… one of my aunts is gravely sick."
    li "Pel que fa a la segona pregunta... una de les meves tietes està molt malalta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3188
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_b01de102:

    # hi "Ah. I'm… sorry."
    hi "Ah. Em... sap greu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3193
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_219f6d4d:

    # li "Don't be. It feels strange, really. We're being summoned there for her, yet we've barely met before. I can't even remember the sound of her voice."
    li "No ho sentis. De fet, se'm fa estrany. Ens fan anar allà per ella, però gairebé no l'he conegut abans. Ni tan sols recordo la seva veu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3195
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_628028f0:

    # "Equally strange is the total lack of antipathy she feels towards her family for doing such a thing. I can't help feeling slightly humbled."
    "La manca d'aversió que sent cap a la seva família per fer una cosa així és igual d'estranya. No puc evitar sentir una mica d'humilitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3197
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_a20c4662:

    # "That said, her wistful exterior is just hiding her emotions. Seeing her like this is depressing."
    "Dit això, el seu posat pensatiu només amaga les seves emocions. Veure-la així és depriment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3201
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_8447abea:

    # "Knowing what to do, I lift myself off the bed. Lilly notices the bed's movements, her head perking up and her hand reaching sideways to feel where I was."
    "M'aixeco del llit tot sabent què fer. La Lilly nota els moviments del llit, aixeca el cap i mou les mans al costat per veure on soc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3206
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_0bbd4169:

    # li "Hisao…?"
    li "Hisao...?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3210
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_ba68fae8:

    # "I walk over to my bag, still leaning against the wall. Unbuckling the front flap and retrieving the opaque bag from within, I take the small, plain box in my hands."
    "Vaig cap a la meva bossa, encara recolzada a la paret. Desenganxo la solapa davantera i n'agafo la bossa opaca de dins, em poso la capseta senzilla a les mans."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3212
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_4c4a98b4:

    # hi "Hold your hands out, Lilly."
    hi "Dona'm les mans, Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3217
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_e75e00f7:

    # "She looks surprised for a moment, but eventually acquiesces."
    "Per un moment, sembla sorpresa, però acaba accedint."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3235
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_bc9cf76f:

    # "I'm amused by her look of curiosity when I place the music box into her open palms, her typically delicate way of handling it making it seem as if it were fragile enough to break if breathed on."
    "Em fa gràcia la cara de curiositat que posa quan li col·loco la capseta de música a les mans, i la manera tan delicada que té de manipular-la fa que sembli que tan fràgil que s'hagi de trencar si li tira l'alè."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3239
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_59233d55:

    # "She wordlessly brings it in front of her face, her slender fingers feeling out its contours and patterning."
    "S'ho acosta a la cara sense dir res, i els seus dits esvelts en palpen els contorns i els patrons."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3241
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_b1603c02:

    # "Eventually her fingers find the recessed line between the lid and body of the box, and her thumb effortlessly pops open the lid."
    "Finalment, amb els dits troba la línia buida entre la tapa i el cos de la capsa, sense gaire esforç n'obre la tapa amb el polze."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3249
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_abbb046f:

    # "I take a seat on the bed next to her, watching her face silently and intently."
    "M'assec al seu costat al llit, i li miro la cara en silenci i amb atenció."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3251
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_e06336f7:

    # "She sits completely motionless as she listens to the diminutive tinny melody, her mouth just slightly open."
    "S'asseu completament immòbil mentre n'escolta la melodia metàl·lica quasi imperceptible, amb la boca lleugerament oberta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3276
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_fae40668:

    # "It takes a long while before she closes the lid with a small snap, bringing the curtain down on the miniature performance playing in her hands."
    "Triga molt a tancar la tapa amb un petit cop sec, tancant així el teló de l'actuació en miniatura que té entre les mans."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3278
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_bc92fa40:

    # "The smile on her face, gentle and wistful, shows that I made the right decision."
    "El somriure que té a la cara, tendre i malenconiós, em demostra que vaig prendre la decisió correcta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3280
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_274d89be:

    # hi "Think of it as a going away present for your trip to Scotland."
    hi "Considera-ho el teu regal de comiat pel teu viatge a Escòcia."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3285
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_9ba32b45:

    # li "I will…"
    li "Ho faré..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3295
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_20097bca:

    # "A restless shuffling can be heard from the floor in front of us, the sound having woken Hanako."
    "A terra, davant nostre, se sent una fregadissa inquieta, el so que la Hanako s'ha despertat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3307
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_ed5f27ec:

    # "She climbs out of the blankets I put over her, looking befuddled and wiping the sleep from her eyes."
    "Surt de sota les mantes que li vaig posar, amb cara de desconcert i traient-se les lleganyes dels ulls."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3309
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_40e9e54d:

    # hi "I see you're finally up."
    hi "Veig que per fi t'has despertat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3314
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_936a2342:

    # ha "Hmm? What?"
    ha "Hmm? Què?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3319
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_fec3b271:

    # "Hanako looks around the room with her eyes only half open, her mind far from being as awake as her body. Her dazed state makes me and Lilly chuckle."
    "La Hanako mira al voltant de l'habitació amb els ulls entreoberts, no sembla tenir la ment tan desperta com el cos. El seu estat d'atordiment ens fa riure a mi i a la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3327
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_48bc9480:

    # "As Lilly gets off the bed and tends to Hanako, I take one last look around the room."
    "Mentre la Lilly s'aixeca del llit i va cap a la Hanako, faig una última ullada a l'habitació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3329
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_4c62e9da:

    # hi "I guess I'd better get going, then. There'll be questions if I am seen leaving the girls' dormitories in the morning."
    hi "Suposo que millor que me'n vaig, doncs. Em faran massa preguntes si em veuen sortir dels dormitoris de les noies de bon matí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3334
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_2650b55a:

    # li "Goodbye, Hisao."
    li "Adeu, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3339
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_713b3435:

    # ha "Oh… goodbye."
    ha "Oh... adeu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3341
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_6e028f92:

    # "I stand and walk to the door, picking up my somewhat lighter bag along the way."
    "M'aixeco i camino cap a la porta, i agafo la bossa, una mica més lleugera, de camí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3346
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_00934ed0:

    # "After I leave the room and enter the hallway, though, I hear Lilly's footsteps behind me."
    "Però després de sortir de l'habitació i entrar al passadís, sento els passos de la Lilly darrere meu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3348
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_784b50e4:

    # hi "Hmm? What's wrong?"
    hi "Hmm? Què passa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3358
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_f91c7120:

    # "Without a word, she strides up to me. I freeze as I feel her hand slide onto my cheek, seemingly every nerve taking in the feeling of her fingers and palm upon it."
    "Sense dir res, ve cap a mi. Em congelo quan sento que la seva mà em frega la galta, i sembla que cada nervi retingui la sensació dels seus dits i el palmell sobre seu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3362
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_a4320b3c:

    # "Immediately after, her face slowly moves next to mine, a light, momentary touch of her lips brushing against my other cheek."
    "Tot seguit, mou la cara lentament cap a la meva, i noto com els seus llavis em freguen fugaçment l'altra galta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3364
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_f99ee165:

    # "For a moment, everything seems to stand still. I absentmindedly bring my fingers to my cheek, as if to try and recapture that fleeting feeling."
    "Durant un instant, tot sembla estar quiet. Inconscientment, em passo els dits per la galta, com si intentés reviure aquest sentiment fugaç."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3366
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_5e04a1b9:

    # hi "Lilly…"
    hi "Lilly..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3371
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_9fc830fc:

    # li "That's my thank you, Hisao."
    li "Així et dono les gràcies, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3373
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_6f205422:

    # hi "Thank you…?"
    hi "Gràcies...?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3378
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_d1e1b050:

    # li "For your present. Have a nice day in school."
    li "Pel teu regal. Passa un bon dia a l'escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3387
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_9a2629a1:

    # "And with that, she disappears behind her door and gently closes it, the muffled voices of her and Hanako audible through it much as they were yesterday night."
    "I així, desapareix darrere la porta de la seva habitació i la tanca suaument, i a través es poden sentir la seva veu i la de la Hanako esmorteïdes, com va passar anit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3389
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_ce617998:

    # "…"
    "…"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3391
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_b5405bcf:

    # "…I think I'd be hard pressed not to have a nice day, after that."
    "... Crec que em costarà molt no tenir un bon dia, després d'això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3396
translate ca a2_lilly_the_day_after_3aeb9a27:

    # "I walk away with a certain spring to my step. I think there were some people around that glanced at me emerging from the girl's dormitory building, but I find it difficult to care."
    "Marxo amb una mica d'empenta. Crec que algunes persones del voltant m'han vist quan sortia de l'edifici del dormitori de les noies, però em costa preocupar-me'n."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3409
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_56656f40:

    # mi "Hicchan~."
    mi "Hicchan~."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3411
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f1e2ae52:

    # hi "Go away."
    hi "Fot el camp."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3413
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_56656f40_1:

    # mi "Hicchan~."
    mi "Hicchan~."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3415
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0fff2552:

    # hi "Leave me alone."
    hi "Deixa'm en pau."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3417
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_918ac9f9:

    # mi "Come on, Hicchan~."
    mi "Va, Hicchan~."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3419
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_575c307b:

    # hi "Hmph, let me sleep."
    hi "Humph, deixa'm dormir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3421
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9db5c6b2:

    # "After two nights of not being able to sleep at all, the last thing I want is to be woken when I finally manage to."
    "Després de dues nits de no poder dormir gens, l'últim que vull és que em despertin quan per fi ho aconsegueixo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3423
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_406f8c63:

    # "It may be the last period of class, with a textbook as my pillow, but I'll take whatever sleep I can get by this point."
    "Pot ser que sigui l'última hora de classe, i que tingui un llibre de text com a coixí, però dormiré com pugui, arribats a aquest punt."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3425
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bea5a7a0:

    # mi "See Hicchan, even Shicchan wants you to get up~!"
    mi "Veus Hicchan, fins i tot la Shicchan vol despertar-te~!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3427
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d1af3f3c:

    # "I don't care what Shizune wants, leave me alone."
    "No m'importa què vulgui la Shizune, deixa'm en pau."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3429
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_acc3c830:

    # mi "Geez, Hicchan, I'll just have to wake…"
    mi "Caram, Hicchan, t'hauré de despertar..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3431
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a50f2a4c:

    # "Wait, Misha's going to…?"
    "Espera, la Misha em...?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3433
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_00c1be2e:

    # mi "…you…"
    mi "... amb..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3435
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c46960eb:

    # "This is bad!"
    "Això pinta malament!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3443
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_10d0fe90:

    # hi "I'M UP!, I'M UP! YOU DON'T… have to…"
    hi "ESTIC DESPERT! DESPERT! NO... has de..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3445
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_08a1c4fb:

    # "I can feel my face flowering into a scarlet red blush."
    "Noto com la cara se'm comença a posar vermella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3447
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d2b084cd:

    # "The students still in class are sitting bolt upright and staring at the shouting fool who was sleeping just moments before."
    "Els estudiants que encara hi ha a classe seuen amb l'esquena dreta i miren el ximple cridaner que fa uns moments estava dormint."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3449
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5ffc9abc:

    # hi "…Dammit."
    hi "... Collons."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3454
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fa79cdcc:

    # "I let my head smack back down on the table with a noticeable thud."
    "Deixo que el cap torni a caure sobre la taula amb una patacada sorda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3459
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2272a033:

    # mi "Wahahahahaha~!"
    mi "Pffhahahahaha~!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3461
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_db9748ca:

    # "Misha's trademark uncontrolled laughter reverberates through the classroom."
    "El riure descontrolat distintiu de la Misha ressona per l'aula."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3474
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_057a3cf7:

    # "As I turn my mournful eyes to the bespectacled Shizune beside her, she carefully adjusts her glasses, desperately trying to maintain a look of serious disapproval."
    "Giro els ulls afligits cap a la ulleruda Shizune al seu costat, mentre s'ajusta les ulleres amb cura i intenta, desesperadament, posar una mirada plena de retret."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3476
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bf45b8b6:

    # "Narrowing my eyes, I can see the badly-hidden grin spreading across her face."
    "Tot contraient els ulls, puc veure una mitja rialla mal amagada que s'estén per tota la cara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3478
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fbf62840:

    # hi "Et tu, Shizune?"
    hi "Tu també, Shizune?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3483
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8bc5c30d:

    # "Shizune looks away quickly as she crosses her arms tightly, barely on the edge of her control."
    "La Shizune m'aparta els ulls de seguida i plega els braços amb força, amb prou feines al límit del seu control."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3488
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c37bf51c:

    # mi "Wahahahahahaha~!"
    mi "Pffhahahahahaha~!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3490
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_87867d37:

    # "Misha's laughter doubles in volume as she glances at Shizune. All I can do is drag my hand down my face in resignation."
    "El riure de la Misha dobla el volum mentre mira a la Shizune. L'única cosa que puc fer és arrossegar la mà per la cara en resignació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3492
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c1f7f998:

    # hi "You two…"
    hi "Vosaltres dues..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3497
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_75ccbc9c:

    # mi "Who was the one who slept in class, Hicchan~?"
    mi "Qui és que s'ha adormit a classe, Hicchan~?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3499
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_20a3410f:

    # hi "Yeah, yeah, it was me."
    hi "Ja, ja, he estat jo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3504
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2db9ec3b:

    # mi "Poor Shicchan was having a fit trying to wake you up. Weren't you?"
    mi "La pobra Shicchan estava tenint un atac intentant despertar-te. Oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3509
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5705ffaf:

    # "I move my eyes back to the standoffish Shizune, who with a single huff of confirmation returns to looking away with her arms crossed."
    "Torno a moure els ulls cap a la distant Shizune, que amb un esbufec de confirmació torna a apartar-me la mirada tot plegant els braços."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3511
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_27d33e03:

    # hi "Why was Shizune trying to wake me up?"
    hi "Per què intentava despertar-me, la Shizune?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3516
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_40cc0f51:

    # mi "Shicchan wanted to give you the handouts the substitute teacher gave out while Hicchan was sleeping."
    mi "La Shicchan volia donar-te les fotocòpies que el professor substitut ens ha donat mentre estaves dormint."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3518
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2fe13430:

    # hi "Handouts?"
    hi "Fotocòpies?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3526
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_07b92199:

    # "I suddenly find two sheets of paper thrust down in front of my face."
    "De cop i volta, em trobo amb dos fulls de paper davant de la cara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3532
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a4388b8f:

    # "Following the hand holding them, I see the still-pouting figure looking down at me with a distinct scowl. I guess I really am in the wrong here."
    "Segueixo la mà que els sosté, i veig una figura que encara fa morros, i que em mira amb molt mala cara. Suposo que m'he equivocat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3534
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9a4acbaa:

    # hi "…Ah. Um, sorry about that."
    hi "... Ah. Daixò, em sap greu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3538
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9473f1f5:

    # "No dice. Her irritated face still holds. I clasp my hands together and flick my head downwards in apology."
    "No funciona. Encara fa mala cara. Ajunto les mans i abaixo el cap en senyal de disculpes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3540
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_03ff4492:

    # hi "Very, very sorry."
    hi "Em sap molt i molt de greu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3552
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ebdef7f4:

    # "She huffs and simply drops the papers on the desk."
    "Esbufega i deixa caure els papers sobre l'escriptori."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3554
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4bf99ed5:

    # hi "Damn."
    hi "Òndia."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3560
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_31757b6a:

    # "I look up over my hands to see Shizune and Misha signing frantically to each other, a look of frustration on Shizune's face."
    "Miro per sobre de les mans i veig a la Shizune i la Misha signant amb desfici entre elles, la Shizune fa cara de frustració."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3565
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b33ba1f7:

    # shi "…!"
    shi "...!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3567
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_67dec14e:

    # "It looks to be less of a dialogue and more of a tirade, punctuated with sidelong glances at me. To say it's unsettling is an understatement."
    "Més que un diàleg, sembla una tirallonga, puntuada amb mirades cap a on soc jo. Dir que és inquietant és dir massa poc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3569
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aabbd89d:

    # hi "Um…"
    hi "Daixò..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3575
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4f5acc60:

    # "The two suddenly stop signing and look at me in unison, both having exactly the same look of disapproval. In one fluid motion, Misha's hand suddenly extends high above me and comes rocketing down."
    "De sobte deixen de signar i em miren alhora, totes dues ben bé amb la mateixa cara de retret. En un únic moviment fluid, la Misha, d'improvís, allarga la mà molt per sobre meu i me l'estavella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3582
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f1a52daa:

    # "Before I can even hope to react, my head is sent bouncing up and down like a jack-in-the-box." with vpunch
    "Sense deixar-me temps per reaccionar, em fa rebotar el cap amunt i avall, com si tingués una molla al cul." with vpunch

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3584
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9e538298:

    # "I quickly bring my hands to my head, more out of reflex than actual pain."
    "De seguida em poso les mans al cap, més per reflex que per dolor real."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3586
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_015aafc7:

    # hi "Ow! What was that for!?"
    hi "Au! A què ha vingut això?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3593
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7a387540:

    # "I open my eyes to see the two grinning at each other while exchanging an enthusiastic thumbs-up."
    "Obro els ulls i veig com riuen entre elles mentre intercanvien un senyal entusiàstic amb els polzes amunt."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3599
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_50c5b004:

    # mi "Shicchan says she forgives you now, Hicchan~!"
    mi "La Shicchan diu que ara ja et perdona, Hicchan!!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3601
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_00e7fea7:

    # hi "Could you forgive me with a little less force next time?"
    hi "Podria perdonar-me amb una mica menys de força la pròxima vegada?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3606
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_cb5680f2:

    # mi "Wahahahaha~!"
    mi "Pffhahahaha~!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3608
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_de7d4748:

    # "I look at the two with a blank face. Misha and Shizune: one, Hisao: nil."
    "Les miro amb una cara inexpressiva. Misha i Shizune: un, Hisao: zero."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3613
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ef2b123c:

    # shi "…"
    shi "..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3618
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1197fc0f:

    # mi "Oh, Shicchan also says that you should check your student mail more often~!"
    mi "Ah, la Shicchan també diu que hauries de revisar el teu correu d'estudiant més sovint!!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3628
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d28b865a:

    # "She produces a bright yellow envelope and hands it over with an exuberant grin."
    "Em mostra un sobre de color groc radiant i me'l passa amb un somriure exuberant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3630
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b0a6dae5:

    # "Strange. Who could have written me a letter? Now is not the time and most definitely not the place to find out, though."
    "Que estrany. Qui podria haver-me escrit una carta? Però no és ni el moment ni, sens dubte, el lloc per a descobrir-ho."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3639
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5471717f:

    # "Giving up on the nap so cruelly stolen from me, I rub my forehead and slowly get up, putting the sheets and envelope in my bag before swinging it over my shoulder."
    "Renuncio a la becaina que m'han robat tan cruelment, em frego el front i m'aixeco lentament, posant els papers i el sobre a la bossa abans de penjar-me-la sobre l'espatlla."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3647
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fc57d361:

    # "I take a step back and move to depart with a small bow, while Misha clutches her sides laughing and Shizune nods back in a curt farewell."
    "Faig una passa enrere i em disposo a marxar amb una petita reverència, mentre la Misha s'agafa els costats tot rient i la Shizune fa un cop de cap per acomiadar-se."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3656
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b57fd2d5:

    # "I join the flow of students exiting the open door, and turn the corner into the hallway."
    "M'uneixo a la riada d'estudiants que surten per la porta oberta i giro per la cantonada cap al passadís."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3663
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b77ae1d7:

    # "…only to end up face to face with Hanako."
    "... i acabo cara a cara amb la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3665
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3cd5c53c:

    # hi "Whoa. Uh, hey Hanako."
    hi "Caram. Uh, ei, Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3670
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_398bdfe8:

    # ha "Good afternoon… Hisao."
    ha "Bona tarda... Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3675
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_df0d65a1:

    # "Silence falls between us as busily chatting students pass us by. She's fidgeting constantly, her eyes drawn to her rather unremarkable footwear."
    "Ens quedem en silenci mentre els estudiants, que parlen animadament, ens passen pel costat. No para de regirar-se nerviosa, amb els ulls clavats a les seves sabates discretes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3677
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bd441f57:

    # "I take the bridge of my nose in my fingers while I blink my eyes heavily in an attempt to make things seem clearer. I'm barely staying awake as it is."
    "M'agafo el pont del nas amb els dits mentre parpellejo amb força per intentar veure les coses més clares. Amb prou feines puc mantenir-me despert."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3679
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7ce4fd25:

    # hi "Hanako, you want to say something. What is it?"
    hi "Hanako, vols dir alguna cosa. Què passa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3684
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6a729400:

    # ha "U-um… I wanted to… give you this…"
    ha "U-um... Volia... donar-te això..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3686
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_34d1d59d:

    # hi "Hmm?"
    hi "Hmm?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3691
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2bc43c90:

    # "She holds out a small rectangular piece of paper. I blink again to make out the text through barely open eyes, slowly starting to make out what's written."
    "Em dona un trosset de paper rectangular. Torno a parpellejar per distingir el text amb els ulls mig oberts, i començo a entendre lentament què hi ha escrit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3697
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_29b04a72:

    # hi "…A shopping list?"
    hi "... Una llista de la compra?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3699
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_149fba9e:

    # "I look upwards, raising an eyebrow."
    "Miro enlaire, aixecant una cella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3704
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0d7192af:

    # ha "I usually go shopping with Lilly but I can't come, so…"
    ha "Normalment vaig a comprar amb la Lilly però no puc anar-hi, així que..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3706
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9e829355:

    # hi "You want me to run errands for you?"
    hi "Vols que et faci els encàrrecs?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3711
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bc79b556:

    # ha "I-it's okay if you don't want to! I just thought that, maybe, um…"
    ha "N-no passa res si no vols! Només pensava que, potser, um..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3713
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_542407a0:

    # "She's panicking. I sigh. Yet another battle lost, though this time by a weakly-fought surrender."
    "Està en pànic. Sospiro. Una altra batalla perduda, encara que aquesta vegada em rendeixo sense haver lluitat gaire."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3715
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9d00727a:

    # "I smile tiredly and rest a hand on her head to calm her down."
    "Somric sense esma i li poso la mà al cap per calmar-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3717
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e1a0fa8a:

    # hi "It's fine, I was going to go anyway. Just the stuff on this list?"
    hi "Està bé, hi volia anar de totes maneres. Només les coses d'aquesta llista?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3722
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1ab2d4ad:

    # "She nods then bows deeply, twice, as if to make her gratitude perfectly clear."
    "Assenteix i em fa una gran reverència, dues vegades, com per deixar claríssima la seva gratitud."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3727
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_37a687bb:

    # ha "W-we were going to meet outside the school gates at six… thank you, I was going to get it, but I need to study for the test tomorrow."
    ha "He-hem quedat a la sortida de l'escola a les sis... gràcies, anava a fer-ho, però he d'estudiar per a la prova demà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3729
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c1692ba6:

    # hi "Test? Ah, that's right, science. How're you doing with it?"
    hi "Prova? A, tens raó, la de ciències. Com ho portes?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3734
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_43435734:

    # "She brightens ever so slightly."
    "Se li il·lumina una mica la cara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3739
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_68dd8dff:

    # ha "I've been… spending more time on it than before. I think I can do… okay."
    ha "Li he dedicat... més temps que abans. Així que espero poder fer-ho... bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3741
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_de1dd8da:

    # hi "Good work, then."
    hi "Bona feina, doncs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3746
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ad66c6db:

    # "She too starts smiling, and much more earnestly than I at that."
    "També comença a somriure, i amb molta més força que jo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3748
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5a95ffe4:

    # "I have full confidence that I can do fine in it without any extra studying, but the fact that she's putting in the effort instead of just reading in the library is heartening."
    "Confio plenament que m'anirà bé sense estudiar de més, però el fet que estigui fent l'esforç en lloc de limitar-se a llegir a la biblioteca és reconfortant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3750
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8e218da8:

    # hi "I'll grab your stuff and take it to your dorm in the evening. Seeya."
    hi "Agafaré les teves coses i te les portaré al dormitori al vespre. Siau."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3758
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_eccdced4:

    # "With a small wave, we part ways."
    "Ens separem després d'acomiadar-nos amb la mà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3760
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d41f8cf9:

    # "I'll go do my homework before meeting Lilly. I should be able to take care of it in time."
    "Me'n vaig a fer els deures abans de trobar-me amb la Lilly. Hauria de poder-los acabar a temps."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3769
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_42391cd6:

    # "Wrangling with a particularly complicated math problem has caused me to be a little bit late for my meeting with Lilly."
    "Arribo una mica tard a trobar-me amb la Lilly per culpa d'un problema de matemàtiques especialment complicat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3771
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_25bd684a:

    # "Only a couple of minutes, but enough to make me step smartly out into the courtyard and to the school gate."
    "Només un parell de minuts, però prou per fer-me travessar de pressa al pati fins a la porta de l'escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3776
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_69fd5d75:

    # "I make a right turn and start my way towards the small town below, leaving a few students turning the other way to the bus station."
    "Giro a la dreta i començo a caminar cap al petit poble de sota, deixo uns quants estudiants que giren en sentit contrari cap a l'estació d'autobusos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3778
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3fde32e7:

    # "I slip my right hand into my pocket as I walk in the orange sunlight of dusk."
    "Em fico la mà dreta a la butxaca mentre camino a la llum ataronjada del sol del capvespre."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3780
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8d44efc8:

    # "Thankfully the sweltering summer heat's started to die down, making way for a pleasant cool breeze."
    "Afortunadament, la calor de l'estiu ja ha començat a calmar-se, i ha donat pas a un ventet fresc i agradable."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3786
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b5efbfe1:

    # "When I stretch my hands high above my head, a familiar figure takes form, cane in her right hand."
    "Quan estiro les mans per sobre del cap, agafa forma una figura familiar, amb un bastó a la mà dreta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3788
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6ccdbfa9:

    # hi "Ah, Lilly."
    hi "Ah, Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3794
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_716d8d47:

    # "She stops and turns around, swiveling her head slightly to try and work out exactly where the voice came from."
    "S'atura i es gira, gira una mica el cap per intentar esbrinar exactament d'on ve la veu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3796
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_452195d5:

    # hi "Hey. It's me."
    hi "Ei. Soc jo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3798
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9294c7b3:

    # "I quickly catch up to her, coming in beside her and matching her slow pace as we resume walking."
    "De seguida l'atrapo, arribo al seu costat i igualo el seu pas lent mentre torno a caminar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3803
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_09b2b4f1:

    # li "Good afternoon, Hisao."
    li "Bona tarda, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3805
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_adfacf09:

    # hi "Hi there."
    hi "Com va?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3812
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3048d166:

    # "I glance up at the sky."
    "Aixeco la vista cap al cel."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3814
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6db93071:

    # "A distinct tinge of orange discolors the clouds, washing the footpath in its light. Long shadows from the trees fall across the wide road down the hill."
    "Els núvols es tenyeixen de taronja i inunda la senda amb la seva llum. Les ombres llargues dels arbres s'estenen per l'àmplia carretera que baixa pel turó."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3820
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3372b531:

    # li "So, Hisao, what brings you here?"
    li "Llavors, Hisao, què fas aquí?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3822
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_be581ac2:

    # hi "Just going to town to grab some groceries. Hanako sent me."
    hi "Només vaig a la ciutat per agafar una mica de menjar. La Hanako m'ha enviat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3827
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bdfccf3f:

    # li "Hanako sent you?"
    li "La Hanako t'ha enviat?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3829
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a0adb89e:

    # hi "Yeah, said she needed to study for a test tomorrow. I was going to come down anyway, so I'll just buy her stuff as well."
    hi "Sí, ha dit que necessitava estudiar per a la prova de demà. Anava a baixar de totes maneres, així que no em fa res comprar les seves coses."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3831
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2f836cb4:

    # "Unspoken is that Lilly really could use some help to get food, but it's an obvious fact that neither of us needs to state."
    "No dic que la Lilly realment necessita ajuda per comprar menjar, però és un fet tan obvi que no cal que cap dels dos ho afirmem."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3836
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_17ca0b34:

    # li "It's good to hear she's studying for it."
    li "M'alegro de saber que està estudiant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3838
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ed68a402:

    # hi "I thought the same thing when she asked me to come with you."
    hi "He pensat el mateix quan m'ha demanat que vingués amb tu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3843
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5f3ba4a5:

    # "We continue walking down the street, the familiar sound of her cane echoing through the air as we go. Except for the occasional passing car and the leaves whispering in the branches, there's a blissful silence."
    "Seguim caminant pel carrer, el so familiar del seu bastó ressona per l'aire mentre avancem. Excepte pel so puntual d'algun cotxe que passa i pel murmuri de les fulles sobre les branques, regna un silenci feliç."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3845
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c641880b:

    # "Thank God I can finally relax for the first time today."
    "Gràcies a Déu, avui per fi puc relaxar-me per primera vegada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3857
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_75434c45:

    # "I glance over at Lilly."
    "Miro cap a la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3859
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8745a9ae:

    # "That porcelain face of hers never seems to lack that air of relaxed confidence. I guess the same could be said of her personality, too."
    "Sembla que mai li falti aquest aire de confiança plàcida a la cara de porcellana que té. Suposo que també es podria dir el mateix de la seva personalitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3861
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aa80a94e:

    # "As she silently walks, her face remaining pointed to the street ahead of her, I look ahead and savor the cool air blowing over my face."
    "Mentre camina en silenci, amb la cara apuntant cap al carrer que té al front, miro cap endavant i assaboreixo l'aire fresc que em bufa sobre la cara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3863
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_53ae037b:

    # "This is probably the calmest moment I've had since the about-face my life took so recently."
    "Aquest deu ser el moment més tranquil que he tingut des que la meva vida va fer un gir tan radical."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3865
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c297bed3:

    # "To have it while walking to get some groceries. What a weird life."
    "Tenir-lo mentre anem a comprar menjar. Quina vida més rara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3872
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b953049b:

    # "I feel the crumpled-up note rubbing against my hand in my pocket, and pull it out to check its contents."
    "Noto la nota arrugada que em frega la mà dins la butxaca i la trec per comprovar-ne el contingut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3874
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d1f78157:

    # hi "Let's see here… eggs, bread, cereal, thyme, lettuce, shaved ham…"
    hi "A veure... ous, pa, cereals, farigola, enciam, pernil tallat a rodanxes..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3879
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7d23dc59:

    # li "That sounds like quite a bit to carry back along with your own."
    li "Això sembla ser força cosa per portar de tornada amb les teves coses."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3881
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d20c0fdc:

    # hi "Yeah. Just how much does this girl eat anyway?"
    hi "Sí. De totes maneres, quant menja aquesta noia?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3883
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1f51cac7:

    # "My mind suddenly clicks that yes, there actually is a person beside me."
    "De sobte, recordo que sí, que hi ha una persona al meu costat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3885
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_011dd1ad:

    # hi "W-wait, I mean…"
    hi "E-espera, volia dir..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3890
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7d154311:

    # "She laughs wholeheartedly."
    "Es peta de riure."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3895
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_07dc4ff3:

    # li "My my, Hisao."
    li "Ara pla, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3897
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a5630c95:

    # "Her giggles punctuate her words, though she's making little effort to suppress them."
    "La seva rialleta acompanya les seves paraules, tot i que no fa cap esforç per suprimir-les."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3902
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_34b046cb:

    # li "Quite direct today, aren't we?"
    li "Avui estàs molt directe, no?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3904
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d457e996:

    # hi "Yeah, you got me there. Still, it is quite a bit."
    hi "Sí, aquí m'has pillat. Igualment, hi ha força cosa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3909
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0665d233:

    # li "Usually I go shopping with Hanako, so I know what she buys. It's the same thing every week."
    li "Normalment vaig a comprar amb la Hanako, així que sé què compra. Sol ser el mateix cada setmana."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3911
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c3026676:

    # hi "Huh. She a good cook?"
    hi "Eh. És bona cuinera?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3916
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_cfd26a7b:

    # "She gives a nervous giggle."
    "Fa una rialleta nerviosa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3918
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b42c8967:

    # li "It's usually me who ends up cooking. I used to do so for Akira, so it's no problem doing it for Hanako as well."
    li "Normalment soc jo qui acaba cuinant. Solia fer-ho per l'Akira, així que no m'és cap problema fer-ho també per la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3920
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_160b8e85:

    # hi "You can cook? But…"
    hi "Ja pots cuinar? Si..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3925
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2eeacef7:

    # "A short hum with an amused lilt emanates from beside me. I wonder if the fact that she seems amused by my comments so often is actually genuine, or rather just from a want to make me more comfortable in addressing her blindness?"
    "Del meu costat en surt un breu cantusseig amb un ritme divertit. Em pregunto si és realment genuí que sembli alegre pels meus comentaris tot sovint o, més aviat, ho fa perquè em senti més còmode amb la seva ceguesa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3930
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_15bf6568:

    # li "There are ways around it. Some meals are more difficult to cook than others because of being unable to see what I'm doing, but it usually only takes a little more time. Fingers can double as very useful measurement tools, for example."
    li "Hi ha maneres de trampejar-ho. Alguns plats són més complicats de cuinar que d'altres perquè no puc veure què estic fent, però normalment només tardo una mica més. Per exemple, els dits poden ser molt útils com a eines per mesurar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3932
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b27105a5:

    # "It makes sense, but she'd have to be pretty careful not to hurt herself. I wonder how many times that's happened, given that it sounds like she's cooked alone for possibly years while Akira worked and her parents were gone."
    "Té sentit, però hauria d'anar amb compte de no fer-se mal. Em pregunto quantes vegades li haurà passat, ja que sembla com si hagués estat sola durant anys mentre l'Akira treballava i els seus pares no hi eren."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3934
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1417aabb:

    # "With that, the conversation trails off."
    "I així, la conversa s'acaba."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3936
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6864a99b:

    # "Compared to the awkward silences of Hanako, Lilly seems genuinely content to say what she thinks and stay quiet when there's nothing to say."
    "En comparació amb els silencis incòmodes de la Hanako, la Lilly sembla realment contenta de dir allò que pensa i quedar-se callada quan no té res a dir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3938
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a034634e:

    # "The slick road under my feet is bathed in an orange glow, the occasional fallen leaf crunching underfoot as we walk. I let out a deep yawn, my lack of sleep coming back to haunt me."
    "El paviment relliscós per on passem està banyat en una lluïssor taronja, alguna fulla cau de tant en tant, tot cruixint sota els peus mentre caminem. Deixo anar un badall profund, em persegueix la falta de son."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3943
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_28fd2af4:

    # li "Did you not get much sleep last night?"
    li "Que no vas dormir gaire ahir a la nit?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3945
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ed399d51:

    # hi "I couldn't sleep at all for the last two nights. Probably insomnia."
    hi "No he pogut dormir res aquestes dues últimes nits. Dec patir d'insomni."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3952
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1dff58e8:

    # "Lilly's face suddenly becomes worried. It feels like a personal failure every time she gets worried about my well-being, even if it's genuinely nice to know someone cares."
    "De sobte, la Lilly fa cara de preocupada. Em sembla un fracàs personal cada vegada que es preocupa pel meu benestar, encara que sigui realment agradable saber que algú es preocupa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3954
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_da7bbb21:

    # li "You have insomnia? Aren't you going to see the nurse about it?"
    li "Pateixes d'insomni? No hauries d'anar a veure a l'infermer?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3956
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3e1040b8:

    # hi "Nah, no real need. It's happened before a few times. My meds screw with my sleeping occasionally."
    hi "No, no cal pas. M'ha passat algunes altres vegades. La medicació de vegades em fot enlaire el son."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3961
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c26fa9ff:

    # li "…Ah. I'm… sorry."
    li "... Ah. Em... sap greu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3963
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e8f3cbd3:

    # hi "Come on, it's not your fault. At least I shouldn't have any trouble getting to sleep tonight."
    hi "Au va, nique fos culpa teva. En tot cas, no hauria de tenir problemes per dormir aquesta nit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3968
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a8b9c62c:

    # li "You do worry me sometimes."
    li "De vegades em preocupes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3970
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d4ff12b9:

    # hi "I… worry you?"
    hi "Et... preocupo?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3972
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0cd9d769:

    # "I reach around and scratch the back of my neck. I kind of want to address this."
    "Estiro la mà per gratar-me la nuca. D'alguna manera, vull tocar aquest tema."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3974
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_466b47b5:

    # hi "Hey, Lilly…"
    hi "Ei, Lilly..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3979
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_16b10efa:

    # li "Hmm?"
    li "Hmm?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3981
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f056deb6:

    # hi "I don't mean to sound weird, but… please try to forget about my heart condition."
    hi "No vull sonar estrany, però... si us plau, intenta oblidar-te del meu problema de cor."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3986
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_17e30856:

    # "She looks kind of lost. I hardly blame her."
    "Sembla una mica perduda. No la culpo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3988
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_443e1de5:

    # hi "I guess what I'm trying to get at is… just don't treat me differently because of it."
    hi "Suposo que el que vull dir és... no em tractis diferent per això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3993
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ac8d3fd8:

    # "She bows her head slightly, her white cheeks reddening almost imperceptibly."
    "Inclina el cap lleugerament, les seves galtes blanques s'enrogeixen tan poc que costa d'apreciar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3995
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8dbebeb2:

    # li "It's only natural to worry about those around you…"
    li "És normal preocupar-se pels que t'envolten..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:3997
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bed869bd:

    # hi "Well, it's still nice to know there's someone like that out there."
    hi "Bé, de totes maneres és agradable saber que hi ha gent així pel món."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4002
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4a6c8612:

    # "It may be somewhat embarrassing to say, but it's the truth. Lilly takes a breath to regain her composure and manages a gentle smile, though her cheeks remain flushed."
    "Fa una mica de vergonya dir-ho, però és la veritat. La Lilly agafa aire per refer-se i aconsegueix fer un somriure amable, tot i que encara té les galtes vermelles."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4004
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1d82ca4b:

    # "The final downhill walk to the store passes in silence."
    "L'última baixada fins a la botiga transcorre en silenci."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4011
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_9dcc8766:

    # "Storewoman" "Welcome!"
    "Botiguera" "Benvinguts!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4013
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_990b2716:

    # hi "I suppose I'll get my stuff first and Hanako's on the second round."
    hi "Suposo que primer agafaré les meves coses i les de la Hanako a la segona volta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4018
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d0f35177:

    # "I grab two well-worn red baskets from the stack beside the entrance and pass one to Lilly."
    "Agafo dues cistelles vermelles ben desgastades de la pila que hi ha al costat de l'entrada i li'n passo una a Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4030
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a1ddab84:

    # "Just as she did before, she lays it on the ground and slides her retracted cane between the basket's handles before picking it back up with her right hand."
    "Com li havia vist fer abans, la deixa a terra i fa lliscar el bastó retràctil entre les nanses de la cistella abans de tornar-la a agafar amb la mà dreta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4041
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_12330940:

    # "When she takes hold of my arm in her own, I'm surprised at just how fast this kind of casual contact became so natural. Mostly due to necessity, no doubt."
    "Quan m'agafa el braç, em sorprenc per la rapidesa amb què aquest tipus de contacte casual s'ha anat convertint en una cosa natural. Sobretot per necessitat, sens dubte."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4046
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6452ac38:

    # li "Shall we?"
    li "Som-hi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4050
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_21ce94c5:

    # hi "Sure."
    hi "Vinga."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4052
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5576141e:

    # "While we navigate around the store, the odd person occasionally passing us pays us no heed at all. It's nice, compared to the stares and whispers around the city."
    "Mentre passegem per la botiga, la gent que ens passa de tant en tant pel costat no ens para cap mena d'atenció. És agradable, comparat amb les mirades i els xiuxiuejos que ens trobem per la ciutat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4057
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f14ab533:

    # "As we reach each aisle, I quickly check with Lilly what she needs and grab it along with what I want, putting our items into their respective baskets."
    "Cada cop que arribem a un passadís, li demano un moment a la Lilly què necessita i li agafo juntament amb allò que vull jo hi poso cada cosa a la cistella que toca."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4059
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_08b195ba:

    # "It's an odd feeling, to be depended on so much for something so basic as shopping. Hanako would be practically a necessity for her to pick out what she wants, after all."
    "És una sensació estranya, dependre tant d'algú per fer una cosa tan bàsica com anar a comprar. Ben mirat, realment necessita a la Hanako perquè li triï tot allò que vol."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4061
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6de5cccf:

    # hi "Right, I'm pretty much done with both my stuff and Hanako's. You needing anything else, Lilly?"
    hi "D'acord, he acabat tant amb les meves coses com amb les de la Hanako. Necessites res més, Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4066
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_37f84067:

    # li "No, this should be everything."
    li "No, ja ho tinc tot."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4068
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_efb676c2:

    # hi "Off we go, then."
    hi "Som-hi, doncs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4070
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aa1a8a4c:

    # "Oddly, there's a queue a mile long. Considering the store's only large enough to warrant one counter, seems like it'll take a while."
    "Per estrany que sembli, hi ha un quilòmetre de cua. Si tenim en compte que a la botiga només hi cap un taulell, sembla que trigarem una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4072
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4bf99ed5_1:

    # hi "Damn."
    hi "Òndia."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4077
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_98d0de8c:

    # "Lilly gives an inquisitive look, unable to see the reason for my complaint."
    "La Lilly fa una mirrada interrogativa, incapaç de veure per què em queixo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4079
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_43727403:

    # hi "The queue's really long. Looks like we'll have to wait."
    hi "La cua és molt llarga. Sembla que haurem d'esperar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4084
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_25828eea:

    # li "How strange."
    li "Que estrany."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4086
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_5c6c741e:

    # "Sharing the same mood of resignation, we reluctantly take our place at the end of the line."
    "Tot compartint la mateixa actitud de resignació, ocupem, sense ganes, el nostre lloc al final de la cua."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4090
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3f8dccf5:

    # "One person finishes, the line moves up. Another person finishes, the line moves up."
    "Una persona acaba, la cua avança. Una altra persona acaba, la cua avança."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4092
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_124c39e9:

    # "By the time we finally reach the head of the line, I'm so close to dozing off that Lilly has to gently pat me on the back for me to move up."
    "Quan per fi arribem al davant de la cua, em falta tan poc per quedar-me adormit que la Lilly m'ha de fer un copet a l'esquena perquè avanci."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4097
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_44d14e70:

    # li "Hisao… Hisao!"
    li "Hisao… Hisao!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4101
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_90256f2c:

    # hi "Hmm? Ah, sorry."
    hi "Hmm? Ah, perdona."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4106
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0de25e28:

    # "She gives a short sigh of consternation as I move up, getting the groceries for Hanako and me put into separate bags."
    "Sospira consternada mentre avanço, fent que em posin el menjar de la Hanako i el meu en bosses separades."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4108
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7ff8d8cd:

    # "Storewoman" "Thank you, please come again!"
    "Storewoman" "Gràcies, que vagi bé!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4116
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e32fa01b:

    # "By the time we emerge from the store, Lilly's holding a single bag while I struggle to carry four, both hands well and truly full. It's a lot of work, but thankfully the items in them are light."
    "Quan sortim de la botiga, la Lilly porta una bossa mentre jo m'escarrasso per portar-ne quatre, totes dues mans ben plenes. És molta feina, però per sort les coses que duc no pesen gaire."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4118
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4cc243c5:

    # "Even without looking skyward it's obvious that a surprising amount of time's passed, the road outside being dark and lit by streetlamps."
    "Fins i tot sense mirar el cel, és obvi que ha passat molt més temps del que pensava, la carretera de fora es veu fosca i il·luminada pels fanals."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4123
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4c021530:

    # "Once Lilly retrieves her cane, we set out back to the dormitories the way we came, leaving the welcoming warm glow of the store."
    "Un cop la Lilly recupera el bastó, tornem als dormitoris pel camí que hem vingut, deixant enrere la calidesa de la botiga."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4130
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_bfcff13a:

    # "Despite the road being empty of cars, the full bags abundantly make up for the lack of noise, constantly clunking and squeaking together."
    "Tot i que la carretera està buida de cotxes, les bosses plenes compensen de sobres la falta de soroll, sense parar de fer sorolls mentre van xocant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4135
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b8c62053:

    # li "My my, Hisao, it's good to find that you're eating well."
    li "Caram, Hisao, m'alegra que mengis tan bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4137
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c136f60b:

    # hi "I'm a growing guy after all, I need to eat all I can!"
    hi "Al cap i a la fi, encara estic creixement, necessito menjar tot el que pugui!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4142
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8f4eab61:

    # li "Hmm… it must be nice, being a man."
    li "Hmm... deu estar bé, això de ser un home."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4144
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3798bf3f:

    # hi "W-what?"
    hi "Q-què?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4146
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_eb3d38f0:

    # "Seemingly not noticing, or ignoring, my surprise at the completely out-of-left-field comment, she continues on without missing a beat."
    "Sense adonar-se'n o tot ignorant la meva sorpresa pel seu comentari tan fora de lloc, continua sense perdre el ritme."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4151
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_88eca837:

    # li "Weight doesn't really bother you when eating, most of the time."
    li "Normalment, el pes no et preocupa a l'hora de menjar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4153
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c408f346:

    # hi "I get what you mean. Women tend to worry about stuff like that more than we do, I guess."
    hi "Entenc què vols dir. Les dones tendiu a preocupar-vos per aquestes coses més que nosaltres, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4158
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_77396e19:

    # li "Exactly. It makes me somewhat envious, to be honest."
    li "Exactament. Em fa una mica d'enveja, si et soc sincera."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4160
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_29792541:

    # hi "Well, it's not like we can outright ignore it."
    hi "A veure, nosaltres tampoc ho podem ignorar del tot."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4162
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_500a35f5:

    # "With an affirmative nod, we continue on our walk."
    "Assenteix afirmativament i seguim caminant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4164
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ef765caa:

    # hi "Huh, that's right."
    hi "Huh, tens raó."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4169
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d78581af:

    # li "What is it?"
    li "Què passa?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4171
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c1aab370:

    # hi "Hanako mentioned your birthday was earlier this year. Do anything special for it?"
    hi "La Hanako m'ha comentat que el teu aniversari va ser a principis d'aquest any. Vas fer alguna cosa especial?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4176
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_3a7dadec:

    # "She gives a long pause, lost in thought for a few seconds as she recalls the event."
    "Fa una llarga pausa, perduda en els pensaments durant uns segons tot recordant què va fer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4181
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d73a329c:

    # li "Not really. It was just Hanako and me having a little party during the night after school."
    li "De fet, no. Vam ser només la Hanako i jo fent una festeta durant la nit després de l'escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4183
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4fadebeb:

    # hi "Your birthday's supposed to be a big event, you know."
    hi "Se suposa que el teu aniversari és un gran dia, saps."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4185
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_075cdabd:

    # "Sounds like a pretty lonely way to spend a birthday, just her and Hanako staying overnight."
    "Sembla una manera molt solitària de passar un aniversari, només ella i la Hanako passant la nit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4187
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_aa952473:

    # "Birthdays always felt like a family occasion for me. They were a time when, in spite of their full-time jobs, both my parents would make an effort to be there for the day or at least for a party beforehand."
    "Els aniversaris sempre m'han semblat una celebració familiar. Un moment en què els meus pares, malgrat que treballessin a temps complet, feien un esforç per ser allà aquell dia o almenys per celebrar-lo abans."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4189
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c46631b1:

    # "It reminds me of how Lilly mentioned she hadn't seen her family in such a long time, and even ended up moving away from Akira's house afterwards."
    "Em recorda quan la Lilly em va dir que no havia vist la seva família des de feia temps, i que fins i tot va acabar marxant de casa l'Akira més tard."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4191
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d0e1bfaf:

    # "But I guess it's the same in situations as mundane as these. Considering her inability to read the packaging, just getting groceries would be a pain without somebody else around."
    "Però suposo que és el mateix en aquest tipus de situacions mundanes. Si tenim en compte que no pot llegir els paquets, només el fet d'aconseguir menjar ha de ser una tortura si no tens algú més al voltant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4193
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1bee66fd:

    # "In the end, she just has Hanako and me, and Akira when she's off from work."
    "Al final, només ens té a la Hanako i a mi, i a l'Akira quan està fora de la feina."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4195
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_65faf027:

    # "Be that as it may, she still seems to have many more distant friends among the students, not to mention people like Yuuko."
    "Sigui com sigui, sembla que també té molts amics més llunyans entre els estudiants, per no parlar de gent com la Yuuko."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4197
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0e59f486:

    # "It seems to be her own choice that there's such a separation between those who are close to her, and those who she only socializes with."
    "Sembla que ella mateixa faci una separació entre aquells que estan a prop seu, i aquells amb qui només socialitza."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4199
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b7937c23:

    # "It humbles me a little to see how much Lilly seems to have her life set up and going just as she wants."
    "M'humilia una mica veure fins a quin punt sembla que la Lilly té la vida muntada i funcionant tal com vol."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4201
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fcf05cfa:

    # "Yet Hanako is there for her to celebrate her birthday, and I'm here helping her with shopping. It's a weird kind of symbiosis, I suppose."
    "Tot i això, la Hanako va ser-hi per celebrar el seu aniversari, i jo estic aquí ajudant-la a anar a comprar. És una espècie estranya de simbiosi, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4206
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f712ac2b:

    # li "Are you all right, Hisao?"
    li "Estàs bé, Hisao?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4208
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_47b6c948:

    # hi "Sorry?"
    hi "Perdona?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4210
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_91a64b97:

    # li "You just seemed to go very quiet, that's all."
    li "Semblaves molt callat, només això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4212
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_29370ca7:

    # hi "Ah, sorry. I was just thinking."
    hi "Ho sento. Només pensava."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4217
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ff06eaa7:

    # li "Oh?"
    li "Oh?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4237
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8fd2fb11:

    # "Eventually we get to the girl's dormitories, both my arms aching from the weight of two sets of groceries."
    "Al final arribem als dormitoris de les noies, em fan mal els braços pel pes dels dos parells de bosses de menjar a cada mà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4239
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a8bd7764:

    # hi "Hah… we're finally here. Phew."
    hi "Ah... per fi hem arribat. Uf."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4249
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_f66bd1eb:

    # "I bend down to wipe my forehead with the back of my hand. Lilly stops in front of her door and sets down her bag, fishing around in her pocket for the key."
    "M'ajupo per eixugar-me el front amb el dors de la mà. La Lilly s'atura davant de la porta, deixa la bossa i busca la clau dins la butxaca."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4254
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e2967411:

    # li "Thank you, Hisao. I really appreciate your help."
    li "Gràcies, Hisao. Aprecio molt la teva ajuda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4256
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_935469e8:

    # hi "Ah, this is nothing."
    hi "Ah, no és res."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4261
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_e460ead2:

    # li "It might be nothing to you, but it's… definitely something for me."
    li "Pot ser que no sigui res per a tu, però és... definitivament molt per a mi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4272
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_616d9289:

    # "And with that, she steps through her door, closing it behind her."
    "I després d'això, travessa la porta i la tanca darrere seu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4274
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c9e3031e:

    # "I blink. Those were nothing but honest thanks, but I can't help feeling something different about them."
    "Parpellejo. Això era un agraïment sincer, però no puc evitar sentir una cosa diferent."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4276
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_150a3fda:

    # "Anyway, I have something else to do before I can mull on that at my leisure."
    "De totes maneres, he de fer una altra cosa abans de poder reflexionar-hi tranquil·lament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4288
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_91e36db1:

    # "I turn back to the door to Hanako's room and proceed to knock twice in quick succession, the bags still in my hand rustling together."
    "Em giro cap a la porta de l'habitació de la Hanako i li faig dos trucs seguits, amb les bosses encara a la mà fregant-se."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4296
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8469acb7:

    # "After a couple of seconds, the door slowly opens. If one weren't looking closely, they could be forgiven for thinking it hadn't moved at all."
    "Al cap d'un parell de segons, la porta s'obre lentament. Si un no s'hi fixa bé, podria arribar a pensar que no s'ha mogut gens."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4298
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_25dce765:

    # "I twist my head to the side to try and peer through the tiny sliver of a gap between the door and the doorframe."
    "Em giro cap a un costat per intentar mirar a través del petit forat que hi ha entre la porta i el marc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4300
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_de0e367f:

    # hi "Hey Hanako, I've got your stuff."
    hi "Ei, Hanako, tinc les teves coses."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4306
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_730fbd1d:

    # ha "Ah!"
    ha "Ah!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4313
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_309f9190:

    # "With that, she opens the door completely, making her plain room visible over her shoulder. Sparsely decorated, it's probably even more unremarkable than my room."
    "Dit això, obre de bat a bat la porta, i deixa veure la seva senzilla per sobre l'espatlla. Poc decorada, segurament és encara més discreta que la meva."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4315
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0e628dc8:

    # "I hold out my right arm, both bags almost pulling it straight back down with their weight."
    "Estiro el braç dret, les dues bosses me'l tornen a tirar cap avall pel pes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4320
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_4267d6cc:

    # ha "Th-thank you, Hisao."
    ha "Gr-gràcies, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4325
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_6b7942b1:

    # ha "I'm sorry to make you… carry them all this way."
    ha "Perdona que t'hagi... fet portar això fins aquí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4327
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b2a4ffeb:

    # hi "It's fine, don't worry. Just don't make me do it every day, okay?"
    hi "No passa res, no et preocupis. No em facis fer-ho cada dia, eh?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4332
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b4655e25:

    # "I pass the bags to her as I give a lighthearted chuckle. After the initial transfer of weight she manages to take them easily."
    "Li passo les bosses mentre deixo anar una rialleta despreocupada. Després de l'intercanvi inicial de pes, aconsegueix agafar-les fàcilment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4334
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ad86357c:

    # hi "I'll be off then. 'Night, Hanako."
    hi "Marxo ja. Bona nit, Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4339
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d01bac3a:

    # ha "Good night. Um, s-see you in class… tomorrow…"
    ha "Bona nit. Um, e-ens veiem demà... a classe..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4346
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_0e4b04a5:

    # "With a deep bow, her groceries still held in both hands, she steps back and shuts the door."
    "Després d'una gran reverència, amb les bosses encara a les mans, tira enrere i tanca la porta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4353
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_626096e5:

    # "Making my way back to my own dorm, I put one bag into my other hand to balance them out."
    "Torno al meu dormitori, i em poso una de les bosses a l'altra mà per equilibrar-les."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4355
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_36cac368:

    # "Even as I do so, I can't get Lilly's lighthearted smile out of my mind. When I'd first met her, it would have been nearly impossible to imagine her like that."
    "Mentre ho faig, no em puc treure del cap el somriure alegre de la Lilly. M'hauria estat quasi impossible imaginar-la així quan la vaig conèixer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4357
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1095c053:

    # "Indeed, it feels like we've become closer in the past few weeks since I first got to know both her and Hanako."
    "De fet, sembla que ens hem apropat més últimament, des que les vaig conèixer tant a ella com a la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4359
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a4f22b42:

    # "The time that I spend with her each day. The small exchanges of happiness we share. Those small moments of joy as I get closer to her."
    "El temps que cada dia passo amb ella. Els petits intercanvis de felicitat que compartim. Aquells petits moments d'alegria a mesura que m'hi apropo més."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4361
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_fb454ff6:

    # "I'm far from certain, but I don't think these are just the normal feelings of friendship."
    "No n'estic segur, però no crec que aquests siguin els sentiments normals d'una amistat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4366
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_d4fcca5b:

    # "Once I return to my room, I store away my groceries and begin getting ready for the night."
    "Quan torno a la meva habitació, guardo el menjar i començo a preparar-me per dormir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4376
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_23d9a7aa:

    # "I swap the school books in my bag for those I'll need tomorrow, pulling out the yellow envelope Misha gave me earlier in the process."
    "Canvio els llibres de l'escola pels que necessitaré demà, i també trec el sobre groc que m'ha donat abans la Misha."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4378
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_075af758:

    # "I got so sidetracked by one thing after another that I couldn't deal with it earlier. Who could have written me, I wonder?"
    "M'he distret fent una cosa darrere l'altra i no me n'he pogut ocupar abans. Qui em podria haver escrit?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4380
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_51fbc4ee:

    # "The name neatly adorning the back of the envelope freezes me in my tracks. It's been so long since I've seen her writing, there's little chance I could have identified it as hers otherwise."
    "El nom que decora amb bona lletra la part posterior em deixa gelat. Fa tant de temps que no veig la seva lletra que, d'una altra manera, no l'hauria pogut reconèixer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4382
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_a9c40d09:

    # "'Iwanako.'"
    "\"Iwanako.\""

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4384
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7511a44e:

    # "Why… should she have written me? I can't think of any good reason for her to do this."
    "Per què... m'hauria d'haver escrit? No se m'acut cap raó bona perquè ho hagi fet."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4386
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_7a7545fa:

    # "I almost don't open the letter, but there'd be little point to that. If I just left it alone, its mere existence would gnaw at me until I did something about it."
    "Estic a punt de no obrir la carta, però no tindria gaire sentit. Si simplement la deixés de banda, la seva mera existència em turmentaria fins que fes alguna cosa al respecte."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4393
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_daecc507:

    # "I look down at the piece of paper on my desk, its bright and summery decoration beaming happily at me."
    "Miro el tros de paper que hi ha a la meva taula, amb una decoració brillant i estiuenca que em somriu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4395
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_8adb0ce8:

    # "The lettering is in pink, jarring badly with the yellow sunflower border on the card. The handwriting is neat, the characters having been written thoughtfully and with an unusual amount of care."
    "Les lletres són de color rosa, contrasten amb la vora de groc gira-sol de la targeta. La cal·ligrafia és impecable, i els caràcters estan escrits amb especial atenció i meticulositat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4397
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b620de73:

    # "I'd barely given the letter a second thought when it was given to me, but now I can't get its contents out of my mind."
    "Amb prou feines he pensat en la carta quan me l'han donat, però ara no em puc treure el contingut del cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4399
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4402
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_511e7377:

    # n "{vspace=90}While I'd like to say that I don't know why she used such an old-fashioned method of communication, considering a phone call or an email would be both much faster and easier, the answer feels obvious enough given the content."
    n "{vspace=90} M'agradaria dir que no sé per què ha utilitzat un mètode de comunicació tan antiquat, si tenim en compte que una trucada o un correu electrònic serien molt més ràpids i senzills, però la resposta sembla força òbvia atès el contingut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4404
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_1c007415:

    # n "A letter leaves a comfortable distance between the sender and the recipient. Unlike a phone, it isn't required that you engage in conversation, and unlike email, there is less expectation of an immediate reply."
    n "Una carta deixa una distància còmoda entre el remitent i el destinatari. A diferència d'un telèfon, no és necessari entaular una conversa, i a diferència del correu electrònic, no s'espera una resposta immediata."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4406
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_c81f1e35:

    # n "{vspace=30}Statements such as 'the third-years seem to be very anxious about the final exams,' and 'it's so weird to think we are already seniors, isn't it?' are just smalltalk. Smalltalk that could have been achieved by simply replying to any of the messages I'd sent her while in hospital."
    n "{vspace=30} Paraules com ara \"sembla que els de tercer estan molt nerviosos pels exàmens finals\", i \"és tan estrany pensar que ja som al darrer any, oi?\" són només xerrameca. Xerrameca que podríem haver tingut si simplement hagués respost a qualsevol dels missatges que li vaig enviar mentre era a l'hospital."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4408
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76ba8aef:

    # n "The ending, though, is the true reason she sent this. The last couple of lines, added almost as an afterthought."
    n "El final, però, és la veritable raó per la qual ho ha enviat. L'últim parell de línies, afegides gairebé com de més a més."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4410
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76b2fe88_1:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4420
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_58f09731:

    # n "{vspace=210}'I wonder if we will meet again. Perhaps it's for the best if we don't?'"
    n "{vspace=210}\"Em pregunto si ens tornarem a veure. Potser serà millor si no ho fem?\""

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4422
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_727474c6:

    # n "It's a statement that should hurt. I've always heard breakups are nasty stuff, but it feels like this is simply a reaffirmation of what we both already knew instead."
    n "És una declaració que m'hauria de fer mal. Sempre he sentit dir que les ruptures són desagradables, però sembla que això no és més que una reafirmació d'allò que ja sabíem tots dos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4424
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_ad4e15d3:

    # n "It's the preceding text, no more than smalltalk, that makes me feel most uneasy. I can't figure out why, no matter how long I sit here and look down at this bright and summery piece of paper."
    n "És el text precedent, només xerrameca, allò que em fa sentir més incòmode. No entenc per què, per molt de temps que m'assegui aquí i miri aquest tros de paper brillant i estiuenc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4426
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_2b06ee39:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

    old "[_n_] {vspace=240}'If you would like to correspond with me, by all means write me back.'"
    new "[_n_] {vspace=240}\"Si vols tenir correspondència amb mi, escriu-me de nou\"."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4430
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_236438f2:

    # n "It's plainly obvious that this is not the type of letter to be replied to. In the end, this letter is no more than a simple abdication of responsibility; a final statement to reassure herself that our relationship is over."
    n "És evident que aquest no és el tipus de carta que s'ha de respondre. Al final, aquesta carta no és més que una simple abdicació de responsabilitats; una declaració final per a assegurar-se que la nostra relació ha acabat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4435
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_76b2fe88_2:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4440
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_87109222:

    # "As such, I find I have little problem in scrunching the letter and envelope into a ball and tossing it into the wastebin, ridding myself of its existence."
    "És per això que no tinc problema a fer una bola amb la carta i el sobre i llançar-los a la paperera, desfent-me així de la seva existència."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4442
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_164d2fe6:

    # "I go to bed with mixed feelings, cheated out of a pleasant evening by this intruder from the past."
    "Vaig al llit amb reserves, defraudat després d'una vetllada agradable per aquesta intrusa del passat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4444
translate ca a2_lilly_a_brief_history_of_thyme_b149940b:

    # "Ironically, it takes a while before I can manage to sleep."
    "Irònicament, em costa una mica dormir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4457
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_cf393bd8:

    # n "{vspace=120}I sweat profusely, awaiting the dreaded moment."
    n "{vspace=120}Suo a raig fet, esperant el moment temut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4462
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_2c6c44df:

    # n "Each tick of the clock tenses my muscles that much more, every minute making more hairs stand on end."
    n "Cada tic-tac del rellotge em tensa més i més els músculs, cada minut em posa més els pèls de punta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4464
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a96b8f51:

    # n "It's coming for me, I can feel it."
    n "Em ve a buscar, puc notar-ho."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4468
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_38ff58c0:

    # n "{vspace=60}{image=vfx/reddash.png}{color=#FF0000}{b}Death.{/b}{/color}"
    n "{vspace=60}{image=vfx/reddash.png}{color=#FF0000}{b}La mort.{/b}{/color}"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4470
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_53617801:

    # n "{vspace=60}Death in the form of a single sheet of paper."
    n "{vspace=60}La mort en forma d'un simple full de paper."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4474
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_76b2fe88:

    # nvl clear
    nvl clear

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4480
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c80a94cd:

    # "I take the small pile of papers from the student in front of me and pass it backwards after plucking off the top piece."
    "Agafo la petita pila de papers de l'estudiant que tinc al davant i la passo enrere després de treure'n la fulla de dalt de tot."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4482
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bd04f9e8:

    # "Looking to the top right of the page, I find my fears realized within that small red circle."
    "Miro la part superior dreta de la pàgina, veig les meves pors fetes realitat dins d'aquest petit cercle vermell."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4488
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_dc2619ca:

    # "Forty-three."
    "Quaranta-tres."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4490
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_38928e64:

    # "I hang my head and sigh in resignation. Cursing under my breath, I can feel the aura of a similar sentiment rising from the entire class. It's strange, but that fact lifts my mood by a minuscule amount."
    "Deixo caure el cap i sospiro resignat. Maleeixo entre dents, puc sentir l'aura d'un sentiment similar que sorgeix a tota la classe. És estrany, però aquest fet m'aixeca una mica l'ànim."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4492
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ab4d7549:

    # "Misery loves company, I suppose."
    "A la misèria li agrada la companyia, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4494
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_915cc5de:

    # "As the teacher opens her mouth, the room braces for the inevitable onslaught…"
    "Quan el professor obre la boca, la classe es prepara per a la inevitable envestida..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4500
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ba13a641:

    # "…only to be saved at the last minute."
    "... però ens salvem a l'últim minut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4502
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_41848011:

    # "We quickly move to collect our bags and leave for lunch post-haste, but the teacher delivers a parting broadside."
    "Ens afanyem a recollir les nostres bosses per anar a dinar, però el professor deixa anar un últim tret de comiat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4504
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9496a65d:

    # "Teacher" "We'll be discussing the test scores next lesson. Needless to say, there will be quite some discussion to be had."
    "Professor" "Parlarem dels resultats de les proves a la pròxima classe. No cal que us digui que tocarà discutir bastant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4506
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_36ebe3fc:

    # "A collective groan resounds from the class, now reduced to shuffling out dejectedly."
    "Ressona un gemec col·lectiu a la classe, que es redueix al so de les passes ensopides que surten arrossegant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4511
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_cb7f3439:

    # "I push the sheet into my bag as I walk along the hallway, crumpling it in the process. It's enough that such a troublesome letter ended up on my desk yesterday, and now this."
    "Entaforo el full dins la bossa mentre camino pel passadís, i s'arruga. Ja en tenia prou amb el fet que una carta inoportuna ahir acabés al meu escriptori, i ara això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4513
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e8ce3abe:

    # hi "I hate English…"
    hi "Odio l'anglès..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4517
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_0acb53ba:

    # mystery "HI—{w=0.3}SA—{w=0.3}O!"
    mystery "HI—{w=0.3}SA—{w=0.3}O!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4519
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bbd6f2e8:

    # "A stern female voice gruffly calls out from behind me."
    "Una veu femenina i decidida em crida amb des de darrere meu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4523
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_aaca95cd:

    # "I freeze on the spot, my face becoming like stone. It's as if I can feel my brain disconnecting from my body."
    "Em quedo gelat, i amb la cara de pedra. És com si pogués sentir que el cervell se'm desconnecta del cos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4525
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_8971236b:

    # "My eyes slowly shift right, trying to catch a glimpse of the disembodied voice."
    "Moc lentament els ulls cap a la dreta, per intentar veure a qui pertany la veu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4529
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e8eadcf9:

    # "…nothing?"
    "... res?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4531
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bc3bd82d:

    # "My face begins to slip as time passes, and I decide to risk turning my head. Ever so slowly, I twist it to the—"
    "A mesura que passa el temps, la cara comença a desdibuixar-se'm i decideixo arriscar-me a girar el cap. Molt a poc a poc, el giro cap a la..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4535
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_22d6f8a7:

    # hi "GYAAAAH!" with vpunch
    hi "UAAAAH!" with vpunch

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4537
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_2305000c:

    # "I jump into the air and drop my bag, yelling out in surprise."
    "Salto pels aires i deixo caure la bossa, tot cridant de sorpresa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4539
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_7f626672:

    # "As I recover and regain my composure, I turn to see… I should have known."
    "A mesura que em recupero i m'assereno, em giro i veig... Ho hauria d'haver sabut."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4541
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b18cd80c:

    # hi "Emi."
    hi "Emi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4548
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a87e7265:

    # emi "Gotcha, Hisao."
    emi "T'he pillat, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4550
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_5db94be3:

    # "She stands there with a mischievous grin on her face, hands forward and fingers pointed inwards. She was the one who jabbed my ribs with her fingers."
    "Està dreta amb un somriure entremaliat a la cara, les mans cap endavant i els dits cap endins. Ha estat ella qui m'ha clavat els dits a les costelles."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4552
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a22fca09:

    # "I look down at her with a grimace, rubbing my hair in frustration."
    "La miro amb una ganyota, i em frego els cabells tot frustrat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4554
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c3e042eb:

    # hi "That's no way to greet someone, you know."
    hi "Aquesta no és manera de saludar a algú, saps."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4559
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_377973b9:

    # emi "You have no sense of humor."
    emi "No tens sentit de l'humor."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4561
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_61a866a5:

    # hi "I left my sense of humor in my English class. Complain to the teacher if you want it given back to me."
    hi "M'he deixat el sentit de l'humor a classe d'anglès. Queixa't al professor si vols que me'l torni."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4566
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_56b94a94:

    # "She pulls her best puppy-dog eyes on me as she pouts. Lilly's managed to build up my resistance to the tactic, but Emi's short stature adds enough to the effect to make me relent."
    "Em posa la seva millora cara de pena mentre arrufa els llavis. La Lilly ha aconseguit augmentar la meva resistència a la tàctica, però la baixa estatura de l'Emi augmenta l'efecte prou per fer-me cedir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4568
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_3a1d852f:

    # hi "So, how are things? I haven't seen you around for a while."
    hi "Llavors, com et van les coses? Fa temps que no et veig."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4573
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e5a8c96f:

    # emi "Same old, same old. I run so fast, nobody wants to join me on my morning runs."
    emi "Res de nou. Corro tan ràpid que ningú vol acompanyar-me en les meves curses matutines."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4578
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_3edeb4aa:

    # emi "It's a real pain."
    emi "És una putada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4580
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9935e964:

    # "Her modesty never fails to amuse me."
    "La seva modèstia sempre em diverteix."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4585
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_46afa957:

    # emi "Although…"
    emi "Tot i que..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4587
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_12c320ca:

    # "Uh oh."
    "Ui ui."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4592
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_589c4751:

    # emi "You know what I'm thinking, don't you Hisao?"
    emi "Saps què estic pensant, oi Hisao?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4594
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_89442612:

    # "Wearing my emotions on my sleeve is one of my worst habits. She's seen right through me."
    "Anar amb les emocions a la mà és un dels meus pitjors hàbits. M'ha ben calat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4596
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f33cc201:

    # "Fortunately, I see somebody else approaching us that will give me an out."
    "Afortunadament, veig que algú més se'ns acosta i que em servirà d'excusa per marxar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4598
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_42a0e457:

    # hi "Oh, hi Hanako."
    hi "Uei, hola Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4607
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_605c983d:

    # "I give her a welcoming wave, and try my best at looking like I haven't noticed Emi's pouting face. She gives a small wave back."
    "La saludo amb la mà, i faig tot el possible per fer veure que no m'he adonat de la mala cara que posa l'Emi. Em torna un petit gest."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4612
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f1c59e8c:

    # ha "H-hello, Hisao… Emi."
    ha "H-hola, Hisao... Emi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4617
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_79af79c5:

    # emi "Hey Hanako."
    emi "Ei Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4619
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_7f1332b1:

    # hi "I'll join you and Lilly in a sec."
    hi "M'uneixo a tu i a la Lilly en un segon."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4621
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f57ce7ca:

    # hi "Actually, speaking of lunchtime company, it's odd to see you without Rin, Emi."
    hi "De fet, parlant de companyia a l'hora de dinar, és estrany veure't sense la Rin, Emi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4627
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a3e85df2:

    # emi "Ah! Rin!"
    emi "Ah! La Rin!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4634
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f3f6fcc4:

    # "Without a second word, she forgets all about us and bolts off up the hallway. She must've forgotten she was waiting for her."
    "Sense dir res més, s'oblida de nosaltres i surt corrents pel passadís. Deu haver oblidat que l'estava esperant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4636
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_6edfe935:

    # "Hanako and I stand speechless, only able to helplessly stand and watch this ball of seemingly boundless energy dash off."
    "La Hanako i jo ens quedem sense saber què dir, només som capaços de quedar-nos drets amb perplexitat i mirar com s'allunya aquesta bola d'energia aparentment il·limitada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4646
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c74ed047:

    # emi "Oh yeah, Hisao…"
    emi "Ah sí, Hisao..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4648
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b390c175:

    # "She suddenly stops herself just before vanishing around the corner to the rooftop staircase, spinning around to meet our bemused faces."
    "De sobte s'atura, just abans de desaparèixer per la cantonada on hi ha l'escala que va al terrat, gira i es troba amb les nostres cares desconcertades."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4653
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_aeb04147:

    # emi "I hate English too."
    emi "Jo també odio l'anglès."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4662
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bc6a3772:

    # "And with that, she disappears."
    "I tot seguit, desapareix."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4664
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_05238884:

    # "All I can do is hang my head and give a long sigh, thoroughly left in the dust."
    "Només puc abaixar el cap i deixar anar un llarg sospir, completament fet pols."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4669
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_530de478:

    # "As I hear a short giggle coming from behind me, I turn to see Hanako smiling at the corner my attacker rounded."
    "Sento un petit riure que ve de darrere meu, em giro i veig a la Hanako somrient a la cantonada on ha girat la meva atacant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4677
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c961089c:

    # "I pick up my dropped bag from the floor and quickly dust it off."
    "Agafo la bossa de terra i li trec ràpidament la pols."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4679
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c4feb367:

    # hi "Afternoon. Been busy?"
    hi "Bona tarda. Ocupada?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4684
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_0ced8f99:

    # ha "You don't… like English?"
    ha "No... t'agrada l'anglès?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4686
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_984f3a3b:

    # hi "Hmm? Oh, uh, nah. I had a test on it a while back, and Emi caught me brooding about the results."
    hi "Hmm? Oh, eh, no. He tingut una prova fa poc, i l'Emi m'ha pillat pensant els resultats."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4691
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_45940ae1:

    # ha "Ah, sorry…"
    ha "Ah, em sap greu..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4693
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_658ae0c3:

    # "She averts her gaze, guilt written onto her face. A casual observer would think she'd just accidentally reminded me of a dead relative."
    "Desvia la mirada, amb la culpa escrita a la cara. Un observador de passada pensaria que li he recordat accidentalment a un parent mort."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4695
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_3382a9ba:

    # hi "Come on, it's not your fault. How're you doing in it?"
    hi "Au va, no és pas culpa teva. Com t'ha anat a tu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4700
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d4ce6237:

    # "She looks up, though still avoids meeting my eyes."
    "Mira cap amunt, tot i que encara evita trobar-se amb els meus ulls."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4705
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_37138615:

    # ha "All right, I… suppose."
    ha "Prou bé... suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4707
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_025b84b6:

    # "An awkward silence passes. They seem all too common around Hanako."
    "Es fa un silenci incòmode. Semblen ser força comuns al voltant de la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4712
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_07dfe828:

    # ha "Oh, Lilly asked if… you'd like to join us for lunch on the roof."
    ha "Oh, la Lilly m'ha demanat si... voldries acompanyar-nos a dinar al terrat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4714
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_6508177d:

    # "I guess I don't exactly have any pressing engagements to attend to."
    "Suposo que ben bé no tinc cap compromís urgent per atendre."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4716
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_599ae248:

    # hi "Sure, I'll be right up."
    hi "I tant, ara aniré."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4721
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_dde0ee91:

    # ha "Um, I'll… go get my lunch from the cafeteria now… then."
    ha "Um, llavors... aniré a buscar el menjar a... la cafeteria."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4723
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_927d43d5:

    # hi "Go on. You don't need my approval to leave, you know."
    hi "Endavant. No necessites el meu permís per marxar, saps."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4728
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_198655f4:

    # ha "O-okay. I'll… be going then."
    ha "D-d'acord. Hi... vaig doncs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4735
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d82f88a4:

    # "She gives a skittish reply, a small nod and quickly makes off towards the cafeteria."
    "Em contesta nerviosa, fa un petit cop de cap i es dirigeix de pressa cap a la cafeteria."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4751
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e5a3182e:

    # "I guess she must've forgotten to bring lunch today. As I walk through the hallways, more and more students start to come out of classrooms and pass me, going in the same direction as Hanako went."
    "Suposo que es deu haver oblidat el dinar avui. Mentre camino pels passadissos, cada vegada més i més estudiants surten de les seves aules i em passen per davant, tot anant en la mateixa direcció que la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4753
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f939d98d:

    # "By the time I manage to make it to the stairs, I'm having to push my way past a busily chatting throng of students."
    "Quan aconsegueixo arribar a les escales, m'he d'obrir camí entre la multitud d'estudiants ocupats petant la xerrada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4763
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_116fd64a:

    # "I finally manage to get past the last of the crowd and round the staircase, slumping slightly in relief and slowing my pace before I open the door to the roof."
    "Per fi aconsegueixo passar l'últim tram de la multitud i arribo a l'escala, em relaxo alleujat i alenteixo el pas abans d'obrir la porta al terrat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4772
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_dcbf2b27:

    # hi "Ah, damn!"
    hi "Ah, merda!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4774
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ca0e48fa:

    # "I momentarily avert my eyes, all but blinded by the harsh summer sun."
    "Aparto un moment els ulls, quasi cegat pel fort sol d'estiu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4792
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_74df9be6:

    # mystery "Hmm?"
    mystery "Hmm?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4796
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_4eb993a0:

    # "As I slowly regain my vision, the surroundings finally take form."
    "A mesura que vaig recuperant la vista, l'entorn comença a agafar forma."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4798
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_76623e59:

    # "Lilly, Emi and Rin sit together on the rooftop, the top of the hilltop forest around Yamaku visible past the fence around them, as if to frame the view."
    "La Lilly, l'Emi i la Rin seuen juntes al terrat, el cim del bosc de voltant del Yamaku és visible més enllà de la tanca que l'envolta, com si emmarqués el paisatge."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4803
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9c84d970:

    # emi "Ah, Hisao!"
    emi "Ah, Hisao!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4809
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_dc3baf73:

    # "Lilly and Rin give a quick nod of acknowledgment and a deep nod of greeting respectively."
    "La Lilly i la Rin fan un cop de cap ràpid per saludar-me i una gran inclinació per saludar-se entre elles."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4811
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_8c193b67:

    # "I start walking towards the rather mismatched trio, and can't help marveling at the speed with which Emi devours the rest of her half-eaten banana."
    "Començo a caminar cap al trio, bastant desaparellat, i no puc evitar meravellar-me per la velocitat amb què l'Emi devora la meitat del plàtan que li queda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4813
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_fc819a6b:

    # hi "Hey. Strange to see you three together like this."
    hi "Ei. És estrany veure-us a les tres així juntes."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4818
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e02583f1:

    # li "It seems to have been quite the day of coincidences; Emi and Rin decided to eat on the roof just as Hanako and I decided to."
    li "Sembla que ha estat un dia de casualitats; l'Emi i la Rin han decidit menjar al terrat igual que la Hanako i jo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4823
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_32f554a8:

    # emi "You stole it! This spot was ours!"
    emi "Ens l'has robat! Aquest és el nostre lloc!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4825
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f558f1e1:

    # hi "Simmer down, you can't steal a place in the school."
    hi "Calma't, no pots robar un lloc a l'escola."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4827
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_7b758fcc:

    # "I plonk myself down beside Lilly, the four of us creating a semicircle."
    "Em deixo caure al costat de la Lilly, els quatre fem una rotllana."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4832
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b4c194b0:

    # rin "I think she is right."
    rin "Crec que té raó."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4834
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_48218b6b:

    # hi "You too?"
    hi "Tu també?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4839
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_04b4581d:

    # rin "The butterfly is her accomplice."
    rin "La papallona és la seva còmplice."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4841
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_614e8f0f:

    # hi "The butter…"
    hi "La papa..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4843
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9d192438:

    # "As I glance around, sure enough, a small yellow butterfly floats across my field of vision."
    "Miro al voltant i, efectivament, hi ha una papalloneta groga que em passa per davant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4845
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_3dbe61fa:

    # hi "So tell me, how did this butterfly help Lilly 'steal' this spot?"
    hi "Digues, com ha pogut aquesta papallona ajudar a la Lilly a \"robar\" aquest lloc?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4850
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_081d29a9:

    # rin "It scouted out our conversation and told her."
    rin "Va espiar la nostra conversa i li va dir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4852
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_7a5f7f56:

    # "I should've known better than to expect sound reasoning from Rin. Regardless, I guess it wouldn't hurt to play along."
    "Hauria d'haver sabut que no podia esperar un raonament sòlid de la Rin. Sigui com sigui, suposo que no em farà mal seguir-li el joc."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4854
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_562caac5:

    # hi "You're telling me she can talk to butterflies?"
    hi "M'estàs dient que pot parlar amb papallones?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4859
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_37c9fbbb:

    # rin "There are people who can talk to horses, called horse whisperers."
    rin "Hi ha gent que pot parlar amb els cavalls, se'ls diu murmuradors de cavalls."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4864
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_608c298f:

    # rin "Lilly must be a butterfly whisperer."
    rin "La Lilly deu ser una murmuradora de papallones."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4866
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_33ae872d:

    # "I bury my head in my hands as Emi rounds on her strange companion. She doesn't seem to share Rin's sense of humor."
    "Enterro el cap entre les mans mentre l'Emi s'encara amb la seva estranya companya. Sembla que no comparteix el mateix sentit de l'humor que la Rin."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4871
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_28745091:

    # emi "Whisperers don't work like that."
    emi "Els murmuradors no funcionen així."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4873
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_34d0001f:

    # "Emi and Rin continue their banter as I turn to Lilly, who's busily finishing off her small box of curry and rice."
    "L'Emi i la Rin segueixen fent broma mentre em giro cap a la Lilly, que està atrafegada acabant-se la seva carmanyoleta de curri i arròs."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4875
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b05883a9:

    # hi "So what brought you up here, anyway?"
    hi "Per cert, què t'ha portat a pujar aquí?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4880
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_29b8a23e:

    # li "A little fresh air every now and again doesn't hurt."
    li "Una mica d'aire fresc de tant en tant no fa mal."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4885
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9dde5fe4:

    # emi "Ah!"
    emi "Ah!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4887
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_462dce6f:

    # "Emi breaks off from her vain attempts to introduce the concept of logic to Rin."
    "L'Emi interromp els seus intents inútils d'introduir el concepte de lògica a la Rin."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4892
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_6eb7897b:

    # emi "That was why we came up here too!"
    emi "Nosaltres també hem vingut per això!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4894
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_dd6b669c:

    # "Something tells me it was her idea alone, and that Rin only got dragged up here on Emi's whim. Then again, the same could probably be said of Lilly and Hanako."
    "Alguna cosa em diu que va ser idea seva, i que la Rin només s'hi ha vist arrossegada pel seu capritx. També és veritat que podria dir el mateix de la Lilly i la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4899
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f4686d17:

    # li "Now, now. We can share."
    li "Va, va. Podem compartir."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4910
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_1f9a0da5:

    # "The creaking of the door to the roof can be heard as soon as she says the words. A moment of silence falls over us as everyone's attention focuses on the figure appearing from it."
    "Se sent cruixir la porta al terrat tan aviat com diu aquestes paraules. Es fa silenci, ja que tots parem atenció a la figura que apareix de dins."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4928
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_080fb3ab:

    # "Hanako slowly walks over to us, her eyes pinned to the ground, silently ruing the attention she's attracting. She tenses, just barely, when her eyes meet Rin's."
    "La Hanako camina lentament cap a nosaltres, amb els ulls a terra, penedint-se en silenci de l'atenció que atreu. Es tensa, una mica, quan es troba amb els ulls de la Rin."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4930
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_7bfcf171:

    # "I can't help raising an eyebrow as she walks over to us and sits next to me, doing her utmost to avoid looking up even as she brings her cafeteria bread to her mouth."
    "No puc evitar aixecar una cella mentre camina cap a nosaltres i seu al costat meu, fent tot el possible per evitar aixecar el cap, fins i tot quan es posa l'entrepà de la cafeteria a la boca."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4938
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_de5cae52:

    # hi "So how do you and Emi know each other, anyways?"
    hi "En fi, de què us coneixeu tu i l'Emi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4946
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_077a5b0a:

    # li "Emi's somewhat well known around the school for her athletic ability. She's the fastest member of the track and field club by some margin, even beating Miki Miura at the track meet last week."
    "L'Emi és molt coneguda a l'escola per la seva habilitat atlètica. És la més ràpida del club d'atletisme de lluny, fins i tot va superar a la Miki Miura a la cursa de la setmana passada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4948
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d687e3c4:

    # "Miki Miura… ah, that tanned girl from the front of my class. Considering her height and toned body, being able to beat her is quite an accomplishment."
    "La Miki Miura... ah, aquella noia morena que seu al davant de la meva classe. Atesa la seva alçada i el cos tonificat, ser capaç de vèncer-la deu ser tota una fita."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4953
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9a0f6a6f:

    # "Looking over to Emi, it's very clear she's well aware of this fact as she beams proudly."
    "Miro cap a l'Emi, està clar que és molt conscient d'aquest fet mentre somriu tot orgullosa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4958
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9fc551e7:

    # emi "So, Hisao. What was your score in English?"
    emi "Així que, Hisao. Quina nota has tret a anglès?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4960
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_1263e952:

    # "Ouch."
    "Au."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4965
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_27984b74:

    # hi "No comment."
    hi "Sense comentaris."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4971
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_4af384a4:

    # emi "Boo~."
    emi "Uuh~."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4973
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_98cff811:

    # "She puffs her cheeks and pouts, but it doesn't take long for her to bounce back."
    "Infla les galtes i arrufa els llavis, però no tarda gaire a refer-se."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4978
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_3595ebbe:

    # emi "All right, if I tell you mine, you have to tell me yours. Deal?"
    emi "Va, si et dic la meva, tu em dius la teva. Fet?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4985
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_87be1db0:

    # hi "Fine, fine."
    hi "Vinga, va."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4991
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bf4ed537:

    # emi "Okay, on the count of three, we both say our results."
    emi "D'acord, a la de tres tots dos diem la nostra nota."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:4996
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9c1b62b9:

    # emi "One…{w=1.0} Two…{w=1.0} Three!{w=1.0}{nw}"
    emi "Un…{w=1.0} dos…{w=1.0} tres!{w=1.0}{nw}"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5003
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ed96174c:

    # "I beam a mischievous grin."
    "Faig un somriure murri."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5015
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_823b4dfc:

    # emi "Ah! Evil! Evil, evil, evil, evil!"
    emi "Ah! Dolent! Dolent, dolent, dolent!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5020
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c3938668:

    # hi "You said it, not me. Still, the fact that you managed an even lower score than me is kind of amazing."
    hi "Ho has dit tu, no jo. Tot i això, si has tret una nota encara més baixa que la meva em sorprendria una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5026
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_727ac656:

    # emi "Grr~!"
    emi "Grr~!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5028
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c699fa5f:

    # "She looks and sounds like a small terrier growling at an intruder. I can't say it's the most threatening sight I've seen."
    "Sembla i sona com un petit terrier que gruny a un intrús. No puc dir que sigui la visió més amenaçadora que hagi vist mai."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5034
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_1cd74053:

    # li "Either way, scoring higher than thirty-two isn't something to boast about, much less scoring below it. For any subject."
    li "Sigui com sigui, aconseguir més de trenta-dos punts no és per presumir, i molt menys treure menys nota. De qualsevol assignatura."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5039
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_813e264c:

    # hi "Yes, Lilly."
    hi "Sí, Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5045
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_3d3e7724:

    # emi "Sorry, Lilly."
    emi "Perdona, Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5050
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_433446e6:

    # li "I could help you with your English, if you'd like. It would be my pleasure to—"
    li "Podria ajudar-vos amb el vostre anglès, si volguéssiu. Seria un plaer..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5055
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b51102d2:

    # emi "No, no, that's fine. But I appreciate the thought. Really."
    emi "No, no, no et preocupis. Però gràcies per l'oferiment. De debò."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5062
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_8b5120f2:

    # "Lilly looks slightly deflated, her hopes of imparting her knowledge dashed. Judging from the badly hidden laughter of the rest of us, neither she nor Emi seem to have garnered too much pity."
    "La Lilly sembla una mica desanimada, les seves esperances de transmetre els seus coneixements a fer punyetes. A jutjar per les rialles mal dissimulades de la resta, ni ella ni l'Emi semblen fer-los massa llàstima."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5074
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_505f7434:

    # "As I sit happily laughing though, I feel my voice suddenly cut off as my chest clenches."
    "Però mentre m'assec rient tot feliç, sento que se'm talla la veu de sobte i noto una pressió al pit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5083
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_529d176d:

    # "I sit in silence for a few seconds, all my concentration forced on my heartbeat. It's only a small pain, but the ache feels like it's growing."
    "M'assec en silenci durant uns segons, i concentrant-me en els batecs del meu cor. Només és un petit dolor, però sembla que vagi creixent."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5103
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f3585eb6:

    # "Breathe deeply… breathe deeply…"
    "Inspira profundament... inspira profundament..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5112
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d664a161:

    # "I glance upward to try and keep at least some of my attention on my surroundings, to see Emi suddenly freezing when she notices the expression of pain on my face out of the corner of her eye."
    "Miro cap amunt per intentar mantenir almenys part d'atenció en el meu voltant, i veig que l'Emi es congela de sobte, després de veure de reüll la meva cara de dolor."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5117
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9cd42848:

    # emi "Hey, Hisao… are you okay?"
    emi "Ei, Hisao... estàs bé?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5124
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_20ad7d52:

    # hi "Yeah, I'm… fine…"
    hi "Sí, estic... bé..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5133
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_21252ea2:

    # "I look back down and redouble my efforts to try and stay calm, clenching my fists to try and dull the pain."
    "Torno a mirar cap a baix i redoblo els meus esforços per mantenir la calma, estrenyent els punys per intentar calmar el dolor."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5153
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_372f958e:

    # "It takes a short time, but the pain, thankfully, begins to fade."
    "Tarda una mica, però el dolor, per sort, comença a desaparèixer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5157
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_461bb528:

    # "When I look back up, there's only silence and pensive faces to be seen. I guess I'd better explain myself."
    "Quan torno a aixecar el cap, només noto silenci i cares preocupades. Suposo que em tocarà explicar-ho."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5161
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a7695639:

    # hi "Arrhythmia. I'm fine, it's… just a heart flutter."
    hi "Arrítmia. Estic bé, és... només unes palpitacions."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5166
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_00a304ff:

    # li "Are you sure? Should we get the nurse?"
    li "N'estàs segur? Anem a buscar a l'infermer?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5172
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_8160992b:

    # "Taking her cue, Hanako quickly picks herself up and begins to dash to the door."
    "Agafant la indirecta, la Hanako recull de pressa i s'afanya cap a la porta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5174
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ab71301a:

    # hi "Hanako, stop. Lilly, I'm fine."
    hi "Frena Hanako. Lilly, estic bé"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5179
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e8ea6dda:

    # rin "You look like a wet, wrinkled tomato."
    rin "Sembles un tomàquet moll i arrugat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5181
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_0f638bea:

    # hi "Huh?"
    hi "Eh?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5183
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_81563327:

    # "As I bring my hand to my forehead, I can feel the beads of sweat gathered on it and dab them off with my cuff."
    "Em poso la mà al front, i noto les gotes de suor que se m'han acumulat i me les eixugo amb el puny de la roba."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5185
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a6063ed1:

    # hi "Thanks. I told you, I'm fine. I'm just kind of… fragile, I guess."
    hi "Gràcies. Ja us ho he dit, estic bé. Soc una mica... fràgil, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5199
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_cd4c7e04:

    # "The entire atmosphere's changed from one of gaiety to downcast faces, the situation being too awkward for anyone to know exactly how to react."
    "Tota l'ambient ha canviat d'alegria general a cares ensopides, la situació és massa incòmoda perquè ningú sàpiga exactament com reaccionar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5201
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ecc06a2a:

    # "And of course, the whole thing is thanks to me. It just had to happen now, around others."
    "I, per descomptat, tot això és gràcies a mi. Havia de passar-me ara, davant dels altres."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5208
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e90e265a:

    # li "Oh, Emi?"
    li "Oh, Emi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5214
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_19972527:

    # emi "Hmm?"
    emi "Hmm?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5216
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_dc457edc:

    # "She looks up, a box of juice halfway to her mouth."
    "Mira cap amunt, amb un bric de suc a mig beure a la boca."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5221
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d14fe37d:

    # li "I haven't told you of my score yet, have I?"
    li "Encara no t'he dit la meva nota, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5226
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_eb15938a:

    # emi "Yeah, well. You're half-foreign, so your score doesn't count anyway."
    emi "Sí, bé. Ets mig forastera, així que la teva nota no compta igualment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5228
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b2be9a7a:

    # "Lifting an eyebrow, I inquisitively turn to Lilly."
    "Aixeco una cella, i em giro cap a la Lilly amb curiositat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5233
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_91e803f1:

    # hi "What was your test result, anyway?"
    hi "Però bé, quina ha estat la teva nota?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5237
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a0119998:

    # "She gives a cheeky grin."
    "Fa un somriure sorneguer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5243
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_338b4585:

    # li "One hundred percent. Perfect score."
    li "Cent de cent. Una puntuació perfecta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5247
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bb21fe62:

    # "No way. All I can do is hang my mouth open in wonder."
    "No pot ser. Em quedo amb la boca oberta tot sorprès."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5249
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_4edf4152:

    # "Considering those tests are insane even for some native speakers, I can only imagine she's gone and done something like committing to mind part of the dictionary. A gift for rote memorization, maybe."
    "Si considerem que aquestes proves són una bogeria fins i tot per a alguns parlants nadius, em puc imaginar que anat i ha fet alguna cosa així com memoritzar part del diccionari. Potser té un do per memoritzar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5254
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_57b69778:

    # hi "That's…"
    hi "Això..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5260
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_5fd7d042:

    # emi "See! Only someone part-foreign could get a score that good."
    emi "Veus! Només algú mig foraster podria tenir tan bona nota."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5265
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_f818113a:

    # hi "'See'…"
    hi "\"Veus\"..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5271
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_be8d5fe3:

    # emi "Er…"
    emi "Gr..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5277
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_94a74791:

    # "Lilly and I grin at Emi's expense, her reaction identical to mine when I'd first tripped on that little landmine. Lilly's foreign ancestry does raise a point, though."
    "La Lilly i jo riem a costa de l'Emi, la seva reacció és idèntica a la meva quan vaig trepitjar per primera vegada aquella petita mina. Tot i que l'ascendència estrangera de la Lilly sí que planteja un punt."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5282
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_3ae4d60e:

    # hi "Ah, that's right. You leave tomorrow for Scotland, don't you?"
    hi "Ah, és veritat. Demà marxes cap a Escòcia, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5288
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_cb0d3c8c:

    # li "That's correct. Emi heard some rumors about it; it seems word's spreading quickly, considering I only told a friend in my class a couple of days ago."
    li "És cert. L'Emi va sentir algú parlar-ne; sembla que s'ha escampat la veu molt de pressa, donat que només li vaig dir a un amic de classe fa un parell de dies."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5293
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_c7ad04db:

    # emi "It must be so nice to go halfway around the world on a holiday."
    emi "Deu estar bé això de recórrer mig món de vacances."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5298
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_6228a829:

    # emi "Hey, could you buy me something while you're there?"
    emi "Ei, em podries comprar una cosa mentre siguis allà?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5303
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_7d03870a:

    # hi "Don't be too shy now."
    hi "No et tallis tant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5308
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_7571ba00:

    # "Lilly gives a lighthearted giggle, evidently fully expecting Emi's bluntness."
    "La Lilly deixa anar una rialleta despreocupada, totalment acostumada a la franquesa de l'Emi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5310
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bd20579e:

    # "The rest of the lunch continues much the same as before, the jauntiness from before my heart flutter thankfully returning in full."
    "La resta del dinar segueix més o menys igual que abans, l'alegria d'abans de tenir les palpitacions ja ha tornat completament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5320
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_4b8d9d13:

    # "As everyone files off with the appropriate farewells, only Lilly and I are left."
    "Quan tothom ja s'ha acomiadat, només quedem la Lilly i jo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5322
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d407bcd4:

    # hi "Hey, Lilly?"
    hi "Ei, Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5324
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_4d2dde6d:

    # "She packs the last of her things into her bag and clips it shut, before perking her head up slightly."
    "Posa les últimes coses a la seva bossa i la tanca, abans d'aixecar una mica el cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5329
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_16b10efa:

    # li "Hmm?"
    li "Hmm?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5331
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_43061556:

    # hi "Um… thanks for breaking the silence back there. I kind of wanted to stop it, but didn't really know how to."
    hi "Um... gràcies per trencar el silenci abans. Volia intentar parar-ho, però no sabia com fer-ho."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5333
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_663fb400:

    # "As much as I'd like to sound less morose about it, the letter from yesterday, screwing up a test so badly in class, and now my heart make things very hard indeed."
    "Per més que m'agradaria sonar menys malhumorat sobre això, entre la carta d'ahir, la mala nota de la prova, i ara el meu cor fa que les coses siguin molt dures."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5338
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_76018c39:

    # "She gives an indulgent smile and nods. I hope she hasn't picked up on it, but knowing her, it's unlikely that she hasn't."
    "Fa un somriure indulgent i assenteix. Espero que no se n'hagi adonat, però coneixent-la, és poc probable que no ho hagi fet."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5340
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_2567438c:

    # li "Emi's strong, but only human. We do worry about you, Hisao."
    li "L'Emi és forta, però no deixa de ser humana. Ens preocupem per tu, Hidao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5342
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ff33e596:

    # hi "Hold on, why would I worry you?"
    hi "Frena, per què hauria de preocupar-vos?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5349
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b480b763:

    # "Her smiling face collapses, becoming uncomfortably serious."
    "Deixa de somriure i fa una cara incòmodament seriosa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5351
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_2147ce8b:

    # li "Hisao, we are not ignorant of your situation."
    li "Hisao, no ignorem pas la teva situació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5353
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d876827f:

    # li "Unli…"
    li "A dif..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5358
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_66fd4e7f:

    # "She suddenly cuts herself short, unsure of whether she should say what she intends to. I give a weak smile and rest my hand on her shoulder."
    "De sobte s'interromp, sense saber si ha de dir això que pretenia dir. Somric tímidament i li poso la mà a l'espatlla."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5362
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_72540600:

    # hi "Don't. It's enough that I worry about it. I don't want you all to shoulder my burden."
    hi "No ho facis. Ja n'hi ha prou que jo me'n preocupi. No vull que arrossegueu la meva càrrega."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5367
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_25bbf6bb:

    # li "But…"
    li "Però..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5369
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_8ff88e7c:

    # hi "If you all worry about it, I have to worry about your worrying. If… that makes sense."
    hi "Si totes us preocupeu, em preocuparà que estigueu preocupades. Si això... té cap sentit."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5371
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_0e454488:

    # hi "I'm fine, okay?"
    hi "Estic bé, entesos?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5376
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_5cc5435d:

    # "For a moment she looks to be lost in thought, carefully pondering how to react."
    "Per un moment sembla absorta, reflexionant amb prudència com hauria de reaccionar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5381
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_de9634ec:

    # li "Hisao, do you have any paper left from your food's packaging?"
    li "Hisao, et queda una mica del paper amb què has embolicat el teu menjar?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5383
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_2ecc8e81:

    # hi "I… think so? I'll just check."
    hi "Crec... que sí. Deixa'm que ho miri."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5387
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_1acfffc4:

    # "I rummage around in my bag for the leftovers from lunch, eventually finding a paper square from my sandwich's package."
    "Remeno dins la bossa les sobres del dinar, i finalment trobo un quadrat del paper amb què he embolcallat el meu entrepà."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5389
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9ad01c4c:

    # "My eyebrow raised and my expression rather quizzical, I gently place the square into Lilly's hand. Without another word, she brings her fingers around it to feel out its edges."
    "Amb la cella aixecada i una expressió més aviat escèptica, col·loco suaument el quadrat a la mà de la Lilly. Sense dir res, posa els dits al voltant per sentir-ne les vores."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5394
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a53bf07c:

    # li "This should be large enough…"
    li "Crec que és prou gran..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5396
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_635ca1cd:

    # "With both of us seated on the roof, the minutes to the lesson ticking away, she proceeds to lay the item on the ground and begin her work in earnest."
    "Tots dos asseguts al terrat, mentre passen els minuts que falten per la pròxima classe, es posa a col·locar-lo a terra i comença la seva feina tot convençuda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5401
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_8e8e2bea:

    # "Wrapped in silence, I watch her fingers move about on the small square with amazing dexterity. A small fold here, a larger fold there, her fingertips keep a slow but sure pace."
    "Envoltats de silenci, veig com va movent els dits pel quadradet amb una destresa increïble. Un petit plec aquí, un plec més gran allà, les puntes dels dits mantenen un ritme lent però segur."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5403
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b671936c:

    # "Looking up, her expression is calm and placid. The fact her face is pointed well above the sheet in front of her makes the sight of her work all the more curious."
    "Quan aixeco la vista, veig que té una expressió tranquil·la i plàcida. El fet que la seva cara apunti molt per sobre el full que té davant, fa que la visió de la seva obra sigui encara més curiosa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5405
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_21b98153:

    # "Her shoulders slump a bit after finishing one final fold, her work apparently done. It's only when she holds the item up in her hands that I realize what it is."
    "Abaixa les espatlles poc després d'acabar el plec final, la seva feina teòricament acabada. Només quan ho agafa amb les mans m'adono de què ha fet."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5420
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bbd1334e:

    # "A small origami crane."
    "Una petita grua d'origami."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5422
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_861fb214:

    # "Light brown thanks to the packaging used, the result looks quite delicate and precise."
    "De color marró clar gràcies a l'embolcall que ha utilitzat, el resultat es veu força delicat i precís."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5424
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_35ce8983:

    # hi "You can do origami?"
    hi "Saps fer origami?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5426
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_250236f5:

    # li "I taught myself how to do it when I was younger. It improved my dexterity a bit."
    li "Vaig aprendre'n jo sola quan era més petita. Així vaig millorar una mica la meva destresa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5428
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_940a9afc:

    # hi "Huh…"
    hi "Eh..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5430
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_165e21f5:

    # "A little baffled, I carefully take the small bird from her pale cupped hands as if it would break from the slightest breath. It seems to be folded quite well, and holds its shape easily."
    "Una mica desconcertat, agafo amb cura l'ocellet de les seves pàl·lides mans juntes com si s'hagués de trencar al més mínim alè. Sembla prou ben plegat, i manté la forma perfetament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5438
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_bb941c83:

    # "We both grab our bags and head out the door, Lilly extending her cane as she does so."
    "Tots dos agafem les bosses i sortim per la porta, mentre la Lilly estén el bastó."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5445
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e4fcfde8:

    # "I hold Lilly's handiwork up to my face for further inspection while we walk down the hallway, her hand running along the silver handrails for orientation."
    "Mentre caminem pel passadís, m'apropo l'obra de la Lilly a la cara per inspeccionar-la encara més, ella fa córrer la mà pels passamans de plata per orientar-se."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5447
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_9b87e334:

    # "If she taught herself origami to improve her dexterity, with the use of her hands meaning so much to her given her condition… ah, so that's it."
    "Si es va ensenyar a si mateixa per millorar la destresa, ja que l'ús de les mans significa tant per ella donada la seva condició... ah, així que m'ho ha fet per això."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5449
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_27eda1e3:

    # "I smile as I realize the bird's meaning."
    "Somric quan m'adono del significat de l'ocell."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5451
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_ade2c2cb:

    # "'Everyone here has had to find their own ways of dealing with their conditions. You aren't alone here when you have problems.'"
    "\"Cadascun ha hagut de trobar la seva manera d'afrontar la seva condició. Aquí no estàs sol quan tens problemes\"."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5453
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_37d88425:

    # hi "Thanks, Lilly. I appreciate this."
    hi "Gràcies, Lilly. Ho aprecio."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5458
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_b1493468:

    # "She gives a sweet smile and a nod, not using words where none need be used, in her typical manner."
    "Somriu dolçament i assenteix, no fa servir paraules quan no cal fer-ho, típic d'ella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5463
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_0f6d3107:

    # li "All I ask is that you take care of yourself, Hisao."
    li "Només et demano que et cuidis, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5465
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_d5be8d45:

    # hi "Don't worry, I will."
    hi "No et preocupis, ho faré."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5470
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_1bb7182e:

    # li "Promise?"
    li "M'ho promets?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5472
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_a316709f:

    # hi "Promise."
    hi "T'ho prometo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5479
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_2138bb24:

    # "And with that, we part ways."
    "I així, cadascú tira per la seva banda."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5481
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_86f9924f:

    # "To be honest, I don't know what annoys me more - the fact that I could die at any moment, or the fact that everyone knows that."
    "Si soc sincer, no tinc clar què em molesta més: el fet que podria morir en qualsevol moment, o el fet que tothom ho sap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5483
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_30222011:

    # "I guess I'll just take each day as it comes. As the unexpected present in my hand reminds me, I'm not alone here. Even though I may be like this, I'm not alone."
    "Suposo que m'agafaré cada dia tal com vingui. Tal com em recorda l'inesperat regal que tinc a la mà, aquí no estic sol. Encara que estigui així, no estic sol."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5485
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_e824f231:

    # "If they worry, if anyone worries, I'll smile."
    "Si es preocupen, si algú es preocupa, somriuré."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5487
translate ca a2_lilly_little_wing_6aa9a332:

    # "I'll smile enough for all their worries to go away."
    "Somriuré prou perquè totes les seves preocupacions se'n vagin."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5504
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c85844ff:

    # "The moment the bell rings out, a collective sigh of relief comes from everyone."
    "Quan sona la campana, tothom sospira d'alleujament."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5508
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_def79e86:

    # "Much of the morning's been taken up by a droning lecture on stoichiometry, a topic entirely unbefitting of the insufferable heat permeating the classroom."
    "Gran part del matí ha estat ocupat per una classe d'estequiometria, un tema totalment impropi de la calor insofrible que fa a l'aula."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5513
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_af882ca2:

    # "Knowing that attempting to teach anything more would be an exercise in futility, Mutou gives up and begins clearing the teaching materials from his desk for the day."
    "Tot sabent que intentar ensenyar res més seria fer feina inútil, en Mutou es rendeix i comença a recollir els materials didàctics de la seva taula per avui."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5521
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_bd47c786:

    # "As meaningless banter starts filling the classroom, I notice Hanako getting up and coming to my desk. She's been a lot less withdrawn lately, something which gives me a small measure of satisfaction."
    "Mentre l'aula s'omple de bromes sense sentit, veig que la Hanako s'aixeca i ve cap al meu escriptori. Ha estat molt menys retreta últimament, cosa que em satisfà una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5526
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_801c5115:

    # ha "Hello, Hisao."
    ha "Hola, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5528
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_66f1df30:

    # hi "Hey. Want to go pick up Lilly, then? It's close to the time when she'd need to get going if she's going to make the flight."
    hi "Ei. Vols anar a buscar la Lilly, doncs? S'apropa l'hora en què hauria de posar-se en marxa si vol agafar el vol."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5533
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_99765578:

    # ha "Um… about that…"
    ha "Um... sobre això..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5538
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_578146dc:

    # ha "She said she might be held up a bit by her classmates."
    ha "Va dir que els seus companys de classe potser l'endarreririen una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5540
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0dffaa0f:

    # "I suppose that makes sense. Her class usually gets off a little earlier than ours, so Lilly would normally have just come to our classroom. Her class must be sending her off."
    "Suposo que això té sentit. La seva classe normalment surt una mica abans que la nostra, així que la Lilly normalment hauria vingut a la nostra classe. La seva classe la deu estar acomiadant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5542
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0e1ad98d:

    # hi "Well, never mind. We can wait outside her classroom for once, right?"
    hi "Bé, tant se val. Podem esperar fora de la seva classe per variar, oi?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5547
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_993c07c8:

    # "She gives a small giggle before nodding, the two of us taking our things and leaving for 3-2's classroom."
    "Dona una rialleta abans d'assentir, els dos ens agafem les nostres coses i marxem cap a l'aula 3-2."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5554
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_60ef2020:

    # "When we reach our destination, I stop in idle amusement at the scene inside."
    "Quan arribem a la nostra destinació, paro tot divertit veient l'escena de dins."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5556
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b4b1bed0:

    # "One of the shorter girls from the class has Lilly wrapped in an enthusiastic hug, her head no higher than Lilly's chin. Her other friends, of which there are several, are gathered around her as well. Lilly simply smiles kindly and hugs her back."
    "Una de les noies més baixetes de la classe embolcalla la Lilly en una abraçada amb entusiasme, el seu cap no és més alt que la barbeta de la Lilly. Els seus altres amics, n'hi ha forces, també es reuneixen al seu voltant. La Lilly simplement somriu amablement i li torna l'abraçada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5558
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_57bac33f:

    # "I guess Lilly must be pretty popular. Compared to Shizune's harsh but fair dictatorship of 3-3, Lilly seems more like a mother figure for 3-2, to say nothing of her height and looks."
    "Suposo que la Lilly deu ser molt popular. En comparació amb la dura, però justa, dictadura de la Shizune de la 3-3, la Lilly sembla més la figura materna de la 3-2, sense parlar de la seva alçada i aspecte."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5560
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5d2531b5:

    # "Kenji's pointedly cool demeanor as he packs up his things at his seat in the back corner of the classroom is expected. He's no doubt far from a fan of the fuss being made about Lilly's leaving."
    "És d'esperar que en Kenji es comporti fredament mentre recull les seves coses al seu seient a la punta del darrere de la classe. Sens dubte, no és gaire aficionat a l'enrenou que s'està fent sobre la partida de la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5562
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b09c3b05:

    # "Looking beside me and seeing Hanako following my gaze, I decide to finally enter the room."
    "Miro al meu costat i veig que la Hanako em segueix la mirada, finalment decideixo entrar a la classe."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5572
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_cd874f41:

    # hi "'Afternoon, Lilly. It's just me and Hanako."
    hi "Bona tarda, Lilly. Només som jo i la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5582
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_15141b8a:

    # "Hanako withers noticeably when exposed to the din being made around Lilly. Try as she might, I doubt she'll ever completely get over her social anxiety."
    "La Hanako s'arronsa visiblement quan es veu exposada a l'enrenou que hi ha al voltant de la Lilly. Per molt que ho intenti, dubto que mai arribi a superar del tot la seva ansietat social."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5587
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_a7be5c36:

    # ha "Hello…"
    ha "Hola..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5589
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_154e30c8:

    # "Lilly manages to work out our position reasonably well, her classmate detaching herself without a second word. A look of slight exasperation is written on Lilly's face, though I can't say I blame her."
    "La Lilly prou bé per entendre la nostra posició, la seva companya de classe es desenganxa sense dir res més. A la cara de la Lilly s'hi dibuixa una mica d'exasperació, encara que no puc dir que la culpo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5594
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c4737f71:

    # li "Hello Hisao, Hanako. Do we have much time before the flight leaves?"
    li "Hola, Hisao, Hanako. Tenim gaire temps abans no surti el vol?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5596
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0a131b2c:

    # "I give a quick glance at my watch. Taking the trip to the airport into account, there's a good ten, maybe fifteen minutes left while still allowing for contingencies."
    "Faig un cop d'ull al meu rellotge. Si tenim en compte el viatge a l'aeroport, en queden deu, potser quinze minuts, i encara hi hauria marge per contingències."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5598
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0eb4ed18:

    # hi "Yeah, we still have a few minutes to kill. I wouldn't worry about missing it yet."
    hi "Sí, encara et sobren uns minuts. No em preocuparia per perdre'l, encara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5600
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c00b3437:

    # "Classmate" "Ah, is this Hanako?"
    "Company de classe" "Ah, és la Hanako?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5602
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ec2d9bb6:

    # "Uh oh. I think we've just inadvertently become entangled in Lilly's social web."
    "Oh, oh. Crec que ens hem enredat sense voler a la xarxa social de la Lilly."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5604
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_77a2fc52:

    # "The girl is probably part of the legally-blind faction of the class like Kenji, given her almost windowpane-like spectacles. Her short, roughly-cut hair gives her a look that fits her excitable expression."
    "La noia deu ser part de la facció legalment cega de la classe com en Kenji, donades les ulleres que porta de cul de got. Els cabells curts i mal tallats li donen un aspecte que encaixa a la seva expressió esverada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5609
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5477aa3c:

    # ha "H-hello… um…"
    ha "H-hola... um..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5611
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0c1ba9aa:

    # "She takes Hanako's hand and pulls it up and down enthusiastically. I really don't get how girls can be so social to someone they only know as the friend of a friend."
    "Agafa la mà de la Hanako i l'estira amunt i avall amb entusiasme. Realment no entenc com les noies poden ser tan sociables amb algú que només coneixen com l'amic d'un amic."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5613
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_db51a7b0:

    # "While Hanako exchanges nervous greetings, I look around the room for my short and overdressed next-door neighbor. Try as I might, he seems to have slipped out of the classroom without anyone noticing."
    "Mentre la Hanako intercanvia salutacions tota nerviosa, miro al voltant de l'aula buscant el meu veí del costat, baixet i massa arreglat. Per molt que ho intenti, sembla que s'ha escapat de l'aula sense que ningú se n'adoni."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5615
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c81e8a73:

    # "For a moment I try to think of possible career paths that could reasonably benefit from his single skill, before putting my mind to more pertinent matters."
    "Per un moment intento pensar en possibles carreres professionals que puguin beneficiar-se raonablement de la seva única habilitat, abans de plantejar-me qüestions més pertinents."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5621
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_a7c5d3cb:

    # "Lilly seems pleased, if somewhat guarded, about the enthusiasm Hanako's suddenly excited from those around her. She might not see it, but Hanako's much less panicked about the affair than I'd anticipated."
    "La Lilly sembla contenta, si bé una mica desconfiada, de l'entusiasme que la Hanako ha despertat en tots aquells que l'envolten. Pot ser que no ho vegi, però la Hanako està molt menys espantada del que jo havia previst."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5623
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_08dd4691:

    # "Shuffling my way through the gaggle of classmates, I eventually manage to reach her."
    "Caminant amb pas feixuc a través de l'eixam de companys de classe, finalment aconsegueixo arribar-hi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5625
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_37ff7772:

    # hi "Don't worry, Hanako's fine."
    hi "No et preocupis, la Hanako està bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5630
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f507d2d9:

    # li "Thank you. I thought she might be overwhelmed by them."
    li "Gràcies. Pensava que se sentiria aclaparada per tanta gent."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5632
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_747d3bc8:

    # "Classmate" "Don't worry, we'll be gentle!"
    "Company de classe" "No et preocupis, serem amables!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5637
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_335c6b44:

    # "Both of us grimace in unison. Hanako's nervous grin stays plastered on her face as another couple of girls moves in to meet her."
    "Tots dos fem una ganyota a la vegada. El somriure nerviós de la Hanako se li queda enganxat a la cara mentre una altra parella de noies s'apropa per conèixer-la."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5639
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4dcd76ba:

    # "It's kind of amazing that even just a month ago she'd never have been able to cope with a situation such as this. Even when I first met her, the two of us completely alone, she sprinted from the library."
    "És increïble que fins fa només un mes no hagués pogut fer front a una situació com aquesta. Fins i tot quan la vaig conèixer per primera vegada, i això que els dos estàvem sols, va sortir corrent de la biblioteca."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5641
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f7b31355:

    # hi "So, got everything you need?"
    hi "Què, ja tens tot allò que necessites?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5646
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f02ab6e3:

    # li "It's all packed. I just have to go by my room to pick it up on the way, and Hanako and I need to change."
    li "Ja tinc la maleta feta. Només he d'anar a la meva habitació a recollir-la de camí, i la Hanako i jo ens hem de canviar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5648
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4b7efb9a:

    # hi "I guess we'd better get going, then. Hanako?"
    hi "Suposo que és millor que marxem, doncs. Hanako?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5653
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5b89d922:

    # "Hanako's head flicks up towards us in a flash, her face rather unmistakably appreciating the chance to extricate herself from the small group gathered around her."
    "La Hanako aixeca el cap mirant-nos en un instant, fa cara d'agrair una oportunitat de separar-se del petit grup reunit al seu voltant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5660
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4e9c9b46:

    # ha "C-coming!"
    ha "V-vinc!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5671
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_9604c1d2:

    # "The long taxi ride to the airport is surprisingly pleasant, despite the three of us being rather squashed together to fit in the small back seat. On the other hand, maybe 'despite' isn't the right word."
    "El llarg viatge en taxi fins a l'aeroport és d'allò més agradable, malgrat que els tres estem bastant estrets per cabre en el poc espai dels seients de darrere. D'altra banda, potser \"malgrat\" no és la paraula correcta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5673
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b0d34183:

    # "Lilly pays the fare to the driver as we file out, Hanako's eyes flittering left and right. Thankfully there aren't too many people around, most of them being inside the main building rather than milling around outside."
    "La Lilly paga la tarifa al conductor mentre nosaltres sortim, els ulls de la Hanako boleien d'esquerra i a dreta. Afortunadament, no hi ha massa gent, ja que la majoria estan dins de l'edifici principal i no pas a l'exterior."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5680
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_5e441323:

    # "It isn't hard to spot Akira and Hideaki leaning against a fence while talking to pass the time. A large black travel bag, complete with wheels and travel handle, leans against the fence alongside them."
    "No és difícil veure a l'Akira i en Hideaki recolzants en una tanca mentre parlen per passar el temps. Una gran bossa de viatge negra, amb rodes i nansa de viatge, està recolzada contra la tanca del seu costat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5685
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_82e188a5:

    # "Hideaki's the first to notice us, pointing us out to Akira who gives an overenthusiastic wave."
    "En Hideaki és el primer que ens veu, i ens assenyala a l'Akira, que ens saluda amb un gest entusiasta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5690
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_0a43f240:

    # aki "Hey! He~y!"
    aki "Ei! E~i!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5692
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_6f35085b:

    # "I grab Lilly's travel bag for her as we go to meet the two, earning a nod of appreciation."
    "Li agafo la bossa de viatge a la Lilly per anar a trobar-los, i em guanyo un gest d'agraïment."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5698
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_6101972f:

    # aki "I've got all my stuff here, you got yours? Plane ticket as well?"
    aki "Tinc totes les meves coses aquí, tens les teves? El bitllet d'avió també?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5703
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_38ecaa6a:

    # li "Don't worry, I have everything. You?"
    li "No et preocupis, ho tinc tot. Tu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5708
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_d1bb0666:

    # aki "Yep. All ready to go."
    aki "Sip. Tot preparat per marxar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5713
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c9369609:

    # hh "Not without some problems along the way, I might add."
    hh "Podria afegir que no sense alguns problemes de camí."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5721
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_35a5d6fa:

    # "The snide remark has his head roughly dragged around by a very firmly clamped-on hand."
    "Qui ha fet el comentari sarcàstic té una mà molt ferma que l'agafa al voltant del cap."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5727
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_fbb3db1a:

    # aki "Haha yeah, I kinda sorta forgot it was in my trousers' pocket. Trousers that I'd put in the wash…"
    aki "Sí, havia oblidat que ho tenia a la butxaca dels pantalons. Uns pantalons que havia posat a la rentadora..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5732
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_c07cc9dc:

    # li "Oh no…"
    li "Oh no..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5737
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b9652b3c:

    # aki "Don't worry, don't worry. Did you know you can print out tickets if you order online nowadays? It's really cool."
    aki "No passa res, no passa res. Sabies que pots imprimir els bitlles si els compres per internet? És una passada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5742
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_522f5621:

    # "Hideaki's pained expression says that this wasn't a solution found quickly. It could have been worse, I guess."
    "L'expressió de dolor d'en Hideaki diu que aquesta solució no es va trobar tan ràpid. Podria haver estat pitjor, suposo."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5747
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_e6607490:

    # li "We'd better start off then. Check-in should be ready by now."
    li "Serà millor que comencem, va. La facturació ja hauria d'estar preparada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5754
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_8ee007bd:

    # aki "Yeah, you're right."
    aki "Sí, tens raó."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5756
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_2364b61c:

    # "There's a certain amount of wistfulness in both their voices. To say nothing of the people left behind, meeting their family again after all these years would be big for them."
    "Hi ha cert to de nostàlgia en les seves veus. Sense dir res d'aquells que es queden enrere, tornar a veure a la seva família després de tots aquests anys deu ser important per elles."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5763
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_eee002c4:

    # ha "Lilly…"
    ha "Lilly..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5765
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_401313a2:

    # "Hanako wraps Lilly in a gentle hug to say goodbye, one which is warmly reciprocated. Lilly and I share a brief hug afterward, each of us saying our goodbyes."
    "La Hanako envolta a la Lilly amb una suau abraçada per acomiadar-se'n, i és corresposta càlidament. La Lilly i jo compartim una breu abraçada després, cadascun de nosaltres acomiadant-nos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5767
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_f3ad736d:

    # "Beside us, Akira and Hideaki break off from a small hug and a word or two between them. It would probably look quite nice if not for the almost comical height difference between the two."
    "Al nostre costat, l'Akira i en Hideaki es separen d'una petita abraçada i una paraula o dues entre ells. Probablement, semblaria bastant bonic si no fos per la diferència d'alçada gairebé còmica entre tots dos."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5775
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ade2cc52:

    # "Lilly takes ahold of her sister's arm once all that needs to be said in farewells is said, the two walking past the huge glass doors."
    "La Lilly agafa el braç de la seva germana una vegada s'ha dit tot allò que calia dir en els comiats, totes dues passen per davant de les enormes portes de vidre."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5780
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_37f08616:

    # li "Goodbye Hisao, Hanako!"
    li "Adeu, Hisao, Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5785
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_1352e1e2:

    # aki "Seeya! Don't do anything stupid, Shortie!"
    aki "A reveure! No facis res estúpid, Napbuf!"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5791
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_37439474:

    # "We wave at them until they disappear from sight in the throng of people moving about inside."
    "Les acomiadem amb la mà fins que desapareixen de la nostra vista entre la multitud de gent que es mouen allà dins."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5793
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b3f8f497:

    # "And then… we're alone."
    "I llavors... estem sols."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5795
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_18c783e4:

    # hi "Well… that's that."
    hi "Bé... ja està."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5800
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ad23fcbc:

    # "I turn to see Hideaki already beginning to walk off."
    "Em giro i veig que en Hideaki ja comença a marxar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5802
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_b14c559a:

    # hi "Seeya."
    hi "Vagi bé."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5814
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_75e96d9f:

    # "He throws a hand into the air, in a manner I'd expect of Akira. In the end, it's just Hanako and me left standing outside."
    "Fa un gest amb una mà a l'aire, d'una manera que esperaria de l'Akira. Al final, només quedem la Hanako i jo fora."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5819
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4438b574:

    # "I rest my hand on her shoulder. She absentmindedly gazes towards the front doors of the building, as if she might catch a glimpse of either of the two before they disappear."
    "Li poso la mà a l'espatlla. Mira distreta cap a la porta principal de l'edifici, com si pogués veure alguna de les dues abans no desapareguin."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5821
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_ad31e358:

    # hi "Don't worry, the time'll pass fast."
    hi "No et preocupis, passarà de pressa."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5826
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_d87b7c30:

    # "She hesitates for a moment, but eventually nods."
    "Vacil·la un moment, però acaba assentint."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5828
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_dd8a633b:

    # "With the scorching heat of the summer sun beaming down on us, we make our way to the nearby bus stop."
    "Amb la calor abrasadora del sol d'estiu a sobre nostre, ens dirigim cap a la parada d'autobús que hi ha a prop."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5833
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_990dd570:

    # "It's strange, really. Just when I'd begun to see Lilly differently, she leaves on what almost feels like a pilgrimage to the past."
    "És estrany, la veritat. Just quan havia començat a veure la Lilly d'una altra manera, se'n va gairebé de pelegrinatge al passat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5835
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_98ddb856:

    # "In a way, though, that's just what I've been doing since coming to Yamaku."
    "En certa manera, això és el que he estat fent des que vaig arribar al Yamaku."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5837
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_a5ba77c5:

    # "As much as I may reflect on everything that's happened to me, I really am hardly unique. Everyone has their own circumstances and separate paths to get where they are now."
    "Per molt que reflexioni sobre tot el que m'ha passat, no soc únic. Tothom té les seves pròpies circumstàncies i els seus camins que han seguit per arribar on es troben ara."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5839
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_85d5abc6:

    # "Yet I still can't really work out how I should proceed. My life may have practically been reset, and I still can't find anything that satisfactorily fills the hole I still feel in myself."
    "Tot i això, encara no sé com hauria de continuar. La meva vida pràcticament s'ha reiniciat, i encara no he trobat res que m'empleni el forat que sento dins meu."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5841
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_530f8b92:

    # "Maybe Lilly's leaving will be a good thing for me. Without her to lean on, I'll need to do more for myself. I'll have to be there for Hanako as well."
    "Potser la partida de la Lilly serà una cosa bona per a mi. Sense ella per fer-me costat, hauré de fer més per mi mateix. Hauré de ser-hi també per la Hanako."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5843
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_4a141977:

    # "It feels strange to have so much changing so quickly after my months in that hospital that seemed to exist so separately from reality, but that's all the more reason for me to keep focused."
    "És estrany que tandes coses canviïn tan de pressa després dels meus mesos en aquell hospital que semblava existir separat de la realitat, però això és una raó de més perquè em mantingui centrat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5845
translate ca a2_lilly_bon_voyage_89a537b1:

    # "I can't let any opportunity slip out of my fingers in my attempt to rebuild my life."
    "No puc deixar que se m'escapi cap oportunitat en el meu intent per reconstruir la meva vida."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5856
translate ca a2lc1o1_2d803fea:

    # hi "I was just thinking about some of the stuff that's happened, don't worry."
    hi "Només estava pensant en algunes de les coses que han passat, no et preocupis."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5863
translate ca a2lc1o1_16b10efa:

    # li "Hmm?"
    li "Hmm?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5865
translate ca a2lc1o1_eb53b994:

    # "She leans in even closer, forcing me to move sideways."
    "S'inclina encara més a prop, obligant-me a moure'm cap a un costat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5867
translate ca a2lc1o1_50fe9ad9:

    # hi "Come on, don't you ever do that as well?"
    hi "Au va, que no ho fas mai, tu?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5872
translate ca a2lc1o1_d9060065:

    # li "You make it sound as if you're hiding something…"
    li "Ho dius com si estiguessis amagant alguna cosa..."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5876
translate ca a2lc1o1_fe47734e:

    # "Erk. Why must this girl be so perceptive?"
    "Argh. Per què aquesta noia ha de ser tan perspicaç?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5878
translate ca a2lc1o1_3ea72233:

    # "Glancing back at her face though, she wears a cute, playful smile."
    "Li miro la cara de reüll i, malgrat tot, té un somriure bonic i juganer."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5880
translate ca a2lc1o1_89b1018e:

    # "She's… playing with me? Even so, I'd rather not pursue this with her."
    "Està... jugant amb mi? Tot i així, preferiria no continuar el tema amb ella."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5882
translate ca a2lc1o1_c3218ae7:

    # hi "I told you, it's nothing."
    hi "Ja t'ho he dit, no és res."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5887
translate ca a2lc1o1_2a03162e:

    # "Lilly furrows her brow in disapproval."
    "La Lilly arrufa el front com a protesta."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5889
translate ca a2lc1o1_f1b7b2c2:

    # li "Is that so?"
    li "De debò?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5891
translate ca a2lc1o1_178d2b99:

    # hi "Yes, it is."
    hi "Sí, ho és."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5896
translate ca a2lc1o1_3052d214:

    # li "You're a very bad liar, Hisao."
    li "No saps mentir, Hisao."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5898
translate ca a2lc1o1_ea51b25c:

    # hi "That's true, but that's why I'm not lying. I'm a very trustworthy person."
    hi "És cert, però per això no menteixo. Soc una persona de fiar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5903
translate ca a2lc1o1_e0fd7105:

    # li "I'm sure you are. I think I can forgive you just this once, though."
    li "Estic segura que ho ets. Però crec que puc perdonar-t'ho aquesta vegada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5905
translate ca a2lc1o1_6363f6c3:

    # hi "Forgive? What for, exactly?"
    hi "Perdonar-me? Per què, exactament?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5915
translate ca a2lc1o1_9256d547:

    # "She giggles a little before resuming her quiet walking. Just what is she thinking now?"
    "Riu una mica abans de reprendre el seu caminar tranquil. Què deu estar pensant ara?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5919
translate ca a2lc1o1_acb5390d:

    # "I look up to the dark sky as I slump my shoulders."
    "Miro cap al cel fosc i abaixo les espatlles."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5921
translate ca a2lc1o1_2693eeb0:

    # "I think this is something I have to sort out for myself, rather than relying on her for everything."
    "Crec que això és una cosa que he de resoldre jo mateix, en lloc de dependre d'ella per tot."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5926
translate ca a2lc1o2_c0849fe4:

    # hi "It was just kind of… I was thinking about how you seem to have everything so sorted out, even with Hanako relying on you. I can admit that even I kind of relied on you when I first transferred in."
    hi "Només era una mena de... Estava pensant en com sembla que ho tens tot ben resolt, fins i tot amb la Hanako depenent de tu. He d'admetre que fins i tot jo vaig dependre de tu una mica quan vaig arribar."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5928
translate ca a2lc1o2_94e37d34:

    # hi "I think it's a good quality to have."
    hi "Crec que és una bona qualitat."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5930
translate ca a2lc1o2_47a4a17b:

    # "I turn to Lilly, surveying her reaction."
    "Em giro cap a la Lilly, i observo la seva reacció."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5937
translate ca a2lc1o2_924770ff:

    # "She's forcing herself to look forward and furrowing her brow quite a bit. Her face looks a bit awkward, as if she was trying to find just the right words."
    "S'obliga a mirar cap endavant i arrufa força el front. Fa una cara que sembla una mica incòmoda, com si estigués intentant trobar les paraules adequades."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5939
translate ca a2lc1o2_ae1c704a:

    # hi "…Lilly?"
    hi "... Lilly?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5944
translate ca a2lc1o2_d195aac8:

    # li "I would thank you, but… assuming that I don't rely on the presence of others is too much. You'd be wrong to think that Hanako simply depends on me with nothing in return."
    li "T'ho agrairia, però... suposar que no compto amb la presència dels altres és massa. T'equivocaries si pensessis que la Hanako simplement depèn de mi sense fer res a canvi."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5946
translate ca a2lc1o2_5b54c61c:

    # "She seems to have a bit of trouble saying it, even though it's largely what I'd thought already."
    "Sembla que li costa dir-ho, tot i que és en gran part el que jo ja pensava."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5948
translate ca a2lc1o2_7d220cf8:

    # "If she's tried so hard to maintain her independence, as anyone would have had to in her position, sighted or not, maybe she finds it hard to talk about her own needs."
    "Si s'ha esforçat tant per mantenir la seva independència, com qualsevol persona hauria fet en la seva posició, cega o no, potser li costa parlar de les seves pròpies necessitats."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5950
translate ca a2lc1o2_bc4a7e2b:

    # "It's only now that I realize an omission in what she says, though. I decide to follow it up, largely in jest, to avoid things getting too personal."
    "De sobte m'adono d'una omissió en això que diu. Decideixo insistir, en gran part de broma, per a evitar que les coses es tornin massa personals."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5952
translate ca a2lc1o2_8eefb666:

    # hi "Oh? And what about me?"
    hi "Oh? I jo què?"

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5959
translate ca a2lc1o2_013b7ffa:

    # "She suddenly runs ahead of me and turns, blocking me off."
    "De cop i volta corre davant meu i es gira, bloquejant-me el pas."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5964
translate ca a2lc1o2_d6180298:

    # "With a smile, she holds her hands behind her as she leans forwards."
    "Amb un somriure, es posa les mans a l'esquena mentre s'inclina cap endavant."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5966
translate ca a2lc1o2_4bd09d8f:

    # li "You're different."
    li "Ets diferent."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5972
translate ca a2lc1o2_09006685:

    # "And with that, she turns back and continues to walk ahead of me, a newfound spring in her step."
    "I amb això, es gira i segueix caminant davant meu, amb un nou impuls en el seu pas."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5974
translate ca a2lc1o2_f93e1cd1:

    # "All I can do is raise an eyebrow and give a dazed grin. I don't think I've ever seen this playful and teasing side of her before."
    "L'única cosa que puc fer és aixecar una cella i somriure astorat. Crec que mai l'havia vist tan juganera i bromista."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5976
translate ca a2lc1o2_3198719b:

    # "So… I'm 'different'. It's hard to work out the exact context, but knowing her, this ambiguity was intended."
    "Així que... soc \"diferent\". És difícil desxifrar el context exacte, però coneixent-la, aquesta ambigüitat era intencionada."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5978
translate ca a2lc1o2_984cc428:

    # "Our relationship has been changing, at the very least simply because I've begun to stand on my own feet more and started getting more curious about the situation of those around me."
    "La nostra relació ha anat canviant, com a mínim, simplement perquè he començat a valdre'm més de mi mateix i he començat a sentir més curiositat per la situació d'aquells que m'envolten."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5980
translate ca a2lc1o2_de855c40:

    # "As to why… probably a mix of personal curiosity, and a want to try and work out how to deal with my situation."
    "Pel que fa a per què... probablement una barreja de curiositat personal, i ganes d'intentar esbrinar com fer front a la meva situació."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5982
translate ca a2lc1o2_254c0849:

    # "I'm less sure of Lilly, though. That's why her own statement, so similar to my own feelings towards her, throws me off so much."
    "Tot i així, estic menys segur de la Lilly. És per això que la seva pròpia declaració, tan similar als meus propis sentiments cap a ella, em desconcerta una mica."

# game/script-a2-lilly.rpy:5984
translate ca a2lc1o2_ca410592:

    # "Watching her make her way up the street, cane tapping from left to right, I decide to settle the matter later, and just smile. This is a nice side to her, and I don't want to forget it."
    "Mentre veig com pujar pel carrer, fent copets amb el bastó d'esquerra a dreta, decideixo resoldre l'assumpte més tard, i em limito a somriure. Té un costat bonic i no vull oblidar-lo."

translate ca strings:

